x_pagination=\"next_prev\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][td_block_ad_box spot_id=\"sidebar\" spot_title=\"- Advertisement - \"][td_block_21 custom_title=\"LIFESTYLE\" sort=\"random_posts\" limit=\"3\" ajax_pagination=\"next_prev\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][td_block_ad_box spot_id=\"custom_ad_1\" spot_title=\"- Advertisement - \"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][td_block_16 custom_title=\"BUSINESS\" sort=\"random_posts\" td_ajax_filter_type=\"td_category_ids_filter\" ajax_pagination=\"next_prev\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"td-ss-row\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][td_block_1 custom_title=\"NEWS\" sort=\"random_posts\" ajax_pagination=\"next_prev\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][td_block_4 custom_title=\"SPORT\" sort=\"random_posts\" limit=\"1\" ajax_pagination=\"next_prev\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][td_block_ad_box spot_id=\"custom_ad_1\" spot_title=\"- Advertisement - \"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][td_block_4 custom_title=\"LATEST POSTS\" sort=\"random_posts\" limit=\"3\" td_ajax_filter_type=\"td_category_ids_filter\" ajax_pagination=\"load_more\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','29-revision-v1','','','2016-08-26 08:43:44','2016-08-26 08:43:44','',29,'http://feelsyoung.com/29-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(251,1,'2016-08-30 09:40:03','2016-08-30 09:40:03','<h3>Apart from having huge potentials in their respective Olympic disciplines, these 30 female athletes have everything that can mesmerize any guy. They are smart, beautiful, and they have a nice body. I am quite sure, after going over this article you will be following the Olympics more regularly.</h3>\r\n<h2><strong>30. Eugenie Bouchard</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Canadian superstar is popularly known as Genie. She is the best female tennis player for Canada at the moment.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-266\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Eugenie-Bouchard.jpg\" alt=\"Eugenie Bouchard\" width=\"640\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong> 29. Aly Raisman</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is not the first Olympic for Aly Raisman. She led the US women\'s gymnastics team in London.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-256\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Aly-Raisman.jpg\" alt=\"Aly Raisman\" width=\"680\" height=\"450\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>28. Meghan Hardin</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>She is one of the Hottest LPGA players ever. Apart from golfing, she is also involved in modeling.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-274\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meghan-Hardin.jpg\" alt=\"Meghan Hardin\" width=\"700\" height=\"449\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>27. Caroline Wozniacki</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The former world number 1 tennis sensation is Denmark’s apple of eye in this Olympics. She will brighten up the court with her glamorous presence.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-262\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Caroline-Wozniacki.jpg\" alt=\"Caroline Wozniacki\" width=\"700\" height=\"414\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>26. Jessica Ennis </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Gold medalist in London Olympics, Jessica Ennis is hot favorite in this edition too. The Brits will rely on her for another medal to add to their tally.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-341\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Jessica_Ennis.jpg\" alt=\"Jessica_Ennis\" width=\"609\" height=\"395\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>25. Karsta Lowe</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Opponents will have a hard time stopping Karsta Lowe on the volleyball court. She is one of the tallest players in the US team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-269\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Karsta-Lowe.jpg\" alt=\"Karsta Lowe\" width=\"834\" height=\"448\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>24. Alana Blanchard</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Alana won a lot of competitions throughout her surfing career. She will be eyeing her first Olympic gold this year.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-253\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alana-Blanchard.jpg\" alt=\"Alana Blanchard\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>23. Paige Selenski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The American field hockey sensation is known for her presence in and outside the turf. She is an effective player in the forward position.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-279\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paige-Selenski.jpg\" alt=\"Paige Selenski\" width=\"700\" height=\"402\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>22. Lexi Weeks</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The aspiring American pole-vaulter is a much sought-after name in this Olympic. The Arkansas born is making her Olympic debut.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-272\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lexi-Weeks.jpg\" alt=\"Lexi Weeks\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>21. Camille Leblanc-Bazinet</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Camille is the incumbent Canadian weightlifting champion. She is one of the favorites to make it to the podium.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-261\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Camille-Leblanc-Bazinet.jpg\" alt=\"Camille Leblanc-Bazinet\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>20. Michelle Jenneke</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Michelle bagged a silver in the young Olympic. Could she be able to achieve the same feat in the Rio edition?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-276\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michelle-Jenneke.jpg\" alt=\"Michelle Jenneke\" width=\"700\" height=\"388\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>19. Ellen Hoog</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ellen played a big role in Dutch triumph in London Olympics. This year she will try to continue that success trend.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-264\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ellen-hoog.jpg\" alt=\"ellen hoog\" width=\"604\" height=\"351\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>18. Anastasia Ashley</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anastasia Ashley is an American surfer who is part of the team USA in the Rio Olympics. She has the skill and experience to make a podium finish.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-258 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Anastasia-Ashley.jpg\" alt=\"Anastasia Ashley\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>17. Sophie Horn</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Sophie is participating in this year’s summer Olympics. She is a professional golfer who represents Great Britain.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-280 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sophie-Horn.jpg\" alt=\"Sophie Horn\" width=\"412\" height=\"481\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>16. Lauren Sesselmann</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Canadian soccer star Lauren is a charismatic controller of the ball. She has a touch of glamour as well.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-270\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lauren-Sesselmann.jpg\" alt=\"Lauren Sesselmann\" width=\"720\" height=\"524\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>15. Ana Ivanovic</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Serbian will try her best to win the first Gold medal representing her country. She has recently got married to Bastian Schweinsteiger.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-292\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ana-ivanovic.jpg\" alt=\"ana ivanovic\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>14. Whitney Miller</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Whitney Miller is an American model and Jiu Jitsu player. She is one of the most iconic Olympians in the team USA.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-281\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Whitney-Miller.jpg\" alt=\"Whitney Miller\" width=\"700\" height=\"823\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>13. Christen Press</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Americans will rely on Christen Press for yet another gold. She plays as a forward for the national team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-263\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Christen-Press.jpg\" alt=\"Christen Press\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Camila Giorgi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Italian tennis player of Argentine descent can surprise the audience with her signature backhand and forehand.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-260\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Camila-Giorgi.jpg\" alt=\"Camila Giorgi\" width=\"699\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>11. Mikaela Mayer</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Born in LA Mikaela can make the difference for the Americans on the ring. She is firm on her goal to win this year.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mikaela-Mayer.jpg\" alt=\"Mikaela Mayer\" width=\"645\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Maggie Vessey</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Maggie earned the 8th position four years ago. Can she win a medal this time?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Maggie-Vessey.jpg\" alt=\"Maggie Vessey\" width=\"683\" height=\"870\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>9. Leryn Franco</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Paraguayan model cum javelin thrower took part in three consecutive Olympics. This will be another chance for her to win the glory.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-271\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Leryn-Franco.jpg\" alt=\"Leryn Franco\" width=\"441\" height=\"650\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>8. Antonija Sandric</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Croatian woman basketball player is known for her aggressiveness on the court. She plays the role of both shooting guard and point guard.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-295\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Antonija-Sandric-1.jpg\" alt=\"Antonija Sandric\" width=\"673\" height=\"373\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Alex Morgan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The US international helped her team to the top podium finish in the London Olympics. Can she repeat that once again?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-297\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alex-Morgan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alex Morgan\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>6. Michelle Waterson</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The UFC star has a reputation for making those eye catching kicks. She will be a big contender to win a medal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-277\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michelle-Waterson.jpg\" alt=\"Michelle Waterson\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>5. Melanie Adams</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Australian pole-vaulter has earned fame for her modeling performance. This is time for her to prove her athletic skill.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-275\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Melanie-Adams.jpg\" alt=\"Melanie Adams\" width=\"625\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. Zsuzsanna Jakabos</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Hungarian beauty will be competing in the swimming pool to win the glory for her country.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-282\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Zsuzsanna-Jakabos.jpg\" alt=\"Zsuzsanna Jakabos\" width=\"700\" height=\"474\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>3. Hope Solo</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The American goalkeeper has already won the Olympic glory for her country in two previous editions. This year will be an opportunity for her to make history, once again.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-293\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Hope-Solo-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hope Solo\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>2. Emma Coburn</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Colorado born Emma Coburn will bear the torch for her country in 3000 meter steeplechase track competition.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-265\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Emma-Coburn.jpg\" alt=\"Emma Coburn\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>1. Allison Stokke</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Allison Stokke won bronze medal for USA in a previous edition. She will be looking forward to add another to that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-255 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Allison-Stokke.jpg\" alt=\"Allison Stokke\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />','30 Hot Female Athletes That Give You Another Reason To Watch the Olympics','','publish','open','open','','30-hot-female-athletes-that-give-you-another-reason-to-watch-the-olympics','','','2016-08-30 11:14:31','2016-08-30 11:14:31','',0,'http://feelsyoung.com/?p=251',0,'post','',0),(253,1,'2016-08-30 08:49:11','2016-08-30 08:49:11','','Alana Blanchard','','inherit','open','closed','','alana-blanchard','','','2016-08-30 08:49:11','2016-08-30 08:49:11','',251,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alana-Blanchard.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(254,1,'2016-08-30 08:49:14','2016-08-30 08:49:14','','Alex Morgan','','inherit','open','closed','','alex-morgan','','','2016-08-30 08: