ung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Meghan-Hardin.jpg\" alt=\"Meghan Hardin\" width=\"700\" height=\"449\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>27. Caroline Wozniacki</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The former world number 1 tennis sensation is Denmark’s apple of eye in this Olympics. She will brighten up the court with her glamorous presence.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-262\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Caroline-Wozniacki.jpg\" alt=\"Caroline Wozniacki\" width=\"700\" height=\"414\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>26. Jessica Ennis </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Gold medalist in London Olympics, Jessica Ennis is hot favorite in this edition too. The Brits will rely on her for another medal to add to their tally.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-341\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Jessica_Ennis.jpg\" alt=\"Jessica_Ennis\" width=\"609\" height=\"395\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>25. Karsta Lowe</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Opponents will have a hard time stopping Karsta Lowe on the volleyball court. She is one of the tallest players in the US team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-269\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Karsta-Lowe.jpg\" alt=\"Karsta Lowe\" width=\"834\" height=\"448\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>24. Alana Blanchard</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Alana won a lot of competitions throughout her surfing career. She will be eyeing her first Olympic gold this year.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-253\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alana-Blanchard.jpg\" alt=\"Alana Blanchard\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>23. Paige Selenski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The American field hockey sensation is known for her presence in and outside the turf. She is an effective player in the forward position.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-279\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paige-Selenski.jpg\" alt=\"Paige Selenski\" width=\"700\" height=\"402\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>22. Lexi Weeks</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The aspiring American pole-vaulter is a much sought-after name in this Olympic. The Arkansas born is making her Olympic debut.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-272\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lexi-Weeks.jpg\" alt=\"Lexi Weeks\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>21. Camille Leblanc-Bazinet</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Camille is the incumbent Canadian weightlifting champion. She is one of the favorites to make it to the podium.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-261\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Camille-Leblanc-Bazinet.jpg\" alt=\"Camille Leblanc-Bazinet\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>20. Michelle Jenneke</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Michelle bagged a silver in the young Olympic. Could she be able to achieve the same feat in the Rio edition?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-276\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michelle-Jenneke.jpg\" alt=\"Michelle Jenneke\" width=\"700\" height=\"388\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>19. Ellen Hoog</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ellen played a big role in Dutch triumph in London Olympics. This year she will try to continue that success trend.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-264\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ellen-hoog.jpg\" alt=\"ellen hoog\" width=\"604\" height=\"351\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>18. Anastasia Ashley</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anastasia Ashley is an American surfer who is part of the team USA in the Rio Olympics. She has the skill and experience to make a podium finish.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-258 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Anastasia-Ashley.jpg\" alt=\"Anastasia Ashley\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>17. Sophie Horn</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Sophie is participating in this year’s summer Olympics. She is a professional golfer who represents Great Britain.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-280 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sophie-Horn.jpg\" alt=\"Sophie Horn\" width=\"412\" height=\"481\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>16. Lauren Sesselmann</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Canadian soccer star Lauren is a charismatic controller of the ball. She has a touch of glamour as well.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-270\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lauren-Sesselmann.jpg\" alt=\"Lauren Sesselmann\" width=\"720\" height=\"524\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>15. Ana Ivanovic</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Serbian will try her best to win the first Gold medal representing her country. She has recently got married to Bastian Schweinsteiger.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-292\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ana-ivanovic.jpg\" alt=\"ana ivanovic\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>14. Whitney Miller</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Whitney Miller is an American model and Jiu Jitsu player. She is one of the most iconic Olympians in the team USA.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-281\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Whitney-Miller.jpg\" alt=\"Whitney Miller\" width=\"700\" height=\"823\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>13. Christen Press</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Americans will rely on Christen Press for yet another gold. She plays as a forward for the national team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-263\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Christen-Press.jpg\" alt=\"Christen Press\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Camila Giorgi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Italian tennis player of Argentine descent can surprise the audience with her signature backhand and forehand.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-260\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Camila-Giorgi.jpg\" alt=\"Camila Giorgi\" width=\"699\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>11. Mikaela Mayer</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Born in LA Mikaela can make the difference for the Americans on the ring. She is firm on her goal to win this year.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-278\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mikaela-Mayer.jpg\" alt=\"Mikaela Mayer\" width=\"645\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Maggie Vessey</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Maggie earned the 8th position four years ago. Can she win a medal this time?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-273\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Maggie-Vessey.jpg\" alt=\"Maggie Vessey\" width=\"683\" height=\"870\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>9. Leryn Franco</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Paraguayan model cum javelin thrower took part in three consecutive Olympics. This will be another chance for her to win the glory.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-271\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Leryn-Franco.jpg\" alt=\"Leryn Franco\" width=\"441\" height=\"650\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>8. Antonija Sandric</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Croatian woman basketball player is known for her aggressiveness on the court. She plays the role of both shooting guard and point guard.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-295\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Antonija-Sandric-1.jpg\" alt=\"Antonija Sandric\" width=\"673\" height=\"373\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Alex Morgan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The US international helped her team to the top podium finish in the London Olympics. Can she repeat that once again?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-297\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alex-Morgan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Alex Morgan\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>6. Michelle Waterson</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The UFC star has a reputation for making those eye catching kicks. She will be a big contender to win a medal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-277\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michelle-Waterson.jpg\" alt=\"Michelle Waterson\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>5. Melanie Adams</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Australian pole-vaulter has earned fame for her modeling performance. This is time for her to prove her athletic skill.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-275\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Melanie-Adams.jpg\" alt=\"Melanie Adams\" width=\"625\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. Zsuzsanna Jakabos</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Hungarian beauty will be competing in the swimming pool to win the glory for her country.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-282\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Zsuzsanna-Jakabos.jpg\" alt=\"Zsuzsanna Jakabos\" width=\"700\" height=\"474\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>3. Hope Solo</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The American goalkeeper has already won the Olympic glory for her country in two previous editions. This year will be an opportunity for her to make history, once again.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-293\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Hope-Solo-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hope Solo\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>2. Emma Coburn</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Colorado born Emma Coburn will bear the torch for her country in 3000 meter steeplechase track competition.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-265\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Emma-Coburn.jpg\" alt=\"Emma Coburn\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>1. Allison Stokke</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Allison Stokke won bronze medal for USA in a previous edition. She will be looking forward to add another to that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-255 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Allison-Stokke.jpg\" alt=\"Allison Stokke\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />','30 Hot Female Athletes That Give You Another Reason To Watch the Olympics','','inherit','closed','closed','','251-revision-v1','','','2016-08-30 11:14:31','2016-08-30 11:14:31','',251,'http://feelsyoung.com/251-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(343,1,'2016-08-30 11:15:41','2016-08-30 11:15:41','<h3>With new threats popping up every day, army of a country plays the most crucial role in saving sovereignty and the population of a country from external and internal threats. A powerful army doesn’t always necessarily need to be huge, if it can make advances in other fields like cyber warfare and modern technology. Often building on tactical ability could be proven more effective than raising an army with huge firepower.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>30. Portugal</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h3>The Portuguese army’s golden days lie in its colonial past when the country ruled many African countries. Today it might not have the same might as it had before, but it still has an army that is superior to many other nations’.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-226\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Portugal.jpg\" alt=\"Portugal\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong> 29. South Africa</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>There was a time when the South African army was used as a tool to oppress its own people. But after the end of the apartheid regime, the country has rebuilt its army and established it as a protector of the people.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-304\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/South_African_Army.jpg\" alt=\"South_African_Army\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>28. Malaysia</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Despite having a modern and well-equipped military, the Malaysians have a neutral policy to deal with major conflicts. The country’s army is however playing a pivotal role in peacekeeping missions.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-219 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/malaysian.jpg\" alt=\"malaysian\" width=\"568\" height=\"390\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>27. Norway</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You might be frowning to see the name of the country where Nobel peace prize is given. The Norwegian army is one of the most skilled in the world.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-222 \" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Norway.jpg\" alt=\"Norway\" width=\"612\" height=\"408\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>26. Singapore </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A tiny city state like Singapore always has different security concerns. The country’s leaders gave the duty to build their army to the Israelis. The result? Singapore has one of the most professional armies in the South East Asian region.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Singapore.jpg\" alt=\"Singapore\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>25. North Korea</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After the fall of the Soviet Union the authoritarian country found itself friendless. To tackle its neighbor in the South, the country has never stopped developing nuclear weapons that empower the army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-221\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/North-Korea.jpg\" alt=\"North Korea\" width=\"750\" height=\"406\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>24. Mexico</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Mexican army played a vital role in helping the government and local administration in containing drug related violence. Thanks to the Mexican army, the law and order situation in that country is much better, if not the best.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mexico.jpg\" alt=\"Mexico\" width=\"640\" height=\"395\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>23. The Netherlands </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Dutch army was harassed in the hands of the Nazis during WWII. After the war, the country worked hard on building a reliable army to defend its territories.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-301\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dutch-army.jpg\" alt=\"Dutch-army\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>22. Sweden </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When you have border with a country that boasts one of the biggest armies in the world, there is no way to take the matter of defense lightly. The Swedes are also prominent for making high-end military hardware.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-231\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sweden-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Sweden\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>21. Switzerland</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though Switzerland always maintains neutrality, in this ever changing global scenario there is no alternative to having a decent military. And the Swiss have it.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switzerland1.jpg\" alt=\"Switzerland1\" width=\"800\" height=\"505\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>20. Syria</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Syrian army was one of the strongest in the Middle East, before all hell broke loose. Their presence in Lebanon was a major headache for the Israelis.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-305\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Syrian-army.jpg\" alt=\"Syrian army\" width=\"669\" height=\"377\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>19. Iran</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Years of sanctions slapped by the world could not stop the Iranians from building a strong army. In today’s major regional conflicts Iranian presence shows this clearly.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Iran.jpg\" alt=\"Iran\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>18. Australia </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though Australia is a huge country, the army is relatively small. But it doesn’t mean that it is weak.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-206\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Australia.jpg\" alt=\"Australia\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>17. Indonesia</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In all fields, Indonesians are open to everything west. Through vigorous cooperation with major Western military powers, the island nation has formed a strong army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Indonesian.jpg\" alt=\"Indonesian\" width=\"736\" height=\"572\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>16. Poland </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Poland has one of the finest armies in Eastern Europe. With US logistic support and training the Polish army is now able to give any intruder a big fight.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-303\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Polish_Army.jpeg\" alt=\"Polish_Army\" width=\"770\" height=\"447\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>15. Canada</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though the number of the Canadian armed forces personnel is meager in comparison to the Americans, Canada has a modern and professional army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Canada.jpg\" alt=\"RIMPAC 2012\" width=\"750\" height=\"536\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>14. Brazil</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The second largest army in South America has been involved in different peace keeping missions. The Brazilian army’s role in Haiti is praiseworthy for bringing stability.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-307\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/brazilian-army.jpg\" alt=\"brazilian army\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>13. Egypt</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Thanks to years of US military aid, the Egyptian army is one of the biggest and strongest in the Middle East. The army there also is a potent force during major political upheavals.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-210\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Egypt.jpg\" alt=\"Egypt\" width=\"623\" height=\"315\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>12. Israel</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The IDF or Israeli Defense Force is one of the strongest in the world. Till now, it has won all the wars against its larger Arab neighbors.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-216\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/israel-1.jpg\" alt=\"israel 1\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>11. Japan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Japan has recently removed the last barrier to erase the pacifist clause from its constitution. In the coming years we are sure to see a more assertive Japanese Self Defense Force.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Japan.jpg\" alt=\"Japan\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>10. South Korea</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>With an effective conscription system, the South Koreans have made their army ready for any untoward situation. The formidable army is a good match for its bitter rivals in the North.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/south-korean.jpg\" alt=\"A South Korean army soldier runs in front of K-1 tanks after a live-fire military exercise as a part of the Seoul International Aerospace and Defense Exhibition 2011 on the Seungjin fire training field in Pocheon\" width=\"1000\" height=\"568\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>9. Turkey</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Turkey boasts the second largest army in NATO, right after USA. The Turkish army has been able to effectively contain the Kurdish insurgency.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-237\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Turkey.jpg\" alt=\"Turkey Army Troops, Militants Mass in Aleppo: Russian Monitor\" width=\"650\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>8. Germany</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Experts believe that the German army is yet to match its formidable economic might. The biggest economy in Europe is however making rapid advance in the defense sector.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Germany.jpg\" alt=\"Germany\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>7. Pakistan </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Pakistan army is still the most potent state institution in that country. At the moment it is fighting a fanatic Taliban faction in the country’s North Waziristan.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"Pakistan\" width=\"580\" height=\"386\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>6. The United Kingdom</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though the British army went through several budget cuts in the last few years, it’s still one of the strongest militaries in the world. The army still maintains presence in different British overseas territories.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-united-kingdom.jpg\" alt=\"The united kingdom\" width=\"940\" height=\"467\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>5. France</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>France is one of the forces leading the fight against the brutal Islamic State. Besides they have presence in different African countries, where extremism is at rise.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-302\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/french-army.jpg\" alt=\"french army\" width=\"1110\" height=\"624\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>4. India</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The archrival of Pakistan, India has one of the biggest armies in the world. The Indian army has so far beaten the Pakistanis in three big wars.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/india.jpg\" alt=\"india\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>3. China</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>The Chinese has the biggest army in the world with more than 2 million active personnel. In the recent years the country has continued defense budget spending spree to match the likes of United State.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-300\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Chinese-army.jpg\" alt=\"Chinese army\" width=\"885\" height=\"516\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>2. Russia</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>The Russian army might not be in the best position in comparison to its Western rivals, but it still has supremacy around its borders. The annexation of Crimea is the best example of it. The Russians have started modernizing its army after years of stalemate following the collapse of the Soviet Union, though.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/russia.jpg\" alt=\"russia\" width=\"670\" height=\"400\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>1. The United States Army</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The US army is still the strongest army in the world with the most advanced technologies, weapons, and an effective training system. The country’s defense budget is also the world’s biggest, and no other country is likely to overlap it in the upcoming years.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-244\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/United-States.jpg\" alt=\"United States\" width=\"752\" height=\"423\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>','30 Most Powerful Armies In The World','','inherit','closed','closed','','172-revision-v1','','','2016-08-30 11:15:41','2016-08-30 11:15:41','',172,'http://feelsyoung.com/172-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(344,1,'2016-08-30 11:44:52','2016-08-30 11:44:52','','Blue Eyeshadow','','inherit','open','closed','','blue-eyeshadow','','','2016-08-30 11:44:52','2016-08-30 11:44:52','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Blue-Eyeshadow.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(345,1,'2016-08-30 11:44:55','2016-08-30 11:44:55','','Booty Shorts','','inherit','open','closed','','booty-shorts','','','2016-08-30 11:44:55','2016-08-30 11:44:55','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Booty-Shorts.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(346,1,'2016-08-30 11:44:56','2016-08-30 11:44:56','','Costume shoes','','inherit','open','closed','','costume-shoes-2','','','2016-08-30 11:44:56','2016-08-30 11:44:56','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Costume-shoes.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(347,1,'2016-08-30 11:44:58','2016-08-30 11:44:58','','Glitter Eyeshadow','','inherit','open','closed','','glitter-eyeshadow','','','2016-08-30 11:44:58','2016-08-30 11:44:58','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Glitter-Eyeshadow.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(348,1,'2016-08-30 11:45:00','2016-08-30 11:45:00','','Tube Tops','','inherit','open','closed','','tube-tops','','','2016-08-30 11:45:00','2016-08-30 11:45:00','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tube-Tops.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(349,1,'2016-08-30 11:45:01','2016-08-30 11:45:01','','','','inherit','open','closed','','w926-ae-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-jeans-size-0-short-womens-jeans-815d30d5689245458a25f910b1e30c84','','','2016-08-30 11:45:59','2016-08-30 11:45:59','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/w926-ae-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-jeans-size-0-short-womens-jeans-815d30d5689245458a25f910b1e30c84.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(350,1,'2016-08-30 11:45:02','2016-08-30 11:45:02','','w1032-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-size-00-short-womens-jeans-8e54f59c03a4f5ad0f690f5fdcf28e97','','inherit','open','closed','','w1032-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-size-00-short-womens-jeans-8e54f59c03a4f5ad0f690f5fdcf28e97','','','2016-08-30 11:45:02','2016-08-30 11:45:02','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/w1032-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-size-00-short-womens-jeans-8e54f59c03a4f5ad0f690f5fdcf28e97.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(351,1,'2016-08-30 11:45:04','2016-08-30 11:45:04','','Woman Overalls','','inherit','open','closed','','woman-overalls','','','2016-08-30 11:45:04','2016-08-30 11:45:04','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Woman-Overalls.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(352,1,'2016-08-30 11:48:51','2016-08-30 11:48:51','<h3>Maybe you are at the turning point of life where you have started feeling the vibe of hitting the 35 year mark. This is considered as the time of life where you need to settle down. So, a change in everything is inevitable. Every age has its pros and cons. If you are a middle-aged woman, you should avoid wearing a few things that would not suit your personality and look, as they did before.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>25. Costume Shoes</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We all gave up to our urge to get a pair of costume shoes one time or another. But if you are around 40, you should not be wearing those for comfortability’s sake.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Costume-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"Costume shoes\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>24. Bedazzled Anything</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The bedazzled trend began about 16 years ago. Now it is considered as one of the biggest fashion flops. Unless you are in your early teen, you should not be trying them.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bedazzled-anything.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>23. Blue Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To be honest, no matter how old are you, you should avoid wearing them for good.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Blue-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Eyeshadow\" width=\"440\" height=\"329\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>22. Victoria\'s Secret PINK</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Pink is something predetermined for teens. Don’t harass yourself when you are in your 30s.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/21.-Victorias-Secret-PINK.jpg\" alt=\"Victoria\'s Pink\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>21. Leopard Print</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Unless you want to do something extraordinary, you should reconsider your decision. At the end of the day nobody wants to end up getting a title what they are not.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-329\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/20.-Leopard-Print.jpg\" alt=\"20. Leopard Print\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>20. Sparkly Pants</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t make your pants a place to compete with the sun; believe me, they look worse than you can imagine.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-328\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/19.-Sparkly-Pants.jpg\" alt=\"19. Sparkly Pants\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>19. Oversized Sunglasses </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is one of those things allotted for young people, only. Unless you don’t care about your personality, you should give them up for good.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/18.-Oversized-Sunglasses.jpg\" alt=\"18. Oversized Sunglasses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>18. Crop Tops &amp; Hotpants</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When you are more than fit, you can flaunt that beautiful body of yours. But, you should not be wearing crop tops and hotpants at an age when a fat belly can distract others and be a mismatch for your personality.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-335\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/crop-tops-and-hotpants.jpg\" alt=\"crop tops and hotpants\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>17. Non-matching Socks</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Your socks often say who you are. Be careful about that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-326\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/17.-Non-matching-Socks.jpg\" alt=\"17. Non-matching Socks\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>16. Hoop Earrings</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They are more suitable for girls who are attending high school. Get yourself some mature stuff.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-325\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.-Hoop-Earrings.jpg\" alt=\"16. Hoop Earrings\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>15. Furry Boots</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>“Only for teenagers” – doesn’t that say it all! You would regret wearing them.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-324\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15.-Furry-Boots.jpg\" alt=\"15. Furry Boots\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>14. Furry Anything</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anything furry has never been a great choice to look age appropriate. They will just add up to your misery!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-323\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14.-Furry-Anything.jpg\" alt=\"14. Furry Anything\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>13. Tube Tops</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Cameron Diaz recently announced that she is not going to wear them anymore. So, why do you bother?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-348\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tube-Tops.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Tops\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Short Dresses</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You have other ways to look sexy. Don’t bare it all to attract people.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-321\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12.-Short-Dresses.jpg\" alt=\"12. Short Dresses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>11. Mini-Skirts</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>“Know thyself”. Remember, you can’t always mix it up.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-320\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11.-Mini-Skirts.jpg\" alt=\"11. Mini-Skirts\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Woman Overalls</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Do you work at a farm? If not, help yourself.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-351\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Woman-Overalls.jpg\" alt=\"Woman Overalls\" width=\"570\" height=\"570\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>9. Anything Showing Excessive Cleavage</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A mature woman should never flaunt too much. It makes her look vulnerable and helpless.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Showing-Excessive-Cleavage.jpg\" alt=\"Showing Excessive Cleavage\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>8. American Eagle</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They have cool, fitting jeans. But they are no longer for you.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-349\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/w926-ae-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-jeans-size-0-short-womens-jeans-815d30d5689245458a25f910b1e30c84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Booty Shorts</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To be honest, I am yet to find out at what age you can wear them!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-345\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Booty-Shorts.jpg\" alt=\"Booty Shorts\" width=\"564\" height=\"564\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>6. Old Sneakers</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Rundown tennis shoes are not for you. You deserve better than that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-316\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6.-Old-Sneakers.png\" alt=\"6. Old Sneakers\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>5. Cheap Bras</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t deprive your boobies of some quality stuff. They are not young anymore and deserve something more comfortable.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-315\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/5.-Cheap-Bras.jpg\" alt=\"5. Cheap Bras\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. Glitter Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Glitter should be put on things that need to sparkle. It’s not the other way around.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-347\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Glitter-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Glitter Eyeshadow\" width=\"853\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>3. Platform Flip-Flops</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Nobody should wear them. They are neither cool, nor sexy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-313\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3.-Platform-Flip-Flops.jpg\" alt=\"3. Platform Flip-Flops\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Can you even fit yourself in them? I don’t think so.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-312\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2.-Abercrombie-Fitch.jpg\" alt=\"2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>1. Scrunchies</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t look like someone who has no time to do her hair. Your hair is a part and parcel of your personality.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-311\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.-Scrunchies.jpg\" alt=\"1. Scrunchies\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->','25 Things That Middle-Aged Women Should Not Wear','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-revision-v1','','','2016-08-30 11:48:51','2016-08-30 11:48:51','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/287-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(353,1,'2016-08-30 11:49:27','2016-08-30 11:49:27','<h3>Maybe you are at the turning point of life where you have started feeling the vibe of hitting the 35 year mark. This is considered as the time of life where you need to settle down. So, a change in everything is inevitable. Every age has its pros and cons. If you are a middle-aged woman, you should avoid wearing a few things that would not suit your personality and look, as they did before.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>25. Costume Shoes</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We all gave up to our urge to get a pair of costume shoes one time or another. But if you are around 40, you should not be wearing those for comfortability’s sake.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Costume-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"Costume shoes\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>24. Bedazzled Anything</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The bedazzled trend began about 16 years ago. Now it is considered as one of the biggest fashion flops. Unless you are in your early teen, you should not be trying them.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bedazzled-anything.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>23. Blue Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To be honest, no matter how old are you, you should avoid wearing them for good.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Blue-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Eyeshadow\" width=\"440\" height=\"329\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>22. Victoria\'s Secret PINK</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Pink is something predetermined for teens. Don’t harass yourself when you are in your 30s.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/21.-Victorias-Secret-PINK.jpg\" alt=\"Victoria\'s Pink\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>21. Leopard Print</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Unless you want to do something extraordinary, you should reconsider your decision. At the end of the day nobody wants to end up getting a title what they are not.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-329\"