Frasier’.</h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Reginald Veljohnson</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nRemember the famous Limo driver in the franchise? He was also a part of the ‘Die Hard 2’ cast.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-474\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Reginald-Veljohnson.jpg\" alt=\"Reginald Veljohnson\" width=\"750\" height=\"364\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nIn his later appearances on TV shows and movies he played the role of a cop or other bossy figures.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Linda Kozlowski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nIn the movie she was often referred to as the apple of Dundee’s eye. No wonder they got married in real life. However, their marriage didn’t long last.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-471\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Linda-Kozlowski.jpg\" alt=\"Linda Kozlowski\" width=\"625\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nFar away from the limelight, she now motivates in her travel operation business located in Marrakesh.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>David Gulpilil</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nDavid was no central figure in the movie. The franchise however would not have been felt the same if he had been left out.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-469\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil.jpg\" alt=\"David Gulpilil\" width=\"466\" height=\"310\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nDavid was accused of felony and served time in jail for a year. He still continues with his acting career.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Paul Hogan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nThe Crocodile Dundee franchise gave him both name and fame; so much so that he rejected offers for hit movies like “Ghost”. His devotion paid him well.</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nHogan’s later life was not so enviable – he was accused of tax fraud. He now takes care of his son.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Steve Rackman</strong></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Then\r\nHis character Donk was lucky enough to have kissed Dundee in the movie. Before being selected for the hit franchise, he was a professional wrestler.</h3>\r\n<h3>Now\r\nSteve ended his career in a grandeur way by completing the trilogy. Back home in Australia he now runs a gym.</h3>','Look How The Crocodile Dundee Stars Aged Up','','inherit','closed','closed','','467-revision-v1','','','2016-08-31 03:38:25','2016-08-31 03:38:25','',467,'http://feelsyoung.com/467-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(477,1,'2016-08-31 03:43:47','2016-08-31 03:43:47','','David Gulpilil','','inherit','open','closed','','david-gulpilil-2','','','2016-08-31 03:43:47','2016-08-31 03:43:47','',467,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(478,1,'2016-08-31 03:43:49','2016-08-31 03:43:49','','EXCLUSIVE - WORLD RIGHTS','','inherit','open','closed','','exclusive-world-rights','','','2016-08-31 03:46:31','2016-08-31 03:46:31','',467,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/intro-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(479,1,'2016-08-31 03:43:50','2016-08-31 03:43:50','','John Meillon','','inherit','open','closed','','john-meillon-2','','','2016-08-31 03:43:50','2016-08-31 03:43:50','',467,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Meillon-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(480,1,'2016-08-31 03:43:52','2016-08-31 03:43:52','','Linda Kozlowski','','inheri