om/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INS-Vishal.jpg\" alt=\"INS Vishal\" width=\"728\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Agamemnon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The submarine is built keeping in mind a whale’s shape. It can store 3 months’ worth supply. The submarine will be added to the British Navy in 2020.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-497\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Agamemnon.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Agamemnon\" width=\"706\" height=\"530\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HMAS Canberra</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The warship has a sophisticated radar and weapon system. It has a superior missile system that can deflect missiles. 18 helicopters can land on this ship.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-495\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMAS-Canberra.jpg\" alt=\"HMAS Canberra\" width=\"728\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>CNS Linyi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>One of the most sophisticated ships owned by the Chinese Navy, the CNS Linyi has anti-submarine capability. It can jam any incoming missiles. It can carry both aircrafts and helicopters.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-491\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CNS-Linyi.jpg\" alt=\"CNS Linyi\" width=\"728\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>CNS Kunming</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The PLA Navy’s ship is aimed at countering piracy and other subversive activities. It has 6 torpedo tubes.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-490\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CNS-Kunming.jpg\" alt=\"CNS Kunming\" width=\"706\" height=\"530\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>INS Makar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Indian Navy uses this vessel to survey coast. It can also be used as a rescue vessel.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-500\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INS-Makar.jpg\" alt=\"INS Makar\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>French Frigate Forbin\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The sophisticated PAAM radar system made it an effective savior of other ships and aircraft carriers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-493\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-Frigate-Forbin.jpg\" alt=\"French Frigate Forbin\" width=\"728\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dixmude\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This assault ship used by the French navy can do wonders. Apart from its helicopter carrying capability, it can also accommodate one tank and many other vehicles.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-492\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dixmude.jpg\" alt=\"Dixmude\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Russian Corvette Boiky\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A light ship in nature, this corvette weighs only 2,100 tons. It has two torpedo tubes that can neutralize submarines.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-503\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Russian-Corvette-Boiky.jpg\" alt=\"Russian Corvette Boiky\" width=\"728\" height=\"435\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Anchorage\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It can carry up to 4 Sea Knight helicopters. The airframe missile launcher in it is a huge protection against any incoming object.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-510\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Anchorage.jpg\" alt=\"USS Anchorage\" width=\"728\" height=\"484\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The USS America\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The aircraft carrier was added to the US Navy not so long ago. It is known as a floating hospital.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-508\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-USS-America.jpg\" alt=\"The USS America\" width=\"728\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Gerald R Ford\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Named after the ex US president, it is one of the most advanced aircraft carriers in service. It can carry up to 72 fighter jets.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-513\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Gerald-R-Ford.jpg\" alt=\"USS Gerald R Ford\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USNS Spearhead\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a troop carrier that can transport a total of 312 troops to combat zones. It has few militaristic features.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-509\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USNS-Spearhead.jpg\" alt=\"USNS Spearhead\" width=\"728\" height=\"479\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Admiral Gorshkov\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Originally made by Russia, the aircraft is at the moment in Indian navy’s possession. It is equipped with the latest electronic warfare system.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-488\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Admiral-Gorshkov.jpg\" alt=\"Admiral Gorshkov\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Queen Elizabeth\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>HMS Queen Elizabeth is one of the biggest ships of the British navy. 40 aircraft can land on it. The weapon system is the most advanced in the world.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-499\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Queen-Elizabeth.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Queen Elizabeth\" width=\"728\" height=\"488\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Steregushchy (hull number 532)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This Russian made corvette weighs 2,200 tons. North African countries like Algeria recently showed interested in getting this type of warship.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-505\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Steregushchy-hull-number-532.jpg\" alt=\"Steregushchy (hull number 532)\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Enterprise (CVN-80)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This will be the fourth Ford class aircraft carrier to be added to the US Navy’s fleet.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-512\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Enterprise-CVN-80.jpg\" alt=\"USS Enterprise (CVN-80)\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The Juliet Marine Ghost\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is one of the fastest and stealthiest warships owned by the US navy. It is popular by its nickname ‘Ghost’.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-507\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Juliet-Marine-Ghost.jpg\" alt=\"The Juliet Marine Ghost\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Independence (LCS 2)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a type 45 air-defense defender. The warship is highly effective against any types of airborne threat.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-514\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Independence-LCS-2.jpg\" alt=\"USS Independence (LCS 2)\" width=\"728\" height=\"424\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Zumwalt\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Named after Admiral Zumwalt, it is one of the latest warships in the world. Its superior radar system can befool enemies.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-515\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Zumwalt.jpg\" alt=\"USS Zumwalt\" width=\"728\" height=\"455\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Coronado\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Since it was built keeping in mind coastal warfare necessities, the ship is not that big. But, it’s a stealthy and speedy vessel.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-511\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Coronado.jpg\" alt=\"USS Coronado\" width=\"728\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Defender\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a type 45 air-defense defender. The warship is highly effective against any types of airborne threat.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Defender.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Defender\" width=\"728\" height=\"480\" />','Warships That Can Be Proven Major Game Changers In Modern Warfare','','inherit','closed','closed','','486-revision-v1','','','2016-08-31 04:37:23','2016-08-31 04:37:23','',486,'http://feelsyoung.com/486-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(521,1,'2016-08-31 05:39:35','2016-08-31 05:39:35','<h3>Once they were flooded with cash. They had everything that a man can want in life: beautiful women, fast cars, and luxurious houses. But now they are at the verge of a total collapse.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>\r\nMichael Vick\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Michael had sponsorship deals with top brands like Nike and Coca-Cola. He was filed for bankruptcy for his alleged involvement in a dogfighting ring.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-541\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michael-Vick.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"637\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lawrence Taylor\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During his NFL career, Taylor piled up a fortune. He lost it all and was announced bankrupt after 5 years from his retirement.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lawrence-Taylor.jpg\" alt=\"Lawrence Taylor\" width=\"600\" height=\"601\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Bernie Kosar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After his retirement Kosar invested almost everything in real estate and saw it all blow away. To earn bread and butter he now works as a motivational speaker.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-526\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bernie-Kosar.jpg\" alt=\"Bernie Kosar\" width=\"700\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Warren Sapp\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Warren was known for his lavish lifestyle. He had a fascination for lion skins. No wonder he filed for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-551\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Warren-Sapp.jpg\" alt=\"Warren Sapp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Vince Young\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Once he had all the potentials to be the next NFL superstar. A shock injury became a fatal blow to his premature career. He eventually had to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-550\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Vince-Young.jpg\" alt=\"Vince Young\" width=\"711\" height=\"533\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Travis Henry\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Henry had to serve jail term for his involvement in a drug ring. Because of his enormous debt, his children didn’t receive child support.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-549\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Travis-Henry.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"592\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Tiki Barber\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Tiki was fired from NBC right after he was found to have been involved in an extramarital relationship with one of its interns.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-548\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tiki-Barber.jpg\" alt=\"Tiki Barber\" width=\"1200\" height=\"949\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Chris McAlister\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Misguided business investment cost it all for Chris who was once worth $55 million. He now lives with his parents.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-528\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Chris-McAlister.jpg\" alt=\"Chris McAlister\" width=\"700\" height=\"513\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Mark Brunell\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Mark tried to make profit out of the fast food and real estate sector. But he didn’t get what he invested in for and was forced to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-539\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Brunell.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Brunell\" width=\"560\" height=\"560\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Andre Rison\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Playing as a Wide Receiver, Andre earned $17 million during his NFL career. But soon after his retirement, he ran out of money.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-524\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Andre-Rison.jpg\" alt=\"Andre Rison\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dick Lane\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Dick earned a handsome amount from his NFL career. But, due to this uncontrolled lifestyle he soon fell in cash shortage.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dick-Lane.jpg\" alt=\"Dick Lane\" width=\"500\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Raghib Ismail\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ismail was quite unlucky. Unlike others, he didn’t spend money behind illicit things. Unfortunately all his business ventures fell apart.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-544\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Raghib-Ismail.jpeg\" alt=\"Raghib Ismail\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Deuce McAllister\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>His famous run on the field didn’t continue when it came to managing financial matters. He was announced bankrupt with $75 million in debt.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-532\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Deuce-McAllister.jpg\" alt=\"Deuce McAllister\" width=\"600\" height=\"456\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Luther Ellis\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Luther didn’t face any problems after his retirement until he lost it all in dwindling investment decisions.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-538\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Luther-Ellis.jpg\" alt=\"Luther Ellis\" width=\"500\" height=\"748\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Archie Griffin\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In college football, Archie was one of the biggest names. However, he could not continue that trend when he signed for the highest stage, the NFL.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-525\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Archie-Griffin.jpg\" alt=\"Archie Griffin\" width=\"867\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dermontti Dawson\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The NFL Hall of Fame member could not manage his money well and filed for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-531\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dermontti-Dawson.jpg\" alt=\"Dermontti Dawson\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>Dan Marino\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Dan lost $14 million when one of his investments severely failed. He now works as a football analyst.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-530\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dan-Marino.jpg\" alt=\"Dan Marino\" width=\"700\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Terrell Owens\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Terrell spent 11 years in the NFL and earned $70 million. Due to bad investment decisions he lost it all.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-547\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Terrell-Owens.jpg\" alt=\"Terrell Owens\" width=\"650\" height=\"752\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>JaMarcus Russell\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Russell was accused of possessing controlled drugs without prescription. He had to pay $200,000 as compensation.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-535\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/JaMarcus-Russell.jpg\" alt=\"JaMarcus Russell\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Ray Rice\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After being caught on camera knocking his fiancé up, Ray’s contract was immediately terminated.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-545\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ray-Rice.jpg\" alt=\"Ray Rice\" width=\"650\" height=\"441\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Johnny Unitas\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Unitas earned fame playing as a Quarterback. His business investment didn’t work out well, however.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-536\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Johnny-Unitas.jpg\" alt=\"Johnny Unitas\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Aaron Hernandez\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Back in 2012, Aaron got a $40m contract. But he is now serving life term for murder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-523\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Aaron-Hernandez.jpg\" alt=\"Aaron Hernandez\" width=\"1009\" height=\"800\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Mark Ingram, Sr.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Super Bowl XXV hero is now passing his days in uncertainties after being found to be involved in money laundering and tax evasion.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-540\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark_ingram.jpg\" alt=\"Mark_ingram\" width=\"635\" height=\"628\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>O.J. Simpson\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Murder, armed robbery, and kidnapping, all these major crimes doomed Simpson’s career.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-543\" sr