ze-full wp-image-555\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.-Outsourcing-His-Brand.jpg\" alt=\"1. Outsourcing His Brand\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Trump Vodka</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Back in 2007 he released the Trump Vodka, which was made in the Netherlands. It was a huge flop, though.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-556\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2.-Trump-Vodka.jpg\" alt=\"2. Trump Vodka\" width=\"740\" height=\"555\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. Three Wives</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump has so far taken the sacred oath three times. And, all of them were shrouded by controversy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-557\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3.-Three-Wives.jpg\" alt=\"3. Three Wives\" width=\"740\" height=\"464\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. ‘Violent Assault’ on Ex-Wife</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ivana Trump saw the crude side of Donald Trump than anyone else. The real estate tycoon assaulted her after undergoing a surgery by a plastic surgeon that she recommended.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-558\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/4.-Violent-Assault-on-Ex-Wife.jpg\" alt=\"4. Violent Assault on Ex Wife\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>5. Trump’s Yacht\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump had a 282 feet long yacht which he possessed until 1991, when he was forced to sell it to avoid bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-559\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6.-Trump-s-Yacht.jpg\" alt=\"6. Trump s Yacht\" width=\"740\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6. Never Tried His Own Vodka?\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump’s personal physician endorsed the real estate tycoon for the presidential race, telling, Trump would be the healthiest president ever. According to him, Trump never smoked or drank.\r\nThis image, however, tells a different story.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-560\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/7.-Never-Tried-His-Own-Vodka.png\" alt=\"7. Never Tried His Own Vodka\" width=\"720\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Trump Palace\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Everything ‘Trump’ has the word controversy attached to it; the Trump Palace located in Palm Beach is registered to an offshore company in Belize, considered as a tax haven for money launderers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12.-Trump-Tower-Tidbit.png\" alt=\"12. Trump Tower Tidbit\" width=\"655\" height=\"434\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>8. 67,000 New Followers Per Month\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Not everyone dislikes Trump. There are many who pay heed to his words. Proof? He gets 67,000 new followers every month.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-562\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/9.-67000-New-Followers-Per-Month.jpg\" alt=\"9. 67,000 New Followers Per Month\" width=\"740\" height=\"462\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>9. Pricey Mini Bar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A bottle of mineral water in the Trump International Hotel &amp; Tower in Chicago will cost you $25. This is the price you pay to be involved with “Trump”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-563\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/10.-Pricey-Mini-Bar.jpg\" alt=\"10. Pricey Mini Bar\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>10. Bankrupt Casinos\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A casino would fit to Trump’s image more than anything else. He, however, had 4 of them, all of which went bankrupt.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-564\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11.-Bankrupt-Casinos.jpg\" alt=\"11. Bankrupt Casinos\" width=\"600\" height=\"449\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>\r\n11. Trump Tower Tidbit\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The tallest residential structure of the world, located in Chicago, is a 98 story building.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-561\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/8.-Trump-Palace.jpg\" alt=\"8. Trump Palace\" width=\"740\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Trump Twitter\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Donald Trump is so active on Social Media. On average he tweets 12 times a day.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-566\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/13.-Trump-Twitter.jpg\" alt=\"13. Trump Twitter\" width=\"740\" height=\"430\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>13. Trump Loves Golf\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This guy has a fascination for golfing. No wonder he owns 16 golf courses in different countries.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-567\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14.-Trump-Loves-Golf.jpg\" alt=\"14. Trump Loves Golf\" width=\"740\" height=\"508\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>14. A Hollywood ‘Star’\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Many of us don’t know that Trump has had a Hollywood ‘Star’. He received it as recognition of his appearance in ‘The Apprentice’.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-568\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15.-A-Hollywood-Star.jpg\" alt=\"15. A Hollywood Star\" width=\"740\" height=\"437\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>15. Serious Real Estate\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anything real estates in Donald Trump’s hands become successful. When he was just 27, he owned 14,000 apartments throughout the states. To build his real estate empire, he took a $1 million loan.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.-Serious-Real-Estate.jpg\" alt=\"Modern apartment buildings in New Westminster, British Columbia, Canada.\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />','15 Funny Facts About Donald Trump','','publish','open','open','','15-funny-fac