N SUPPORTER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When she was young, she was a Republican supporter and activist.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-573\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ACTIVE-REPUBLICAN.jpg\" alt=\"ACTIVE REPUBLICAN\" width=\"740\" height=\"415\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>WHEN SHE MET HIM\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They came to know each other in Yale library. Before finally talking to each other, they exchanged glances.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-588\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/WHEN-HILLARY-MET-BILL.jpg\" alt=\"WHEN HILLARY MET BILL\" width=\"740\" height=\"1085\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>NOT INTERESTED IN POLITICS\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary never considered entering the political arena seriously. Rather, she wanted to be an astronaut or journalist.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-585\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NOT-INTO-POLITICS.jpg\" alt=\"NOT INTO POLITICS\" width=\"740\" height=\"740\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HILLARY EARNED MORE THAN BILL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>As the governor of Arkansas when Bill was making $35,000, Hillary was drawing $100,000 as salary from her law firm.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-580\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HILLARY-MADE-MORE-MONEY-THAN-BILL.jpg\" alt=\"HILLARY MADE MORE MONEY THAN BILL\" width=\"740\" height=\"590\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>YALE VS. HARVARD\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Had not she been discouraged by a Harvard professor, Hillary could have studied at the prestigious university. She instead joined Yale, which at that time had handful of female students.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-579\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HARVARD-V.-YALE.jpg\" alt=\"HARVARD V. YALE\" width=\"740\" height=\"411\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>TOUGH BAR EXAM\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary’s first bar exam taken in Washington D.C. was a failure. She later passed it from Arkansas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-577\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/FAILING-THE-BAR.jpg\" alt=\"FAILING THE BAR\" width=\"740\" height=\"508\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>NECKLACE COSTS ALMOST BILL\'S MONTHLY SALARY\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During Bill’s inauguration as the governor of Arkansas she wore a diamond necklace that cost $20,000.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-583\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NECKLACE-WORTH-ALMOST-BILLS-ENTIRE-SALARY.jpg\" alt=\"NECKLACE WORTH ALMOST BILL\'S ENTIRE SALARY\" width=\"740\" height=\"565\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HILLARY REFUSED BILL\'S PROPOSAL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After completing their study of law, Bill and Hillary went on a Euro trip. Bill ended up proposing Hillary there, but, was turned down instantly.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-581\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HILLARY-TURNED-BILL-DOWN.jpg\" alt=\"HILLARY TURNED BILL DOWN\" width=\"740\" height=\"501\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>THE WATERGATE SCANDAL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary took the job of advising the House Committee on Judiciary to deal with the Watergate scandal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-584\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NIXON-IMPEACHMENT.jpg\" alt=\"NIXON IMPEACHMENT\" width=\"740\" height=\"494\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>ANOTHER \'ELEANOR AND FRANKLIN\' SAGA\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In 2004 Bill revealed that they enjoy a relationship similar to that is of Eleanor and Franklin.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-576\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ELEANOR-AND-FRANKLIN.jpeg\" alt=\"ELEANOR AND FRANKLIN\" width=\"740\" height=\"384\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>RAT\'S A** CASE\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A canning company took the service of Hillary’s law firm to tackle a suit filed against it. Reportedly a piece of rat was found inside one of its cans. After winning the case she got the title Rat\'s Ass Case from her husband.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-587\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/RATS-ASS-CASE.jpg\" alt=\"RATS ASS CASE\" width=\"740\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>BIG FAMILY\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary wanted to raise a big family. She however abandoned that thought after knowing she has fertility issues.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-582\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/LARGE-FAMILY.jpg\" alt=\"LARGE FAMILY\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>AN INFLUENCIAL LAWYER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary was once named one the most powerful lawyers in the country by the National Law Journal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-586\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/POWERFUL-LAWYER.jpg\" alt=\"POWERFUL LAWYER\" width=\"740\" height=\"986\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>QUIZ SHOW WINNER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary was a regular participant in quiz show College Bowl. She also won a few times.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-575\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/COLLEGE-BOWL.jpg\" alt=\"COLLEGE BOWL\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>A YOUNG PHILANTHROPIST </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During her teen years she formed a babysitting club to look after the children of immigrants from neighboring Mexico.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-574\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/BABYSITTERS-CLUB.jpg\" alt=\"BABYSITTERS CLUB\" width=\"738\" height=\"572\" />','16 Lesser Known Facts About Hillary Clinton','','inherit','closed','closed','','571-revision-v1','','','2016-08-31 08:06:02','2016-08-31 08:06:02','',571,'http://feelsyoung.com/571-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(590,1,'2016-08-31 08:27:22','2016-08-31 08:27:22','<h2><strong>1. Unilever owns Ben &amp; Jerry’s, the popular sweetened frozen food maker.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-592\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"478\" height=\"334\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. 1.8 million dollars is Wal-Mart’s average profit per hour.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-593\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2-1.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"650\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. The purpose of Starbucks round tables is to make their customers feel less lonely.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-594\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3-1.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"650\" height=\"665\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. Almost 94% of the world population can recognize the Coca-Cola logo instantly.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-595\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/4-1.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"1280\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>5. Though Taco is a Mexican food, food chain Taco Bell was a huge flop in Mexico.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-596\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/5-1.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"660\" height=\"340\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6. Do you want to visit Mark Zuckerberg’s Facebook profile? Just add /4 after the Facebook URL.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-597\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"850\" height=\"565\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><stron