src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"615\" height=\"430\" />','16 Interesting Business Facts That Will Make You Go WOW','','inherit','closed','closed','','590-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 15:32:55','2016-09-06 15:32:55','',590,'http://feelsyoung.com/590-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(691,1,'2016-09-06 15:35:17','2016-09-06 15:35:17','<h3>Recent polls show that Hillary is ahead of Donald Trump, and this difference is increasing day by day. Can she be the first female president of the United States? Well, time will tell. For now, you can get to know these facts about Hillary.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>\r\nSENATOR AND FIRST LADY\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary made history by becoming the first first-lady to have been elected to the senate. She was elected from the New York constituency.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-578\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/FIRST-LADY-AND-SENATOR.jpg\" alt=\"FIRST LADY AND SENATOR\" width=\"740\" height=\"496\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>A REPUBLICAN SUPPORTER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When she was young, she was a Republican supporter and activist.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-573\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ACTIVE-REPUBLICAN.jpg\" alt=\"ACTIVE REPUBLICAN\" width=\"740\" height=\"415\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>WHEN SHE MET HIM\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They came to know each other in Yale library. Before finally talking to each other, they exchanged glances.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-588\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/WHEN-HILLARY-MET-BILL.jpg\" alt=\"WHEN HILLARY MET BILL\" width=\"740\" height=\"1085\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>NOT INTERESTED IN POLITICS\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary never considered entering the political arena seriously. Rather, she wanted to be an astronaut or journalist.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-585\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NOT-INTO-POLITICS.jpg\" alt=\"NOT INTO POLITICS\" width=\"740\" height=\"740\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HILLARY EARNED MORE THAN BILL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>As the governor of Arkansas when Bill was making $35,000, Hillary was drawing $100,000 as salary from her law firm.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-580\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HILLARY-MADE-MORE-MONEY-THAN-BILL.jpg\" alt=\"HILLARY MADE MORE MONEY THAN BILL\" width=\"740\" height=\"590\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>YALE VS. HARVARD\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Had not she been discouraged by a Harvard professor, Hillary could have studied at the prestigious university. She instead joined Yale, which at that time had handful of female students.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-579\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HARVARD-V.-YALE.jpg\" alt=\"HARVARD V. YALE\" width=\"740\" height=\"411\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>TOUGH BAR EXAM\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary’s first bar exam taken in Washington D.C. was a failure. She later passed it from Arkansas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-577\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/FAILING-THE-BAR.jpg\" alt=\"FAILING THE BAR\" width=\"740\" height=\"508\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>NECKLACE COSTS ALMOST BILL\'S MONTHLY SALARY\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During Bill’s inauguration as the governor of Arkansas she wore a diamond necklace that cost $20,000.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-583\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NECKLACE-WORTH-ALMOST-BILLS-ENTIRE-SALARY.jpg\" alt=\"NECKLACE WORTH ALMOST BILL\'S ENTIRE SALARY\" width=\"740\" height=\"565\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HILLARY REFUSED BILL\'S PROPOSAL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After completing their study of law, Bill and Hillary went on a Euro trip. Bill ended up proposing Hillary there, but, was turned down instantly.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-581\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HILLARY-TURNED-BILL-DOWN.jpg\" alt=\"HILLARY TURNED BILL DOWN\" width=\"740\" height=\"501\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>THE WATERGATE SCANDAL\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary took the job of advising the House Committee on Judiciary to deal with the Watergate scandal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-584\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/NIXON-IMPEACHMENT.jpg\" alt=\"NIXON IMPEACHMENT\" width=\"740\" height=\"494\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>ANOTHER \'ELEANOR AND FRANKLIN\' SAGA\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In 2004 Bill revealed that they enjoy a relationship similar to that is of Eleanor and Franklin.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-576\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/ELEANOR-AND-FRANKLIN.jpeg\" alt=\"ELEANOR AND FRANKLIN\" width=\"740\" height=\"384\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>RAT\'S A** CASE\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A canning company took the service of Hillary’s law firm to tackle a suit filed against it. Reportedly a piece of rat was found inside one of its cans. After winning the case she got the title Rat\'s Ass Case from her husband.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-587\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/RATS-ASS-CASE.jpg\" alt=\"RATS ASS CASE\" width=\"740\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>BIG FAMILY\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary wanted to raise a big family. She however abandoned that thought after knowing she has fertility issues.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-582\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/LARGE-FAMILY.jpg\" alt=\"LARGE FAMILY\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>AN INFLUENCIAL LAWYER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary was once named one the most powerful lawyers in the country by the National Law Journal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-586\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/POWERFUL-LAWYER.jpg\" alt=\"POWERFUL LAWYER\" width=\"740\" height=\"986\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>QUIZ SHOW WINNER\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Hillary was a regular participant in quiz show College Bowl. She also won a few times.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-575\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/COLLEGE-BOWL.jpg\" alt=\"COLLEGE BOWL\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>A YOUNG PHILANTHROPIST </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During her teen years she formed a babysitting club to look after the children of immigrants from neighboring Mexico.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-574\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/BABYSITTERS-CLUB.jpg\" alt=\"BABYSITTERS CLUB\" width=\"738\" height=\"572\" />','16 Lesser Known Facts About Hillary Clinton','','inherit','closed','closed','','571-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 15:35:17','2016-09-06 15:35:17','',571,'http://feelsyoung.com/571-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(692,1,'2016-09-06 15:58:01','2016-09-06 15:58:01','<h3>As soon as Donald Trump was declared as the Republican Party nominee for the upcoming presidential election, a thunderstorm had hit the US political scene. Mr. Trump’s eccentric character in many ways was responsible for an outcry. On many occasions he uttered a lot of things. Some of them are funny and others are disturbing. Here are some lesser known facts about Donald Trump.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>1. Outsourcing His Brand</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though Mr. Trump is a staunch supporter of ‘Made in America’, and though he regularly advocates policies barring countries like Mexico, China, and Bangladesh, from where major exports come from, he himself outsourced the clothing line for his Donald J. Trump brand to those same countries!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-555\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.-Outsourcing-His-Brand.jpg\" alt=\"1. Outsourcing His Brand\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Trump Vodka</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Back in 2007 he released the Trump Vodka, which was made in the Netherlands. It was a huge flop, though.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-556\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2.-Trump-Vodka.jpg\" alt=\"2. Trump Vodka\" width=\"740\" height=\"555\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. Three Wives</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump has so far taken the sacred oath three times. And, all of them were shrouded by controversy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-557\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3.-Three-Wives.jpg\" alt=\"3. Three Wives\" width=\"740\" height=\"464\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. ‘Violent Assault’ on Ex-Wife</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ivana Trump saw the crude side of Donald Trump than anyone else. The real estate tycoon assaulted her after undergoing a surgery by a plastic surgeon that she recommended.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-558\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/4.-Violent-Assault-on-Ex-Wife.jpg\" alt=\"4. Violent Assault on Ex Wife\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>5. Trump’s Yacht\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump had a 282 feet long yacht which he possessed until 1991, when he was forced to sell it to avoid bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-559\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6.-Trump-s-Yacht.jpg\" alt=\"6. Trump s Yacht\" width=\"740\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6. Never Tried His Own Vodka?\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Trump’s personal physician endorsed the real estate tycoon for the presidential race, telling, Trump would be the healthiest president ever. According to him, Trump never smoked or drank.\r\nThis image, however, tells a different story.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-560\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/7.-Never-Tried-His-Own-Vodka.png\" alt=\"7. Never Tried His Own Vodka\" width=\"720\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Trump Palace\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Everything ‘Trump’ has the word controversy attached to it; the Trump Palace located in Palm Beach is registered to an offshore company in Belize, considered as a tax haven for money launderers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12.-Trump-Tower-Tidbit.png\" alt=\"12. Trump Tower Tidbit\" width=\"655\" height=\"434\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>8. 67,000 New Followers Per Month\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Not everyone dislikes Trump. There are many who pay heed to his words. Proof? He gets 67,000 new followers every month.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-562\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/9.-67000-New-Followers-Per-Month.jpg\" alt=\"9. 67,000 New Followers Per Month\" width=\"740\" height=\"462\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>9. Pricey Mini Bar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A bottle of mineral water in the Trump International Hotel &amp; Tower in Chicago will cost you $25. This is the price you pay to be involved with “Trump”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-563\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/10.-Pricey-Mini-Bar.jpg\" alt=\"10. Pricey Mini Bar\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>10. Bankrupt Casinos\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A casino would fit to Trump’s image more than anything else. He, however, had 4 of them, all of which went bankrupt.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-564\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11.-Bankrupt-Casinos.jpg\" alt=\"11. Bankrupt Casinos\" width=\"600\" height=\"449\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>\r\n11. Trump Tower Tidbit\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The tallest residential structure of the world, located in Chicago, is a 98 story building.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-561\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/8.-Trump-Palace.jpg\" alt=\"8. Trump Palace\" width=\"740\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Trump Twitter\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Donald Trump is so active on Social Media. On average he tweets 12 times a day.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-566\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/13.-Trump-Twitter.jpg\" alt=\"13. Trump Twitter\" width=\"740\" height=\"430\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>13. Trump Loves Golf\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This guy has a fascination for golfing. No wonder he owns 16 golf courses in different countries.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-567\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14.-Trump-Loves-Golf.jpg\" alt=\"14. Trump Loves Golf\" width=\"740\" height=\"508\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>14. A Hollywood ‘Star’\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Many of us don’t know that Trump has had a Hollywood ‘Star’. He received it as recognition of his appearance in ‘The Apprentice’.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-568\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15.-A-Hollywood-Star.jpg\" alt=\"15. A Hollywood Star\" width=\"740\" height=\"437\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>15. Serious Real Estate\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anything real estates in Donald Trump’s hands become successful. When he was just 27, he owned 14,000 apartments throughout the states. To build his real estate empire, he took a $1 million loan.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-569\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.-Serious-Real-Estate.jpg\" alt=\"Modern apartment buildings in New Westminster, British Columbia, Canada.\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" />','15 Funny Facts About Donald Trump','','inherit','closed','closed','','554-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 15:58:01','2016-09-06 15:58:01','',554,'http://feelsyoung.com/554-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(693,1,'2016-09-06 16:00:23','2016-09-06 16:00:23','<h3>Once they were flooded with cash. They had everything that a man can want in life: beautiful women, fast cars, and luxurious houses. But now they are at the verge of a total collapse.</h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h2><strong>\nMichael Vick\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Michael had sponsorship deals with top brands like Nike and Coca-Cola. He was filed for bankruptcy for his alleged involvement in a dogfighting ring.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-541\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michael-Vick.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"637\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Lawrence Taylor\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>During his NFL career, Taylor piled up a fortune. He lost it all and was announced bankrupt after 5 years from his retirement.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lawrence-Taylor.jpg\" alt=\"Lawrence Taylor\" width=\"600\" height=\"601\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Bernie Kosar\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>After his retirement Kosar invested almost everything in real estate and saw it all blow away. To earn bread and butter he now works as a motivational speaker.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-526\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bernie-Kosar.jpg\" alt=\"Bernie Kosar\" width=\"700\" height=\"480\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Warren Sapp\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Warren was known for his lavish lifestyle. He had a fascination for lion skins. No wonder he filed for bankruptcy.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-551\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Warren-Sapp.jpg\" alt=\"Warren Sapp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Vince Young\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Once he had all the potentials to be the next NFL superstar. A shock injury became a fatal blow to his premature career. He eventually had to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-550\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Vince-Young.jpg\" alt=\"Vince Young\" width=\"711\" height=\"533\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Travis Henry\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Henry had to serve jail term for his involvement in a drug ring. Because of his enormous debt, his children didn’t receive child support.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-549\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Travis-Henry.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"592\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Tiki Barber\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Tiki was fired from NBC right after he was found to have been involved in an extramarital relationship with one of its interns.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-548\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tiki-Barber.jpg\" alt=\"Tiki Barber\" width=\"1200\" height=\"949\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Chris McAlister\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Misguided business investment cost it all for Chris who was once worth $55 million. He now lives with his parents.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-528\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Chris-McAlister.jpg\" alt=\"Chris McAlister\" width=\"700\" height=\"513\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Mark Brunell\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Mark tried to make profit out of the fast food and real estate sector. But he didn’t get what he invested in for and was forced to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-539\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Brunell.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Brunell\" width=\"560\" height=\"560\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Andre Rison\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Playing as a Wide Receiver, Andre earned $17 million during his NFL career. But soon after his retirement, he ran out of money.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-524\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Andre-Rison.jpg\" alt=\"Andre Rison\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Dick Lane\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Dick earned a handsome amount from his NFL career. But, due to this uncontrolled lifestyle he soon fell in cash shortage.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dick-Lane.jpg\" alt=\"Dick Lane\" width=\"500\" height=\"545\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Raghib Ismail\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Ismail was quite unlucky. Unlike others, he didn’t spend money behind illicit things. Unfortunately all his business ventures fell apart.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-544\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Raghib-Ismail.jpeg\" alt=\"Raghib Ismail\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Deuce McAllister\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>His famous run on the field didn’t continue when it came to managing financial matters. He was announced bankrupt with $75 million in debt.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-532\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Deuce-McAllister.jpg\" alt=\"Deuce McAllister\" width=\"600\" height=\"456\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Luther Ellis\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>Luther didn’t face any problems after his retirement until he lost it all in dwindling investment decisions.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-538\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Luther-Ellis.jpg\" alt=\"Luther Ellis\" width=\"500\" height=\"748\" />\n\n<h2><strong>Archie Griffin\n</strong></h2>\n<h3>In college football, Archie was one of the biggest names. However, he could not continue that trend when he signed for the highest stage, the NFL.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-525\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Archie-Griffin.jpg\" alt=\"Archie Griffin\" width=\"867\" height=\"600\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Dermontti Dawson\n</strong></h2>\n