losed','closed','','521-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 16:00:25','2016-09-06 16:00:25','',521,'http://feelsyoung.com/521-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(695,1,'2016-09-06 16:04:47','2016-09-06 16:04:47','<h3>Over the years we have seen a huge development in military hardware. Today’s weapons are more tactical, effective, and lethal. As a part of naval warfare, modern warships are developed in such a way that they can change the course of any war in no time. We gather here 28 most advanced warships that can win a naval conflict from nothing.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>HMCS Chicoutimi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The diesel powered submarine is owned by the Royal Canadian Navy. It has 6 submarine tubes, along with a very effective decoy system.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-496\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMCS-Chicoutimi.jpg\" alt=\"HMCS Chicoutimi\" width=\"728\" height=\"481\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HDMS Absalon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>One of the most sophisticated warships ever built, HDMS Absalon is used by the Royal Danish Navy. It is equipped with 7 heavy machineguns. Two helicopters can land on it at the same time.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-494\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HDMS-Absalon.jpg\" alt=\"HDMS Absalon\" width=\"728\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>SAS Mendi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Despite its heavy weight, the frigate has a marvelous speed of 30 knots. It has multiple radar systems to detect any upcoming enemies.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-504\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/SAS-Mendi.jpg\" alt=\"SAS Mendi\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>JDS Hyuga</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To counter Pyongyang’s bigger fleet, this ship was included in the Japanese Maritime Self-defense force about 7 years ago.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-502\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/JDS-Hyuga.jpg\" alt=\"JDS Hyuga\" width=\"728\" height=\"406\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>TCG Heybeliada</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though it is not a proper warship, it has advanced features like anti-aircraft system. The patrol vessel is known for its stealth capability.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-506\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/TCG-Heybeliada.jpg\" alt=\"TCG Heybeliada\" width=\"728\" height=\"403\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>BNS Riachuelo</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The 75 feet long submarine is one of the stealthiest in the world. It is run by electric power, and has 6 torpedo tubes.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-489\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/BNS-Riachuelo.jpg\" alt=\"BNS Riachuelo\" width=\"728\" height=\"484\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>INS Vishal</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The aircraft carrier will be added to the Indian Navy’s fleet in 2023. It can accommodate 1,400 crew members.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-501\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INS-Vishal.jpg\" alt=\"INS Vishal\" width=\"728\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Agamemnon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The submarine is built keeping in mind a whale’s shape. It can store 3 months’ worth supply. The submarine will be added to the British Navy in 2020.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-497\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Agamemnon.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Agamemnon\" width=\"706\" height=\"530\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HMAS Canberra</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The warship has a sophisticated radar and weapon system. It has a superior missile system that can deflect missiles. 18 helicopters can land on this ship.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-495\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMAS-Canberra.jpg\" alt=\"HMAS Canberra\" width=\"728\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>CNS Linyi</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>One of the most sophisticated ships owned by the Chinese Navy, the CNS Linyi has anti-submarine capability. It can jam any incoming missiles. It can carry both aircrafts and helicopters.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-491\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CNS-Linyi.jpg\" alt=\"CNS Linyi\" width=\"728\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>CNS Kunming</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The PLA Navy’s ship is aimed at countering piracy and other subversive activities. It has 6 torpedo tubes.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-490\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CNS-Kunming.jpg\" alt=\"CNS Kunming\" width=\"706\" height=\"530\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>INS Makar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Indian Navy uses this vessel to survey coast. It can also be used as a rescue vessel.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-500\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/INS-Makar.jpg\" alt=\"INS Makar\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>French Frigate Forbin\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The sophisticated PAAM radar system made it an effective savior of other ships and aircraft carriers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-493\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/French-Frigate-Forbin.jpg\" alt=\"French Frigate Forbin\" width=\"728\" height=\"486\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dixmude\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This assault ship used by the French navy can do wonders. Apart from its helicopter carrying capability, it can also accommodate one tank and many other vehicles.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-492\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dixmude.jpg\" alt=\"Dixmude\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Russian Corvette Boiky\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A light ship in nature, this corvette weighs only 2,100 tons. It has two torpedo tubes that can neutralize submarines.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-503\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Russian-Corvette-Boiky.jpg\" alt=\"Russian Corvette Boiky\" width=\"728\" height=\"435\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>USS Anchorage\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It can carry up to 4 Sea Knight helicopters. The airframe missile launcher in it is a huge protection against any incoming object.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-510\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Anchorage.jpg\" alt=\"USS Anchorage\" width=\"728\" height=\"484\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The USS America\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The aircraft carrier was added to the US Navy not so long ago. It is known as a floating hospital.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-508\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-USS-America.jpg\" alt=\"The USS America\" width=\"728\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Gerald R Ford\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Named after the ex US president, it is one of the most advanced aircraft carriers in service. It can carry up to 72 fighter jets.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-513\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Gerald-R-Ford.jpg\" alt=\"USS Gerald R Ford\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>USNS Spearhead\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a troop carrier that can transport a total of 312 troops to combat zones. It has few militaristic features.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-509\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USNS-Spearhead.jpg\" alt=\"USNS Spearhead\" width=\"728\" height=\"479\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Admiral Gorshkov\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Originally made by Russia, the aircraft is at the moment in Indian navy’s possession. It is equipped with the latest electronic warfare system.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-488\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Admiral-Gorshkov.jpg\" alt=\"Admiral Gorshkov\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Queen Elizabeth\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>HMS Queen Elizabeth is one of the biggest ships of the British navy. 40 aircraft can land on it. The weapon system is the most advanced in the world.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-499\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Queen-Elizabeth.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Queen Elizabeth\" width=\"728\" height=\"488\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Steregushchy (hull number 532)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This Russian made corvette weighs 2,200 tons. North African countries like Algeria recently showed interested in getting this type of warship.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-505\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Steregushchy-hull-number-532.jpg\" alt=\"Steregushchy (hull number 532)\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>USS Enterprise (CVN-80)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This will be the fourth Ford class aircraft carrier to be added to the US Navy’s fleet.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-512\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Enterprise-CVN-80.jpg\" alt=\"USS Enterprise (CVN-80)\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The Juliet Marine Ghost\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is one of the fastest and stealthiest warships owned by the US navy. It is popular by its nickname ‘Ghost’.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-507\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Juliet-Marine-Ghost.jpg\" alt=\"The Juliet Marine Ghost\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>USS Independence (LCS 2)\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a type 45 air-defense defender. The warship is highly effective against any types of airborne threat.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-514\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Independence-LCS-2.jpg\" alt=\"USS Independence (LCS 2)\" width=\"728\" height=\"424\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>USS Zumwalt\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Named after Admiral Zumwalt, it is one of the latest warships in the world. Its superior radar system can befool enemies.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-515\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Zumwalt.jpg\" alt=\"USS Zumwalt\" width=\"728\" height=\"455\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>USS Coronado\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Since it was built keeping in mind coastal warfare necessities, the ship is not that big. But, it’s a stealthy and speedy vessel.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-511\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/USS-Coronado.jpg\" alt=\"USS Coronado\" width=\"728\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>HMS Defender\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is a type 45 air-defense defender. The warship is highly effective against any types of airborne threat.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/HMS-Defender.jpg\" alt=\"HMS Defender\" width=\"728\" height=\"480\" />','Warships That Can Be Proven Major Game Changers In Modern Warfare','','inherit','closed','closed','','486-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 16:04:47','2016-09-06 16:04:47','',486,'http://feelsyoung.com/486-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(697,1,'2016-09-06 19:03:26','2016-09-06 19:03:26','<h3>It’s been long since The Crocodile Dundee was released. The movie series changed many people’s view of life. So, what happened to the famous cast? How do they look today? Let’s have a look.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>John Meillon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nMeillon portrayed the character of Dundee’s business partner. As recognition of his acting career, he received the OBE.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-470\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Meillon.jpg\" alt=\"John Meillon\" width=\"503\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nJohn Meillon died in 1989. The second movie in the franchise was released the previous year, where he played the same role as the first one. He was quite lucky to have escaped the third installment in the series, which is considered as the worst.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-479\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Meillon-1.jpg\" alt=\"John Meillon\" width=\"214\" height=\"317\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Mark Blum</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nPerhaps the least loved character in the movie, Mark played the character of Sue’s lover cum editor.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-472\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Blum.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Blum\" width=\"670\" height=\"345\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nMark gave more examples of his acting talent though his roles in ‘The Sopranos’ and ‘Frasier’.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-481\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Blum-1.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Blum\" width=\"454\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Reginald Veljohnson</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nRemember the famous Limo driver in the franchise? He was also a part of the ‘Die Hard 2’ cast.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-474\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Reginald-Veljohnson.jpg\" alt=\"Reginald Veljohnson\" width=\"750\" height=\"364\" />\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nIn his later appearances on TV shows and movies he played the role of a cop or other bossy figures.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-483\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Reginald-Veljohnson-1.jpg\" alt=\"Reginald Veljohnson\" width=\"440\" height=\"550\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Linda Kozlowski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nIn the movie she was often referred to as the apple of Dundee’s eye. No wonder they got married in real life. However, their marriage didn’t long last.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-471\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Linda-Kozlowski.jpg\" alt=\"Linda Kozlowski\" width=\"625\" height=\"417\" />\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nFar away from the limelight, she now motivates in her travel operation business located in Marrakesh.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-480\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Linda-Kozlowski-1.jpg\" alt=\"Look How The Crocodile Dundee Stars Aged Up\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>David Gulpilil</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nDavid was no central figure in the movie. The franchise however would not have been felt the same if he had been left out.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-469\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil.jpg\" alt=\"David Gulpilil\" width=\"466\" height=\"310\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nDavid was accused of felony and served time in jail for a year. He still continues with his acting career.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-477\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil-1.jpg\" alt=\"David Gulpilil\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Paul Hogan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nThe Crocodile Dundee franchise gave him both name and fame; so much so that he rejected offers for hit movies like “Ghost”. His devotion paid him well.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-473\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paul-Hogan.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Hogan\" width=\"750\" height=\"524\" />\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nHogan’s later life was not so enviable – he was accused of tax fraud. He now takes care of his son.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-482\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paul-Hogan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Hogan\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Steve Rackman</strong></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\r\n</span>\r\nHis character Donk was lucky enough to have kissed Dundee in the movie. Before being selected for the hit franchise, he was a professional wrestler.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-475\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Steve-Rackman.jpg\" alt=\"Steve Rackman\" width=\"401\" height=\"544\" />\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\r\n</span>\r\nSteve ended his career in a grandeur way by completing the trilogy. Back home in Australia he now runs a gym.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-484\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Steve-Rackman-1.jpg\" alt=\"Steve Rackman\" width=\"555\" height=\"411\" />','Look How The Crocodile Dundee Stars Aged Up','','inherit','closed','closed','','467-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 19:03:26','2016-09-06 19:03:26','',467,'http://feelsyoung.com/467-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(698,1,'2016-09-06 19:04:41','2016-09-06 19:04:41','<h3>They were once our favorite stars and were the most familiar faces on TV. Those who were children during the 80’s, still allot a special place to these stars. We, however, don’t see them as frequently as before. What happened to them? Some of them left the world of showbiz and now, spending their time in retirement. And the others are still dominating the sliver screen, as they did before.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>Ricky Schroder</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When he was just 12, he played the lead role in the famous TV show Silver Spoons.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-462\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ricky-Schroder.jpg\" alt=\"Ricky Schroder\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Ally Sheedy</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Brat Pack star began her journey with the 1983 hit: Bad Boys.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-440\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ally-Sheedy.jpg\" alt=\"Ally Sheedy\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Judd Nelson </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Judd set his mark with “The Breakfast Club”. Prior to that, he acted in Nikita.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-453\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Judd-Nelson.jpg\" alt=\"Judd Nelson\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Molly Ringwald</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The charming redhead gained fame for her role in “Sixteen Candles”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-459\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Molly-Ringwald.jpg\" alt=\"Molly Ringwald\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Andrew McCarthy</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Andrew got himself another contract with hit Brat Pack lineup in “Pretty in Pink”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-442\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Andrew-McCarthy.jpg\" alt=\"Andrew McCarthy\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Emilio Estevez</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You might not know but Emilio is actor Charlie Sheen’s elder brother. He worked with stars like Sean Penn, during the 80’s.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-449\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Emilio-Estevez.jpg\" alt=\"Emilio Estevez\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Madonna</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>If you ask an 80’s kid about his or her music preference, they are most likely to answer: Madonna.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-455\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Madonna.jpg\" alt=\"Madonna\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Anthony Michael Hall</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anthony got spotlight after appearing in hit comedy “National Lampoon’s Vacation”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-443\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Anthony-Michael-Hall.jpg\" alt=\"Anthony Michael Hall\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>George Michael</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>People still remember the English singer for hit tracks like Careless Whisper and Last Christmas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-450\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/George-Michael.jpg\" alt=\"George Michael\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Demi Moore</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Leaving behind her disappointment in school, Moore established herself as one of the most desirable actresses in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-447\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Demi-Moore.jpg\" alt=\"Demi Moore\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>John Cusack</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Cusack entered the world of showbiz with his enthralling performance in “Better Off Dead”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-452\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Cusack.jpg\" alt=\"John Cusack\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Alyssa Milano</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Alyssa got breakthrough with her performance in ABC sitcom “Who\'s the Boss?”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-441\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alyssa-Milano.jpg\" alt=\"Alyssa Milano\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Tom Cruise</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Cruise is still one of the big shots in Hollywood. Many of us don’t know that Cruise began his career with a minor role in the movie “The Outsiders”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-464\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tom-Cruise.jpg\" alt=\"Tom Cruise\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Rob Lowe</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Rob was also a part of “The Outsiders” cast along with Tom Cruise. He also appeared in Brat Pack.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-463\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Rob-Lowe.jpg\" alt=\"Rob Lowe\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Cyndi Lauper</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Her first album “She\'s So Unusual” was released in 1983. She eventually established herself as the pop sensation of the decade.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-445\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Cyndi-Lauper.jpg\" alt=\"Cyndi Lauper\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Kevin Bacon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>He became a household name after playing the character of Ren McCormack. Even today he is a regular face in Hollywood movies.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-454\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Kevin-Bacon.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Bacon\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Patrick Dempsey</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The actor became audience favorite after playing a nerdy character in “Can’t Buy Me Love”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-461\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Patrick-Dempsey.jpg\" alt=\"Patrick Dempsey\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Matthew Broderick</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Matthew set his footprint with his acting in “Ferris Bueller\'s Day Off”. He eventually made it to some of the biggest hits in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-457\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Matthew-Broderick.jpg\" alt=\"Matthew Broderick\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Matt Dillon</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Bad boy Matt Dillon took part in many 80’s flicks. He was one of the heartthrobs of the decade.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-456\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Matt-Dillon.jpg\" alt=\"Matt Dillon\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Michael J. Fox</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Canadian Michael J. Fox became known for his acting skills with his role in “Family Ties”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-458\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michael-J.-Fox.jpg\" alt=\"Michael J. Fox\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Mr. T</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anyone who grew up during the 80’s will go WOW if you asked them about “The A-Team”. Indeed the name Mr. T became synonymous with the hit show.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-460\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mr.-T.jpg\" alt=\"Mr. T\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Corey Feldman</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Corey commenced his acting career when he was just 3. He became popular for his performance in “The Goonies”.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-444\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Corey-Feldman.jpg\" alt=\"Corey Feldman\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Drew Barrymore</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Successful Hollywood actress Drew Barrymore appeared on television when she was just 11! Her first breakthrough came with E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-448\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Drew-Barrymore.jpg\" alt=\"Drew Barrymore\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Debbie Gibson</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Her hit single Foolish Beat hit the top of the Billboard soon after it was released; making her one of the youngest artists to achieve that feat.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-446\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Debbie-Gibson.jpg\" alt=\"Debbie Gibson\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" />','See How These Stars From The 80’s Aged UP','','inherit','closed','closed','','438-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 19:04:41','2016-09-06 19:04:41','',438,'http://feelsyoung.com/438-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(699,1,'2016-09-06 19:12:27','2016-09-06 19:12:27','<h3>Making a movie is not like just another task. It takes sheer devotion and toil of those who are involved. The process of making a movie goes through an intense examination to make the finished product as accurate as possible. Some mistakes however remain till the end, and don’t get noticed until someone points them out. Exactly that’s what we did!</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>Braveheart</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see the hero, William Wallace wearing kilts throughout the movie. But the thing is, kilts were not used in Scotland before 16th century, which is way later Wallace’s time.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-409\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Braveheart.jpg\" alt=\"Braveheart\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Aviator</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The movie was set in 1928. We see the protagonist ordering chocolate chip cookies in a scene, when in reality, the confectionery was not invented before 1930.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-425\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Aviator.png\" alt=\"The Aviator\" width=\"400\" height=\"204\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Django Unchained</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In almost every scene we see Django wearing cool sunglasses. The funny thing is, before 1929, sunglasses were only used for medical purposes.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-410\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Django-Unchained.jpg\" alt=\"Django Unchained (2012) Blu-ray Screenshot\" width=\"700\" height=\"288\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Titanic</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see Jack announcing that he and his father regularly went fishing on Lake Wissota. However, the lake was formed in 1917, five years after the Titanic sank!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-432\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Titanic.png\" alt=\"Titanic\" width=\"350\" height=\"293\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Forrest Gump</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In the movie, Forrest receives a letter of acknowledgement which dates back to 1975, when the company was yet to be publicly traded.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-411\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Forrest-Gump.jpg\" alt=\"Forrest Gump\" width=\"1000\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Panic Room </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Meg lights the propane to set the intruders on fire and takes shelter under the bed. In reality, they would have been burned as well, since propane is heavier than air.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-417\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Panic-Room.png\" alt=\"Panic Room\" width=\"350\" height=\"196\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Gladiator</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In the movie, the protagonist was named ‘The Spaniard’ upon his capture. But the origin of the word didn’t come into being until 14th century. The movie was set in 180.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-412\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Gladiator.jpg\" alt=\"The Gladiator\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Back to the Future</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The license plate reads: OUTATTIME, which is way over the limit for characters in California license plates!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-408\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Back-to-the-Future.png\" alt=\"Back to the Future\" width=\"1500\" height=\"843\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Independence Day</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see the Empire State Building located in the center of a street exploding in a cool way, but in reality the building is located on a corner.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-414\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Independence-Day.jpg\" alt=\"Independence Day\" width=\"500\" height=\"217\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The Goonies</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see the boy finding a 1973 baseball card in the dead body. The body however had been there since 1930.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-426\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Goonies.jpg\" alt=\"The Goonies\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Halloween</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The events of the movie were described as taking place in Illinois, whereas the street signs indicate that it was shot in California.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-413\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Halloween.png\" alt=\"Halloween\" width=\"400\" height=\"248\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Hurt Locker</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>One character says that the Iraqi with the video camera would post something on YouTube. But the video sharing site was not launched until 2005, whereas the events in the movie took place in 2004.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-428\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Hurt-Locker.jpg\" alt=\"The Hurt Locker\" width=\"477\" height=\"268\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Dr. Jones as an attempt to save his father’s book visits Berlin in 1938. But, the real book burning took place in 1933.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-415\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Last-Crusade.jpg\" alt=\"Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade\" width=\"361\" height=\"260\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Raiders of the Lost Ark</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In another Indiana Jones movie, the idol appears to be guarded by different traps. But there is a hole above which we can realize by seeing the sunlight passing through it!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-421\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Raiders-of-the-Lost-Ark.jpg\" alt=\"Raiders of the Lost Ark\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Malcolm X</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see Malcolm asking someone to call 911. In reality, the emergency service was introduced 3 years later after his death.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-416\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Malcolm-X.jpg\" alt=\"Malcolm X\" width=\"400\" height=\"299\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Patriot</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see the character of Mel Gibson as a father of many children. The movie starts at the beginning of the Revolutionary war which ends 5 years later. But at the end of the movie we see the children as same as they were at the very beginning.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-429\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Patriot.jpg\" alt=\"The Patriot,\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Pirates of the Caribbean</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see captain Barbossa holding a Granny Smith apple, a variety which was not originated before 1868. The setting of the movie was way before that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-419\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Pirates-of-the-Caribbean.jpg\" alt=\"Pirates of the Caribbean\" width=\"700\" height=\"302\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Public Enemies</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In the movie, the murders of Nelson and Floyd take place before that is of Dillinger’s. But in reality, both of them lived longer than Dillinger.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-420\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Public-Enemies.jpg\" alt=\"Public Enemies\" width=\"673\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Saving Private Ryan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see Captain Miller leaning against a motorcycle after being shot. But the type of motorcycle was not manufactured before 1963, which is way after the year in which the movie’s events took place.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-423\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Saving-Private-Ryan.jpg\" alt=\"Saving Private Ryan\" width=\"720\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Green Mile</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In the movie, we see the execution of John Coffey taking place in Louisiana in 1935. But, the state introduced electric chair in 1940.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-427\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Green-Mile.jpg\" alt=\"The Green Mile\" width=\"638\" height=\"388\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The Shawshank Redemption</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Andy Dufresne used a One Million Years B.C. poster to cover the hole he dug. He eventually made off through it in 1966. However, One Million Years B.C. was released in 1967.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-430\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Shawshank-Redemption.jpg\" alt=\"The Shawshank Redemption\" width=\"500\" height=\"639\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Sherlock Holmes</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The famous sewer chase scene starts under the parliament and ends on the top of Tower Bridge. These two places are located at a distance no less than 2 miles from each other.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-424\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sherlock-Holmes.png\" alt=\"Sherlock Holmes\" width=\"380\" height=\"212\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Sound of Music</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Von Trapp family tries to get outside Salzburg to reach Switzerland, a neutral country during WWII. But outside Salzburg, Austria has borders with Germany, not Switzerland.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-431\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-Sound-of-Music.png\" alt=\"The Sound of Music\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Robin’s companion Azeem gives him a telescope. The setting of the movie indicates that it was set in 1194, way before the telescope was invented by Hans Lippershey in 1608.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-422\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Robin-Hood.jpg\" alt=\"Robin Hood\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Pirates of the Caribbean: At World\'s End</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We see the events taking place in Singapore. But in reality Singapore didn’t exist then. It was founded in 1819.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-418\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Pirates-of-the-Caribbean-At-Worlds-End.jpg\" alt=\"Pirates of the Caribbean At World\'s End\" width=\"1502\" height=\"1000\" />','25 Great Movie Mistakes That We Just Can\'t Forget','','inherit','closed','closed','','390-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 19:12:27','2016-09-06 19:12:27','',390,'http://feelsyoung.com/390-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(700,1,'2016-09-06 19:14:50','2016-09-06 19:14:50','<h3>In the recent years, female soccer players are rippling the world of sports with their skills and tactic; so much so that, today, they are not so far behind their male counterparts. Some of them have a glamorous presence in and outside the field.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>Amanda Ilestedt (Sweden)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Swedish defender is known for her tactical skills. She plays for Damallsvenskan club FC Rosengård in the domestic arena.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-359\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Amanda-Ilestedt-Sweden.jpg\" alt=\"Amanda Ilestedt (Sweden)\" width=\"830\" height=\"552\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Amandine Henry (France)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The French international plays in the defensive midfield position. She won the Bronze Ball Award in a world cup.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-386\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Amandine-Henry-France-1.jpg\" alt=\"Amandine Henry (France)\" width=\"600\" height=\"814\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Angela Christ (Netherlands)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Dutch footballer is the Netherlands’ last line of defense under the crossbar.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-361\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Angela-Christ-Netherlands.jpg\" alt=\"Angela Christ (Netherlands)\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Anna Green (New Zealand)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The kiwi defender is someone to keep an eye on. She represented her country in the Beijing Olympics.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-362\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Anna-Green-New-Zealand.jpg\" alt=\"Anna Green (New Zealand)\" width=\"650\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Anouk Hoogendijk (Netherlands)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anouk Hoogendijk plays for top Dutch side Ajax. Her primary position is the midfield.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-363\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Anouk-Hoogendijk-Netherlands.jpg\" alt=\"Anouk Hoogendijk (Netherlands)\" width=\"650\" height=\"487\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Christen Press (USA)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Christen was a part of the Rio Olympics team. She is famous for her athletic skills.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-364\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Christen-Press-USA.jpg\" alt=\"Christen Press (USA)\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Alex Morgan (USA)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Portland Thorn Forward represented her country in highest levels like the Olympics and the World Cup.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-357\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alex-Morgan-USA.jpg\" alt=\"Alex Morgan (USA)\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" />\r\n\r\n<h2> <strong>Lauren Sesselmann (Canada)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Houston Dash defender won an Olympic bronze for her country. By the way, she was born in America.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-378\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lauren-Sesselmann-1.jpg\" alt=\"Lauren Sesselmann\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" />\r\n<h2>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Daniela Cruz (Costa Rica)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Defender Daniela Cruz represents Costa Rica in the international arena.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-366\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Daniela-Cruz-Costa-Rica.jpg\" alt=\"Daniela Cruz (Costa Rica)\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Erika Cristiano dos Santos (Brazil)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Erika won silver medal for her country playing in the Beijing Olympics.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-367\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Erika-Cristiano-dos-Santos-Brazil.jpg\" alt=\"Erika Cristiano dos Santos (Brazil)\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Erin Nayler (New Zealand)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In the international level she is New Zealand’s proven goalkeeper. Besides, she also competes in Association football.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-368\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Erin-Nayler-New-Zealand.jpg\" alt=\"Erin Nayler (New Zealand)\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Florijana Ismaili (Switzerland)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In club level Florijana plays in Switzerland’s Nationalliga A. She plays both as a forward and midfielder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-369\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Florijana-Ismaili-Switzerland.jpg\" alt=\"Florijana Ismaili (Switzerland)\" width=\"500\" height=\"763\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2> <strong>Alexia Putellas (Spain)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Playing for FC Barcelona, Alexia has already won 5 titles in total. In 2013, she scored a magnificent goal that made her famous.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-358\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Alexia-Putellas.jpg\" alt=\"Alexia Putellas\" width=\"500\" height=\"294\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Hope Solo (USA)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Playing for her nation, Hope won the Olympic gold medal twice. She is a goalkeeper.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-370\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Hope-Solo-USA.jpg\" alt=\"Hope Solo (USA)\" width=\"800\" height=\"787\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Jessica Landstrom (Sweden)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Jessica played for the Swedish national side both in the Olympics and the World cup.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-371\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Jessica-Landstrom-Sweden.jpg\" alt=\"Jessica Landstrom (Sweden)\" width=\"650\" height=\"843\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Julia Simic (Germany)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Apart from playing good football Julia is also known for her modeling skills. She posed for the German edition of Playboy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-372\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Julia-Simic-Germany.jpg\" alt=\"Julia Simic (Germany)\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Julie Johnston (USA)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Julie plays as a defender for Chicago Red Stars and the US national women’s soccer team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-373\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Julie-Johnston-USA.jpg\" alt=\"Julie Johnston (USA)\" width=\"736\" height=\"414\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Kaylyn Kyle (Canada)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Born in Saskatoon, Kaylyn is an effective playmaker in the midfield position.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-374\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Kaylyn-Kyle-Canada.jpg\" alt=\"Kaylyn Kyle (Canada)\" width=\"800\" height=\"647\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Kosovare Asllani (Sweden)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Swedish forward Kosovare plays club football in French Division 1 Féminine.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-375\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Kosovare-Asllani-Sweden.jpg\" alt=\"Kosovare Asllani (Sweden)\" width=\"400\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Toni Duggan (England)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The English winger plays as a winger for Manchester City, a top side in England.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-385\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Toni-Duggan-England.jpg\" alt=\"Toni Duggan (England)\" width=\"736\" height=\"441\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tatiana Ariza (Colombia)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Colombian midfield maestro Tatiana is an integral part of the national team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-384\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tatiana-Ariza-Colombia.jpg\" alt=\"Tatiana Ariza (Colombia)\" width=\"620\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lara Dickenmann (Switzerland)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A versatile footballer she is, Lara can cover both the midfield and defense.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-376\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lara-Dickenmann-Switzerland.jpg\" alt=\"Lara Dickenmann (Switzerland)\" width=\"778\" height=\"937\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Laure Boulleau (France)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is said that without Laure the French defense is unfulfilled. She plays for French club Paris Saint-Germain.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-377\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Laure-Boulleau-France.jpg\" alt=\"Laure Boulleau (France)\" width=\"700\" height=\"932\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Adriana Leon (Canada)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Adriana came into spotlight when she was selected for the U-20 team. She is now a member of the regular team.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Adriana-Leon-Canada.jpeg\" alt=\"Adriana Leon (Canada)\" width=\"500\" height=\"436\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Louisa Necib (France)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Considered as one of the best playmakers in the French side, Louisa has all the potentials to be one of the greatest footballers the world has ever known.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-379\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Louisa-Necib-France.jpg\" alt=\"Louisa Necib (France)\" width=\"960\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Maria Coto (Costa Rica)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>19 years old Maria Coto is relatively new in the international stage. She is however maturing up quickly.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-380\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Maria-Coto-Costa-Rica.jpg\" alt=\"Maria Coto (Costa Rica)\" width=\"638\" height=\"380\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Melanie Leupolz (Germany)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Melanie made her presence known to the world during her appearance in the U-17 World Cup. She is primarily a midfielder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-381\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Melanie-Leupolz-Germany.jpg\" alt=\"Melanie Leupolz (Germany)\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Natalie Vinti (Mexico)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though she was born in in the states, Natalie plays for her parents’ country, Mexico, in the international stage.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-382\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Natalie-Vinti-Mexico.jpg\" alt=\"Natalie Vinti (Mexico)\" width=\"600\" height=\"777\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Olivia Schough (Sweden)</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In this year’s Rio Olympics, Olivia won Silver medal for her country. She played a great role in bringing her team to the final.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-383\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Olivia-Schough.jpg\" alt=\"Olivia Schough\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Claire Lavogez (France)</strong></h2>\r\n21 year old Claire plays for Olympique Lyon as a midfielder. She is considered as one of the aspirant stars in the French national side.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-365\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Claire-Lavogez-France.jpg\" alt=\"Claire Lavogez (France)\" width=\"850\" height=\"565\" />','30 Hottest Female Soccer Players In The World','','inherit','closed','closed','','354-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 19:14:50','2016-09-06 19:14:50','',354,'http://feelsyoung.com/354-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (701,1,'2016-10-06 17:41:27','2016-10-06 17:41:27','<h3>Maybe you are at the turning point of life where you have started feeling the vibe of hitting the 35 year mark. This is considered as the time of life where you need to settle down. So, a change in everything is inevitable. Every age has its pros and cons. If you are a middle-aged woman, you should avoid wearing a few things that would not suit your personality and look, as they did before.</h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h2><strong>25. Costume Shoes</strong></h2>\n<h3>We all gave up to our urge to get a pair of costume shoes one time or another. But if you are around 40, you should not be wearing those for comfortability’s sake.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Costume-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"Costume shoes\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>24. Bedazzled Anything</strong></h2>\n<h3>The bedazzled trend began about 16 years ago. Now it is considered as one of the biggest fashion flops. Unless you are in your early teen, you should not be trying them.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bedazzled-anything.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>23. Blue Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\n<h3>To be honest, no matter how old are you, you should avoid wearing them for good.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Blue-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Eyeshadow\" width=\"440\" height=\"329\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>22. Victoria\'s Secret PINK</strong></h2>\n<h3>Pink is something predetermined for teens. Don’t harass yourself when you are in your 30s.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/21.-Victorias-Secret-PINK.jpg\" alt=\"Victoria\'s Pink\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>21. Leopard Print</strong></h2>\n<h3>Unless you want to do something extraordinary, you should reconsider your decision. At the end of the day nobody wants to end up getting a title what they are not.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-329\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/20.-Leopard-Print.jpg\" alt=\"20. Leopard Print\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>20. Sparkly Pants</strong></h2>\n<h3>Don’t make your pants a place to compete with the sun; believe me, they look worse than you can imagine.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-328\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/19.-Sparkly-Pants.jpg\" alt=\"19. Sparkly Pants\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>19. Oversized Sunglasses </strong></h2>\n<h3>This is one of those things allotted for young people, only. Unless you don’t care about your personality, you should give them up for good.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/18.-Oversized-Sunglasses.jpg\" alt=\"18. Oversized Sunglasses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>18. Crop Tops &amp; Hotpants</strong></h2>\n<h3>When you are more than fit, you can flaunt that beautiful body of yours. But, you should not be wearing crop tops and hotpants at an age when a fat belly can distract others and be a mismatch for your personality.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-335\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/crop-tops-and-hotpants.jpg\" alt=\"crop tops and hotpants\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>17. Non-matching Socks</strong></h2>\n<h3>Your socks often say who you are. Be careful about that.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-326\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/17.-Non-matching-Socks.jpg\" alt=\"17. Non-matching Socks\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>16. Hoop Earrings</strong></h2>\n<h3>They are more suitable for girls who are attending high school. Get yourself some mature stuff.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-325\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.-Hoop-Earrings.jpg\" alt=\"16. Hoop Earrings\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>15. Furry Boots</strong></h2>\n<h3>“Only for teenagers” – doesn’t that say it all! You would regret wearing them.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-324\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15.-Furry-Boots.jpg\" alt=\"15. Furry Boots\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>14. Furry Anything</strong></h2>\n<h3>Anything furry has never been a great choice to look age appropriate. They will just add up to your misery!</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-323\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14.-Furry-Anything.jpg\" alt=\"14. Furry Anything\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>13. Tube Tops</strong></h2>\n<h3>Cameron Diaz recently announced that she is not going to wear them anymore. So, why do you bother?</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-348\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tube-Tops.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Tops\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" />\n<h2><strong>12. Short Dresses</strong></h2>\n<h3>You have other ways to look sexy. Don’t bare it all to attract people.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-321\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12.-Short-Dresses.jpg\" alt=\"12. Short Dresses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n<h2><strong>11. Mini-Skirts</strong></h2>\n<h3>“Know thyself”. Remember, you can’t always mix it up.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-320\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11.-Mini-Skirts.jpg\" alt=\"11. Mini-Skirts\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>10. Woman Overalls</strong></h2>\n<h3>Do you work at a farm? If not, help yourself.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-351\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Woman-Overalls.jpg\" alt=\"Woman Overalls\" width=\"570\" height=\"570\" />\n<h2><strong>9. Anything Showing Excessive Cleavage</strong></h2>\n<h3>A mature woman should never flaunt too much. It makes her look vulnerable and helpless.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Showing-Excessive-Cleavage.jpg\" alt=\"Showing Excessive Cleavage\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" />\n<h2><strong>8. American Eagle</strong></h2>\n<h3>They have cool, fitting jeans. But they are no longer for you.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-349\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/w926-ae-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-jeans-size-0-short-womens-jeans-815d30d5689245458a25f910b1e30c84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>7. Booty Shorts</strong></h2>\n<h3>To be honest, I am yet to find out at what age you can wear them!</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-345\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Booty-Shorts.jpg\" alt=\"Booty Shorts\" width=\"564\" height=\"564\" />\n<h2><strong>6. Old Sneakers</strong></h2>\n<h3>Rundown tennis shoes are not for you. You deserve better than that.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-316\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6.-Old-Sneakers.png\" alt=\"6. Old Sneakers\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n<h2><strong>5. Cheap Bras</strong></h2>\n<h3>Don’t deprive your boobies of some quality stuff. They are not young anymore and deserve something more comfortable.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-315\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/5.-Cheap-Bras.jpg\" alt=\"5. Cheap Bras\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>4. Glitter Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\n<h3>Glitter should be put on things that need to sparkle. It’s not the other way around.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-347\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Glitter-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Glitter Eyeshadow\" width=\"853\" height=\"563\" />\n<h2><strong>3. Platform Flip-Flops</strong></h2>\n<h3>Nobody should wear them. They are neither cool, nor sexy.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-313\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3.-Platform-Flip-Flops.jpg\" alt=\"3. Platform Flip-Flops\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n<h2><strong>2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch</strong></h2>\n<h3>Can you even fit yourself in them? I don’t think so.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-312\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2.-Abercrombie-Fitch.jpg\" alt=\"2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>1. Scrunchies</strong></h2>\n<h3>Don’t look like someone who has no time to do her hair. Your hair is a part and parcel of your personality.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-311\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.-Scrunchies.jpg\" alt=\"1. Scrunchies\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />','25 Things That Middle-Aged Women Should Not Wear','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-autosave-v1','','','2016-10-06 17:41:27','2016-10-06 17:41:27','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/287-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(702,1,'2016-09-06 19:30:10','2016-09-06 19:30:10','<h3>Maybe you are at the turning point of life where you have started feeling the vibe of hitting the 35 year mark. This is considered as the time of life where you need to settle down. So, a change in everything is inevitable. Every age has its pros and cons. If you are a middle-aged woman, you should avoid wearing a few things that would not suit your personality and look, as they did before.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>25. Costume Shoes</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We all gave up to our urge to get a pair of costume shoes one time or another. But if you are around 40, you should not be wearing those for comfortability’s sake.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-346\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Costume-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"Costume shoes\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>24. Bedazzled Anything</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The bedazzled trend began about 16 years ago. Now it is considered as one of the biggest fashion flops. Unless you are in your early teen, you should not be trying them.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bedazzled-anything.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>23. Blue Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To be honest, no matter how old are you, you should avoid wearing them for good.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Blue-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Eyeshadow\" width=\"440\" height=\"329\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>22. Victoria\'s Secret PINK</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Pink is something predetermined for teens. Don’t harass yourself when you are in your 30s.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/21.-Victorias-Secret-PINK.jpg\" alt=\"Victoria\'s Pink\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>21. Leopard Print</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Unless you want to do something extraordinary, you should reconsider your decision. At the end of the day nobody wants to end up getting a title what they are not.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-329\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/20.-Leopard-Print.jpg\" alt=\"20. Leopard Print\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>20. Sparkly Pants</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t make your pants a place to compete with the sun; believe me, they look worse than you can imagine.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-328\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/19.-Sparkly-Pants.jpg\" alt=\"19. Sparkly Pants\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>19. Oversized Sunglasses </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is one of those things allotted for young people, only. Unless you don’t care about your personality, you should give them up for good.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/18.-Oversized-Sunglasses.jpg\" alt=\"18. Oversized Sunglasses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>18. Crop Tops &amp; Hotpants</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When you are more than fit, you can flaunt that beautiful body of yours. But, you should not be wearing crop tops and hotpants at an age when a fat belly can distract others and be a mismatch for your personality.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-335\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/crop-tops-and-hotpants.jpg\" alt=\"crop tops and hotpants\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>17. Non-matching Socks</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Your socks often say who you are. Be careful about that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-326\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/17.-Non-matching-Socks.jpg\" alt=\"17. Non-matching Socks\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>16. Hoop Earrings</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They are more suitable for girls who are attending high school. Get yourself some mature stuff.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-325\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16.-Hoop-Earrings.jpg\" alt=\"16. Hoop Earrings\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>15. Furry Boots</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>“Only for teenagers” – doesn’t that say it all! You would regret wearing them.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-324\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15.-Furry-Boots.jpg\" alt=\"15. Furry Boots\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>14. Furry Anything</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Anything furry has never been a great choice to look age appropriate. They will just add up to your misery!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-323\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14.-Furry-Anything.jpg\" alt=\"14. Furry Anything\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>13. Tube Tops</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Cameron Diaz recently announced that she is not going to wear them anymore. So, why do you bother?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-348\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tube-Tops.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Tops\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>12. Short Dresses</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You have other ways to look sexy. Don’t bare it all to attract people.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-321\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12.-Short-Dresses.jpg\" alt=\"12. Short Dresses\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>11. Mini-Skirts</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>“Know thyself”. Remember, you can’t always mix it up.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-320\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11.-Mini-Skirts.jpg\" alt=\"11. Mini-Skirts\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Woman Overalls</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Do you work at a farm? If not, help yourself.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-351\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Woman-Overalls.jpg\" alt=\"Woman Overalls\" width=\"570\" height=\"570\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>9. Anything Showing Excessive Cleavage</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A mature woman should never flaunt too much. It makes her look vulnerable and helpless.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Showing-Excessive-Cleavage.jpg\" alt=\"Showing Excessive Cleavage\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>8. American Eagle</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>They have cool, fitting jeans. But they are no longer for you.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-349\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/w926-ae-american-eagle-skinny-dark-wash-jeans-size-0-short-womens-jeans-815d30d5689245458a25f910b1e30c84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Booty Shorts</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>To be honest, I am yet to find out at what age you can wear them!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-345\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Booty-Shorts.jpg\" alt=\"Booty Shorts\" width=\"564\" height=\"564\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6. Old Sneakers</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Rundown tennis shoes are not for you. You deserve better than that.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-316\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6.-Old-Sneakers.png\" alt=\"6. Old Sneakers\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>5. Cheap Bras</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t deprive your boobies of some quality stuff. They are not young anymore and deserve something more comfortable.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-315\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/5.-Cheap-Bras.jpg\" alt=\"5. Cheap Bras\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. Glitter Eyeshadow</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Glitter should be put on things that need to sparkle. It’s not the other way around.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-347\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Glitter-Eyeshadow.jpg\" alt=\"Glitter Eyeshadow\" width=\"853\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. Platform Flip-Flops</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Nobody should wear them. They are neither cool, nor sexy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-313\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3.-Platform-Flip-Flops.jpg\" alt=\"3. Platform Flip-Flops\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Can you even fit yourself in them? I don’t think so.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-312\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2.-Abercrombie-Fitch.jpg\" alt=\"2. Abercrombie &amp; Fitch\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>1. Scrunchies</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Don’t look like someone who has no time to do her hair. Your hair is a part and parcel of your personality.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-311\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1.-Scrunchies.jpg\" alt=\"1. Scrunchies\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n\r\n','25 Things That Middle-Aged Women Should Not Wear','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-revision-v1','','','2016-09-06 19:30:10','2016-09-06 19:30:10','',287,'http://feelsyoung.com/287-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(703,1,'2016-09-06 19:38:33','2016-09-06 19:38:33','<h3>With new threats popping up every day, army of a country plays the most crucial role in saving sovereignty and the population of a country from external and internal threats. A powerful army doesn’t always necessarily need to be huge, if it can make advances in other fields like cyber warfare and modern technology. Often building on tactical ability could be proven more effective than raising an army with huge firepower.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>30. Portugal</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h3>The Portuguese army’s golden days lie in its colonial past when the country ruled many African countries. Today it might not have the same might as it had before, but it still has an army that is superior to many other nations’.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-226\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Portugal.jpg\" alt=\"Portugal\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" />\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2><strong> 29. South Africa</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>There was a time when the South African army was used as a tool to oppress its own people. But after the end of the apartheid regime, the country has rebuilt its army and established it as a protector of the people.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-304\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/South_African_Army.jpg\" alt=\"South_African_Army\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>28. Malaysia</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Despite having a modern and well-equipped military, the Malaysians have a neutral policy to deal with major conflicts. The country’s army is however playing a pivotal role in peacekeeping missions.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-219 size-full\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/malaysian.jpg\" alt=\"malaysian\" width=\"568\" height=\"390\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>27. Norway</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You might be frowning to see the name of the country where Nobel peace prize is given. The Norwegian army is one of the most skilled in the world.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-222 \" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Norway.jpg\" alt=\"Norway\" width=\"612\" height=\"408\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>26. Singapore </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A tiny city state like Singapore always has different security concerns. The country’s leaders gave the duty to build their army to the Israelis. The result? Singapore has one of the most professional armies in the South East Asian region.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Singapore.jpg\" alt=\"Singapore\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>25. North Korea</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After the fall of the Soviet Union the authoritarian country found itself friendless. To tackle its neighbor in the South, the country has never stopped developing nuclear weapons that empower the army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-221\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/North-Korea.jpg\" alt=\"North Korea\" width=\"750\" height=\"406\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>24. Mexico</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Mexican army played a vital role in helping the government and local administration in containing drug related violence. Thanks to the Mexican army, the law and order situation in that country is much better, if not the best.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mexico.jpg\" alt=\"Mexico\" width=\"640\" height=\"395\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>23. The Netherlands </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Dutch army was harassed in the hands of the Nazis during WWII. After the war, the country worked hard on building a reliable army to defend its territories.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-301\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dutch-army.jpg\" alt=\"Dutch-army\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>22. Sweden </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When you have border with a country that boasts one of the biggest armies in the world, there is no way to take the matter of defense lightly. The Swedes are also prominent for making high-end military hardware.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-231\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Sweden-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Sweden\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>21. Switzerland</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though Switzerland always maintains neutrality, in this ever changing global scenario there is no alternative to having a decent military. And the Swiss have it.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Switzerland1.jpg\" alt=\"Switzerland1\" width=\"800\" height=\"505\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>20. Syria</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Syrian army was one of the strongest in the Middle East, before all hell broke loose. Their presence in Lebanon was a major headache for the Israelis.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-305\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Syrian-army.jpg\" alt=\"Syrian army\" width=\"669\" height=\"377\" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>19. Iran</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Years of sanctions slapped by the world could not stop the Iranians from building a strong army. In today’s major regional conflicts Iranian presence shows this clearly.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Iran.jpg\" alt=\"Iran\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>18. Australia </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though Australia is a huge country, the army is relatively small. But it doesn’t mean that it is weak.</h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-206\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Australia.jpg\" alt=\"Australia\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>17. Indonesia</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In all fields, Indonesians are open to everything west. Through vigorous cooperation with major Western military powers, the island nation has formed a strong army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Indonesian.jpg\" alt=\"Indonesian\" width=\"736\" height=\"572\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>16. Poland </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Poland has one of the finest armies in Eastern Europe. With US logistic support and training the Polish army is now able to give any intruder a big fight.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-303\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Polish_Army.jpeg\" alt=\"Polish_Army\" width=\"770\" height=\"447\" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>15. Canada</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though the number of the Canadian armed forces personnel is meager in comparison to the Americans, Canada has a modern and professional army.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Canada.jpg\" alt=\"RIMPAC 2012\" width=\"750\" height=\"536\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>14. Brazil</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The second largest army in South America has been involved in different peace keeping missions. The Brazilian army’s role in Haiti is praiseworthy for bringing stability.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-307\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/brazilian-army.jpg\" alt=\"brazilian army\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n<h2><strong>13. Egypt</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Thanks to years of US military aid, the Egyptian army is one of the biggest and strongest in the Middle East. The army there also is a potent force during major political upheavals.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-210\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Egypt.jpg\" alt=\"Egypt\" width=\"623\" height=\"315\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>12. Israel</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The IDF or Israeli Defense Force is one of the strongest in the world. Till now, it has won all the wars against its larger Arab neighbors.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-216\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/israel-1.jpg\" alt=\"israel 1\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n<h2><strong>11. Japan</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Japan has recently removed the last barrier to erase the pacifist clause from its constitution. In the coming years we are sure to see a more assertive Japanese Self Defense Force.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Japan.jpg\" alt=\"Japan\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>10. South Korea</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>With an effective conscription system, the South Koreans have made their army ready for any untoward situation. The formidable army is a good match for its bitter rivals in the North.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/south-korean.jpg\" alt=\"A South Korean army soldier runs in front of K-1 tanks after a live-fire military exercise as a part of the Seoul International Aerospace and Defense Exhibition 2011 on the Seungjin fire training field in Pocheon\" width=\"1000\" height=\"568\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>9. Turkey</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Turkey boasts the second largest army in NATO, right after USA. The Turkish army has been able to effectively contain the Kurdish insurgency.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-237\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Turkey.jpg\" alt=\"Turkey Army Troops, Militants Mass in Aleppo: Russian Monitor\" width=\"650\" height=\"375\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>8. Germany</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Experts believe that the German army is yet to match its formidable economic might. The biggest economy in Europe is however making rapid advance in the defense sector.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Germany.jpg\" alt=\"Germany\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>7. Pakistan </strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Pakistan army is still the most potent state institution in that country. At the moment it is fighting a fanatic Taliban faction in the country’s North Waziristan.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"Pakistan\" width=\"580\" height=\"386\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6. The United Kingdom</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Though the British army went through several budget cuts in the last few years, it’s still one of the strongest militaries in the world. The army still maintains presence in different British overseas territories.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-236\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/The-united-kingdom.jpg\" alt=\"The united kingdom\" width=\"940\" height=\"467\" />\r\n</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>5. France</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>France is one of the forces leading the fight against the brutal Islamic State. Besides they have presence in different African countries, where extremism is at rise.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-302\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/french-army.jpg\" alt=\"french army\" width=\"1110\" height=\"624\" /></h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>4. India</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The archrival of Pakistan, India has one of the biggest armies in the world. The Indian army has so far beaten the Pakistanis in three big wars.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/india.jpg\" alt=\"india\" width=\"640\" height=\"392\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h2><strong>3. China</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>The Chinese has the biggest army in the world with more than 2 million active personnel. In the recent years the country has continued defense budget spending spree to match the likes of United State.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-300\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Chinese-army.jpg\" alt=\"Chinese army\" width=\"885\" height=\"516\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>2. Russia</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>The Russian army might not be in the best