<!--nextpage-->\r\nPuerto Rico\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>A country lying in between Central and South America with beautiful sandy beaches could be your destination this summer. Puerto Rican women are famous for their exoticness.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-663\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Puerto-Rico.png\" alt=\"Puerto Rico\" width=\"600\" height=\"372\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Zimbabwe\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Despite ongoing political instability and a slumping economy, Zimbabwe is famous for natural beauty. Moreover, there you can meet African beauty queens.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-667\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Zimbabwe.jpg\" alt=\"Zimbabwe\" width=\"1024\" height=\"601\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Belarus\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Also known as White Russia, the ex-Soviet nation is at the moment is in the process of opening its door to the world. Tennis sensation Victoria Azarenka is a native of this Eastern European country.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-669\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Belarus.jpg\" alt=\"Belarus\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Poland\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Poland is often mentioned as the doorway between Eastern and Western Europe. The country has a significant number of English speakers. Polish women won’t disappoint you, after all, they are known for both sense and sensuality.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-674\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Poland-2.jpg\" alt=\"Poland\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Philippines\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Filipinas love guys from West. They want to see their men well-dressed. Like the women, the country has many beautiful tourist attractions.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-683\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Filipina.jpg\" alt=\"Filipina\" width=\"630\" height=\"420\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Japan\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Japanese women are a little bit choosey. It’s an opportunity for you to impress them since most of the Western guys are tall.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-658\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Japan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Japan\" width=\"640\" height=\"491\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Brazil\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It is said that the Brazilian women can turn your world upside down in a matter of few seconds. The country of samba and world famous Copacabana beach has many things to offer.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-654\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Brazil-1.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Colombia\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Colombian women are said to be the most desirable in the world for their natural tan and dark hair. And their perfect shape can make any guy go crazy. The South American country is famous for a big diversity of birds and flowers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-655\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Colombia.jpg\" alt=\"Colombia\" width=\"600\" height=\"452\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Russia</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The ever cold Russia compensates you with her hot and alluring women. When visiting the country, you will feel a positive vibe everywhere.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-677\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Russia-1.jpg\" alt=\"Russia\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" />','16 Countries Where You Can Meet Beautiful Women','','inherit','closed','closed','','651-revision-v1','','','2016-10-06 10:19:28','2016-10-06 10:19:28','',651,'http://feelsyoung.com/651-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(707,1,'2016-10-06 10:58:29','2016-10-06 10:58:29','<h2>These 16 tips can change the way of your life forever, in a positive way. Get started with them now to feel the change right away.</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>\r\n1. During nighttime our body remains dehydrated for long hours. To fulfill that deficit grow the habit of drinking two glasses of water right after you wake up.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-633\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>2. It is a fantastic idea to read something while taking breakfast. However, instead of starting your day with problematic news articles, you should read something more interesting like a book summary.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-634\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2-3.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"852\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>3. Use every moment of your life. Even when you are riding on metro or simply biking, be sure to stuff your phone with podcasts or audiobooks.</strong><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; color: #222222;\"> </span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-635\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3-3.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>4. The days of caffeine intake in between intervals at work are over. As a replacement you can start drinking green tree, which, unlike coffee, help you relax your mind.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-636\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/4-3.jpg\" alt=\"Woman drinking green tea\" width=\"460\" height=\"288\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>5. Taking naps on regular intervals reboot and refresh your mind and body and increases your efficiency.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-637 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/5.png\" alt=\"5\" width=\"520\" height=\"339\" />\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong>6. Try to avoid anything made of sugar during lunch hour or anytime of the day. Sugar highs and lows impact your brain negatively and thwart its regular capability.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-638\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>7. Don’t visit social media or meme sites more than twice a day. When you indulge in something that switches fast, your brain also gets adjusted to it and later results in difficulty concentrating.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-639\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/7-2.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>8. Gaming is a better choice than watching TV shows or movies. When you do the latter, your brain keeps taking input but doesn’t produce anything in return. On the other hand, gaming works as an exercise for your brain through interaction and processing.</strong></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-640\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/8-2.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"1000\" height=\"562\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>9. Similarly, reading a book is preferable to watching TV. While reading a book your brain works to prepare a mental image of the descriptions you have been reading.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-641\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/9.jpeg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>10. Learning a little bit programming won’t do any harm. Programming helps you to think logically and rationally. Don’t fret. There are many free websites that offer programming lessons for beginners.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-642\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/10-3.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"500\" height=\"358\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>11. It’s not a problem if you are not that into hard exercises. Instead of hitting the gym you can do some simple exercises to reap the most benefits.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-643\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/11-2.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>12. Passing time with people who are smarter than you can help see the world from a new angle. Remember, knowingly or unknowingly, you are influenced by those with whom you spend time.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-644\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/12-2.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>13. Try to get into friendly conversation with people who don’t agree with you. It will sharpen your ability to argument in a gentle way. And, you will be able to get rid of misconceptions that you were nurturing previously.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-645\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/13-1.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"450\" height=\"270\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>14. Every day make time for walk through places where trees are aplenty. As a result your mind will calm down and bodily blood circulation will improve.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-646\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/14-2.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"558\" height=\"364\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>15. Always keep a notepad with you and note down anything interesting or curious that come down your way. Working on them later will improve your logical thinking.</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-647\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/15-2.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>16. Every day take 10 minutes before you go to sleep to plan what’s to be done the next day. This will keep you ahead of your plan and increase productivity.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-648\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/16-2.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"480\" height=\"255\" />','16 Lifestyle Hacks To Get Smarter','','inherit','closed','closed','','630-revision-v1','','','2016-10-06 10:58:29','2016-10-06 10:58:29','',630,'http://feelsyoung.com/630-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(708,1,'2016-10-06 11:28:30','2016-10-06 11:28:30','<h3>Once they were flooded with cash. They had everything that a man can want in life: beautiful women, fast cars, and luxurious houses. But now they are at the verge of a total collapse.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>\r\nMichael Vick\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Michael had sponsorship deals with top brands like Nike and Coca-Cola. He was filed for bankruptcy for his alleged involvement in a dogfighting ring.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-541\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Michael-Vick.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"637\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lawrence Taylor\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During his NFL career, Taylor piled up a fortune. He lost it all and was announced bankrupt after 5 years from his retirement.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-537\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Lawrence-Taylor.jpg\" alt=\"Lawrence Taylor\" width=\"600\" height=\"601\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Bernie Kosar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After his retirement Kosar invested almost everything in real estate and saw it all blow away. To earn bread and butter he now works as a motivational speaker.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-526\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Bernie-Kosar.jpg\" alt=\"Bernie Kosar\" width=\"700\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Warren Sapp\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Warren was known for his lavish lifestyle. He had a fascination for lion skins. No wonder he filed for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-551\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Warren-Sapp.jpg\" alt=\"Warren Sapp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Vince Young\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Once he had all the potentials to be the next NFL superstar. A shock injury became a fatal blow to his premature career. He eventually had to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-550\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Vince-Young.jpg\" alt=\"Vince Young\" width=\"711\" height=\"533\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Travis Henry\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Henry had to serve jail term for his involvement in a drug ring. Because of his enormous debt, his children didn’t receive child support.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-549\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Travis-Henry.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"592\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Tiki Barber\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Tiki was fired from NBC right after he was found to have been involved in an extramarital relationship with one of its interns.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-548\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Tiki-Barber.jpg\" alt=\"Tiki Barber\" width=\"1200\" height=\"949\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Chris McAlister\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Misguided business investment cost it all for Chris who was once worth $55 million. He now lives with his parents.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-528\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Chris-McAlister.jpg\" alt=\"Chris McAlister\" width=\"700\" height=\"513\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Mark Brunell\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Mark tried to make profit out of the fast food and real estate sector. But he didn’t get what he invested in for and was forced to file for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-539\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Brunell.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Brunell\" width=\"560\" height=\"560\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Andre Rison\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Playing as a Wide Receiver, Andre earned $17 million during his NFL career. But soon after his retirement, he ran out of money.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-524\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Andre-Rison.jpg\" alt=\"Andre Rison\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dick Lane\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Dick earned a handsome amount from his NFL career. But, due to this uncontrolled lifestyle he soon fell in cash shortage.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dick-Lane.jpg\" alt=\"Dick Lane\" width=\"500\" height=\"545\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Raghib Ismail\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ismail was quite unlucky. Unlike others, he didn’t spend money behind illicit things. Unfortunately all his business ventures fell apart.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-544\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Raghib-Ismail.jpeg\" alt=\"Raghib Ismail\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Deuce McAllister\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>His famous run on the field didn’t continue when it came to managing financial matters. He was announced bankrupt with $75 million in debt.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-532\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Deuce-McAllister.jpg\" alt=\"Deuce McAllister\" width=\"600\" height=\"456\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Luther Ellis\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Luther didn’t face any problems after his retirement until he lost it all in dwindling investment decisions.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-538\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Luther-Ellis.jpg\" alt=\"Luther Ellis\" width=\"500\" height=\"748\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Archie Griffin\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In college football, Archie was one of the biggest names. However, he could not continue that trend when he signed for the highest stage, the NFL.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-525\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Archie-Griffin.jpg\" alt=\"Archie Griffin\" width=\"867\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dermontti Dawson\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The NFL Hall of Fame member could not manage his money well and filed for bankruptcy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-531\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dermontti-Dawson.jpg\" alt=\"Dermontti Dawson\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>Dan Marino\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Dan lost $14 million when one of his investments severely failed. He now works as a football analyst.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-530\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Dan-Marino.jpg\" alt=\"Dan Marino\" width=\"700\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Terrell Owens\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Terrell spent 11 years in the NFL and earned $70 million. Due to bad investment decisions he lost it all.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-547\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Terrell-Owens.jpg\" alt=\"Terrell Owens\" width=\"650\" height=\"752\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>JaMarcus Russell\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Russell was accused of possessing controlled drugs without prescription. He had to pay $200,000 as compensation.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-535\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/JaMarcus-Russell.jpg\" alt=\"JaMarcus Russell\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Ray Rice\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After being caught on camera knocking his fiancé up, Ray’s contract was immediately terminated.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-545\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ray-Rice.jpg\" alt=\"Ray Rice\" width=\"650\" height=\"441\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Johnny Unitas\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Unitas earned fame playing as a Quarterback. His business investment didn’t work out well, however.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-536\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Johnny-Unitas.jpg\" alt=\"Johnny Unitas\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Aaron Hernandez\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Back in 2012, Aaron got a $40m contract. But he is now serving life term for murder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-523\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Aaron-Hernandez.jpg\" alt=\"Aaron Hernandez\" width=\"1009\" height=\"800\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Mark Ingram, Sr.\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Super Bowl XXV hero is now passing his days in uncertainties after being found to be involved in money laundering and tax evasion.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-540\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark_ingram.jpg\" alt=\"Mark_ingram\" width=\"635\" height=\"628\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>O.J. Simpson\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Murder, armed robbery, and kidnapping, all these major crimes doomed Simpson’s career.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-543\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Oj_simpson.jpg\" alt=\"Oj_simpson\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Charlie Batch\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The former NFL star is saddled with an extraordinary sum of $8 million.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-527\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Charlie-Batch.jpg\" alt=\"Charlie Batch\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Muhsin Muhammad\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Muhammad saw his finances gone into a battered state and was forced to sell his house on eBay.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-542\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Muhsin-Muhammad.jpg\" alt=\"Muhsin Muhammad\" width=\"564\" height=\"594\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Clinton Portis\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Clinton made a formidable income of $50 million dollars. His untamed gambling habit had become his doom.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-529\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Clinton-Portis.jpg\" alt=\"Clinton Portis\" width=\"700\" height=\"393\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Irving Fryar\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>After retirement, Irving tried to find resort in divine duty. This, however, couldn’t prevent him from committing crimes like mortgage scam.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-534\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Irving-Fryar.jpg\" alt=\"Irving Fryar\" width=\"711\" height=\"533\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Ricky Williams\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ricky was rehabilitated for drug abuse. He is yet to be broke for good. He has accused his financial advisor of embezzling his funds.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-546\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Ricky-Williams.jpg\" alt=\"Ricky Williams\" width=\"600\" height=\"781\" /><!--nextpage-->','29 NFL Legends Who Lost It All','','inherit','closed','closed','','521-revision-v1','','','2016-10-06 11:28:30','2016-10-06 11:28:30','',521,'http://feelsyoung.com/521-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(709,1,'2016-10-06 15:32:16','2016-10-06 15:32:16','<h3>It’s been long since The Crocodile Dundee was released. The movie series changed many people’s view of life. So, what happened to the famous cast? How do they look today? Let’s have a look.</h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h2><strong>John Meillon</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nMeillon portrayed the character of Dundee’s business partner. As recognition of his acting career, he received the OBE.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-470\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Meillon.jpg\" alt=\"John Meillon\" width=\"503\" height=\"768\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nJohn Meillon died in 1989. The second movie in the franchise was released the previous year, where he played the same role as the first one. He was quite lucky to have escaped the third installment in the series, which is considered as the worst.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-479\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/John-Meillon-1.jpg\" alt=\"John Meillon\" width=\"313\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Mark Blum</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nPerhaps the least loved character in the movie, Mark played the character of Sue’s lover cum editor.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-472\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Blum.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Blum\" width=\"670\" height=\"345\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nMark gave more examples of his acting talent though his roles in ‘The Sopranos’ and ‘Frasier’.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-481\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Mark-Blum-1.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Blum\" width=\"454\" height=\"605\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Reginald Veljohnson</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nRemember the famous Limo driver in the franchise? He was also a part of the ‘Die Hard 2’ cast.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-474\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Reginald-Veljohnson.jpg\" alt=\"Reginald Veljohnson\" width=\"750\" height=\"364\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nIn his later appearances on TV shows and movies he played the role of a cop or other bossy figures.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-483\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Reginald-Veljohnson-1.jpg\" alt=\"Reginald Veljohnson\" width=\"440\" height=\"550\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Linda Kozlowski</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nIn the movie she was often referred to as the apple of Dundee’s eye. No wonder they got married in real life. However, their marriage didn’t long last.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-471\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Linda-Kozlowski.jpg\" alt=\"Linda Kozlowski\" width=\"625\" height=\"417\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nFar away from the limelight, she now motivates in her travel operation business located in Marrakesh.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-480\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Linda-Kozlowski-1.jpg\" alt=\"Look How The Crocodile Dundee Stars Aged Up\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>David Gulpilil</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nDavid was no central figure in the movie. The franchise however would not have been felt the same if he had been left out.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-469\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil.jpg\" alt=\"David Gulpilil\" width=\"466\" height=\"310\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nDavid was accused of felony and served time in jail for a year. He still continues with his acting career.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-477\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/David-Gulpilil-1.jpg\" alt=\"David Gulpilil\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Paul Hogan</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nThe Crocodile Dundee franchise gave him both name and fame; so much so that he rejected offers for hit movies like “Ghost”. His devotion paid him well.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-473\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paul-Hogan.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Hogan\" width=\"750\" height=\"524\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Now\n</span>\nHogan’s later life was not so enviable – he was accused of tax fraud. He now takes care of his son.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-482\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Paul-Hogan-1.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Hogan\" width=\"650\" height=\"366\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h2><strong>Steve Rackman</strong></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Then\n</span>\nHis character Donk was lucky enough to have kissed Dundee in the movie. Before being selected for the hit franchise, he was a professional wrestler.</h3>\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-475\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Steve-Rackman.jpg\" alt=\"Steve Rackman\" width=\"401\" height=\"544\" /><!--nextpage-->\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoratio