-10-26 15:45:36','','lili-elbe','','inherit','open','closed','','lili-elbe','','','2016-10-26 15:45:36','2016-10-26 15:45:36','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lili-Elbe.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(830,1,'2016-10-26 15:46:19','2016-10-26 15:46:19','','lilly-wachowski','','inherit','open','closed','','lilly-wachowski','','','2016-10-26 15:46:19','2016-10-26 15:46:19','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lilly-Wachowski.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(831,1,'2016-10-26 15:46:49','2016-10-26 15:46:49','','candy-darling','','inherit','open','closed','','candy-darling','','','2016-10-26 15:46:49','2016-10-26 15:46:49','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Candy-Darling.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(832,1,'2016-10-26 15:47:20','2016-10-26 15:47:20','','candis-cayne','','inherit','open','closed','','candis-cayne','','','2016-10-26 15:47:20','2016-10-26 15:47:20','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Candis-Cayne.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(833,1,'2016-10-26 15:47:49','2016-10-26 15:47:49','','hari-nef','','inherit','open','closed','','hari-nef','','','2016-10-26 15:47:49','2016-10-26 15:47:49','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Hari-Nef.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(834,1,'2016-10-26 15:48:22','2016-10-26 15:48:22','','jamie-clayton','','inherit','open','closed','','jamie-clayton','','','2016-10-26 15:48:22','2016-10-26 15:48:22','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Jamie-Clayton.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(835,1,'2016-10-26 15:49:01','2016-10-26 15:49:01','<h3>To change your gender, transitioning is important. This entails plastic surgery and the various professional cosmetic procedures that are needed for the surgery to work. Many people have gone through transitioning. These 31 celebrities underwent the hormonal replacement therapy, facelifts, gender reassignment surgeries, botox injections and other procedures of professional cosmetic surgery so as to ‘feel good’ in their skin.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-802 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/g5tytgfgdter.jpg\" alt=\"g5tytgfgdter\" width=\"611\" height=\"407\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Amanda Lepore</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Amanda is a public figure, model, and a performer as well as singer. She is one of the most recognized transgender celebs. She has been involved in many, popular brand campaigns in the world such as Swatch and M.A.C. The celeb prides for being David LeChapelle’s muse. She has the wigs, drag make-up, weaves, cosmetology, medical specialists, plastic surgery and the outright hormonal prescriptions – just ready to make her the new Amanda Lepore!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-large wp-image-803 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Amanda-Lepore-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"amanda-lepore\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Thomas Beati</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When Beatie tore the internet with news of being the first transsexual male to conceive, the world was left in amusement. His gender reassignment surgery was successfully done, and when he decided to become pregnant on behalf of his wife, who was not able to have children, he took the trans community by storm. He was an icon shining a light on matters of gender expression and trans issues.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-804 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Thomas-Beatie.jpg\" alt=\"Pregnant\" width=\"594\" height=\"396\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Alicia Liu</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Taiwanese TV personality and fashion model was born a man but underwent gender reassignment at 18 years. When she became a celeb, one of her high school classmates took to the internet with one of her male pictures. She defended herself on the media, and she stands for the transgender people in the world.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-805 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Alicia-Liu.jpg\" alt=\"alicia-liu\" width=\"613\" height=\"408\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Jackie Curtis</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Born John Curtis Holder Jr., Jackie Curtis went for a transition to become a woman. Also known as “Warhol Superstar,” Curtis performed as both man and woman in the acting world. Ripped dress, red hair and red lipstick are her signature outfit. Heroin overdose took her life at the age of 38 years.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-806 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Jackie-Curtis.jpg\" alt=\"jackie-curtis\" width=\"600\" height=\"391\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Carmen Carrera</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This TV personality and model was born Christopher Roman, but after the gender reassignment, she became the new Carmen. She once hosted the ‘RuPaul’s Drag Race’ until season 3 presenting as Christopher. She revealed her trans identity in 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-807 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Carmen-Carrera.jpg\" alt=\"carmen-carrera\" width=\"438\" height=\"647\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Alexis Arquette</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>At 23 years of age, Robert Arquettte transitioned into a woman, Alexis, and began her cabaret career. The actress/performer had a gender reassignment surgery with a team of professional surgeons and doctors, and a professional plastic surgeon. She passed away after fighting with illness on September 11th, 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-808 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Alexis-Arquette.jpg\" alt=\"alexis-arquette\" width=\"580\" height=\"579\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Trace Lysette</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This transgender actress appeared in ‘transparent’ and opened up in a recent interview on her identity struggles. Before she became a successful actress, she stayed in secrecy until she opened up about her true self. Her journey has been long.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-809 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Trace-Lysette.jpg\" alt=\"trace-lysette\" width=\"380\" height=\"540\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Chaz Bono</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In 1995, The Advocate – American leading gay newspaper – brought to light the new identity of Chaz. The only child of Sonny Bono and Cher, American music legends, hit the headlines. He had gender reassignment surgery. It all began from his ‘Becoming Chaz’ documentary.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-810 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Chaz-Bono-624x1024.jpg\" alt=\"chaz-bono\" width=\"539\" height=\"885\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Claudia Charriez</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During the 2006 edition of the ‘America’s Next Top Model’ reality series, Charriez battled it to the semis. Her name soared high in the world. She had the grace of the fans and judges alike, BUT she lost due to her birth status as a male. She opted for sex reassignment to deal with her gender dysphoria.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-811 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Claudia-Charriez-697x1024.jpg\" alt=\"claudia-charriez\" width=\"562\" height=\"825\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Nina Arsenault</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It took over 61 surgeries for Nina to fully transition into a woman. The two masters degrees’ holder is a singer, actress, model and an activist for the LGT. Through theater and art, Arsenault expresses her ideals about sexuality and society.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-812 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Nina-Arsenault.jpg\" alt=\"nina-arsenault\" width=\"434\" height=\"575\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Laverne Cox</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The trans community recognizes this face easily. She got to fame thanks to the prison hairdresser, Sophia Burset, a role she portrayed in the ‘Orange is the New Black’ Netflix hit. She went for intensive plastic surgery and dermatological procedures as well as the medical hormone treatments during her transition.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-813 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Laverne-Cox.jpg\" alt=\"laverne-cox\" width=\"428\" height=\"571\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lea T.</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Lea is a renowned Italian fashion model. Back in 2012, she underwent sex reassignment in Thailand. She became an international fashion model for houses like Givenchy. Redken is one of her popular hair care brands.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-814 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lea-T..jpg\" alt=\"lea-t\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lili Chen</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When Lili tried to compete as a transgender woman in various beauty pageants, she shot to the limelight. The model, actress and singer trans was the Miss Artificial Beauty runners up in 2004. Her entry to the Miss Universe was denied.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-816  alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lili-Chen-1.jpg\" width=\"607\" height=\"388\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Caitlyn Jenner</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>She transitioned from Bruce Jenner to Caitlyn Jenner in an unexpected move that was truly revolutionary. She had identity struggles for years before her gender reassignment surgery. In 2015 in the ‘Vanity Fair,\' Jenner revealed her new identity.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-817 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Caitlyn-Jenner.jpg\" alt=\"caitlyn-jenner\" width=\"437\" height=\"513\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Gigi Gorgeous</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Canadian actress and internet personality came to light through her YouTube tutorials on makeup and fashion. Her YouTube channel gained popularity, and when it came time for her gender reassignment surgery, there was outpouring support. She has been featured on the Good Work, Access Hollywood, and Project Runway, All Stars.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-818 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Gigi-Gorgeous.jpg\" alt=\"gigi-gorgeous\" width=\"578\" height=\"684\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Octavia St. Laurent</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The famous trans-soul singer stamped her pop-culture mark in the 1990 “Paris is Burning” documentary. It was a film about an African-America, Latino gay as well as transgender people in New York. She died of AIDS in 2007.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-819 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Octavia-St.-Laurent.jpg\" alt=\"octavia-st-laurent\" width=\"619\" height=\"374\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lana Wachowski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Her role in directing ‘The Matrix’ epic trilogy made her a celeb.  Together with Lily, her sister went for sex transition in 2008. Identity crisis had taken a toll in her childhood ages, and she almost committed suicide. She has now completed her transition.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-820 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lana-Wachowski.jpg\" alt=\"lana-wachowski\" width=\"414\" height=\"600\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Valentijn De Hingh</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The Dutch sensation model began the transition at a young age. Her 10 years of transition are captured in a documentary. She is a renowned model in the fashion world.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-821 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Valentijn-De-Hingh.jpg\" alt=\"valentijn-de-hingh\" width=\"561\" height=\"751\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dana International</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Back in 1993, this great singer went for sex reassignment. It was the same year when her first album was released. She changed her name from Sharon Cohen to Dana International and represented Israel during the 1998 Eurovision Song Contest. Her popular ‘Diva’ song won the content. She is one of the Israeli’s celebrities with over 8 albums released. She is truly an international export for Israel.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-822 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Dana-International.jpg\" alt=\"dana-international\" width=\"601\" height=\"403\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Erika Ervin</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Ervin is a model and fitness instructor. She goes by Amazon Eve, her stage name. She is mostly recognized for her appearance on the cover of “Zoo Weekly” – Australian magazine – and “American Horror Story: Freak Show.” Her staggering 6’8” height makes her the tallest model globally.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-823 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Erika-Ervin.jpg\" alt=\"erika-ervin\" width=\"392\" height=\"594\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Conchita Wurst</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Conchita was truly an icon for the Austrian people. Also known as Thomas Neuwirth won the 2014 Eurovision Song Contest through the ‘Rise Like a Phoenix’ song. When describing her “original personality” and his Conchita ego, the uses the male and female pronouns.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-824 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Conchita-Wurst.jpg\" alt=\"conchita-wurst\" width=\"435\" height=\"580\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Balian Buschbaum</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>During the 2000 Olympics, Balian competed for Germany and retired from sports seven years later. This, she cited to be a leeway for her to transition.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-825 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Balian-Buschbaum.jpg\" alt=\"balian-buschbaum\" width=\"365\" height=\"547\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Andrej Pejic</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The fashion world respects this self-made model. Pejic was discovered at 17 years while working at McDonlds. Just recently, the trans icon went for a sex reassignment surgery.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-826 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Andrej-Pejic.jpg\" alt=\"andrej-pejic\" width=\"603\" height=\"402\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Isis King</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>King was among the first trans women who competed in the “America’s Next Top Model” reality series. She would later feature in the eleventh and seventeenth seasons. This has made her a celeb. She is a clothing designer and model.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-828 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/isis-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"isis\" width=\"585\" height=\"329\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lil Elbe</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Upon the release of the movie, ‘The Danish Girl,\' Elbe’s story came to light. She was the first person to ever undergo a sexual reassignment surgery openly. This opened the gate for many more trans people.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-829 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lili-Elbe-581x1024.jpg\" alt=\"lili-elbe\" width=\"507\" height=\"894\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Lilly Wachowski</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Two male siblings went for a transition to become women. The directing duo shocked the world by both announcing to be transgender.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-830 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Lilly-Wachowski.jpg\" alt=\"lilly-wachowski\" width=\"535\" height=\"463\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Candy Darling</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The American transgender actress was an icon. She is best known as one of ‘Warhol superstars.\' She was a known muse for the rock back – The Velvet Underground in 1960.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-831 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Candy-Darling.jpg\" alt=\"candy-darling\" width=\"472\" height=\"655\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Candis Cayne</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>She shot to fame through her surgical transformation. She was the first transgender to snag a trans role in the ‘Dirty, Sexy, Money’ series. She has undergone multiple cosmetic surgery procedures including breast argumentation surgery and rhinoplasty. She was also on a strict hormone medication regiment.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-832 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Candis-Cayne.jpg\" alt=\"candis-cayne\" width=\"481\" height=\"632\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Hari Nef</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When IMG, an international modeling label signed her as the first ever trans, Nef hit the news.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-833 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Hari-Nef.jpg\" alt=\"hari-nef\" width=\"630\" height=\"420\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Jamie Clayton</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>In ‘Sense8’ Jamie Clayton plays a trans hacker. He is a celeb in the industry. He discusses modern community and blames it for making transgender more of a label than a normal concept.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-834 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Jamie-Clayton.jpg\" alt=\"jamie-clayton\" width=\"426\" height=\"594\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Different personalities had different transition procedures. The celebrities had their story and how they shot into limelight with the news about their transgender. The 31 international celebrities have taken the modern world by storm. Many are now following their path since they have advocated for trans procedures. The news about men and women undergoing various surgery procedures and other transition procedures has been on the rise. The spate of transgender is now a reality, and everyone does no longer have to fight with victimization whatsoever. The list indicates world class personalities in different capacities. It is a wakeup call for many people who are struggling with an identity crisis!</h3>','31 Celebs Who Had Gender Reassignment Surgery','','inherit','closed','closed','','798-revision-v1','','','2016-10-26 15:49:01','2016-10-26 15:49:01','',798,'http://feelsyoung.com/798-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(836,1,'2016-10-27 21:03:32','2016-10-27 21:03:32','<h2><strong>Red Eyed Raven</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>And who wouldn’t love the show that is put by this camera hottie? She is not only red and ready but shoe also got beauty oozing out of her. Look at the twins below the chin, I am left speechless!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-837 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Red-Eyed-Raven.png\" alt=\"red-eyed-raven\" width=\"551\" height=\"408\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dogs Are Crap</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie speaks volumes about the choice of pets you have. Not only do I hate, or love less, dogs but also I admire the independence of cats. They are too creepy and this photograph is my testimony. I doubt how this fits to be a selfie: how was it even taken?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-838 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Dogs-Are-Cra.jpg\" alt=\"dogs-are-cra\" width=\"600\" height=\"376\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>I Wish I Could Photoshop</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The world of today is utterly run by cameras – at least for most selfie fans. If you need a perfect selfie, I think you need to explore other picture editing techniques. I have never done it before but I wouldn’t mind trying Photoshop. Some people struggle so hard to get it right in front of a camera. I wish they knew that beauty can be achieved in other ways.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-839 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-Wish-I-Could-Photoshop.jpg\" alt=\"i-wish-i-could-photoshop\" width=\"580\" height=\"513\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>I DON’T LIKE SHARKS</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is it just me or everyone freaks about sharks? I have always had an issue with sharks. I find it horrible and I hardly have fun with their images in front of me. However, this selfie is worth looking at; time and again. How on earth do you take such an incredible shot?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-840 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-DON’T-LIKE-SHAR.jpg\" alt=\"i-dont-like-shar\" width=\"598\" height=\"336\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>My Perfect Woman</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We all have our take on a perfect woman. This selfie is a mix of the likes and dislikes. It matters the page you are reading from. If you want to see this photo as an obnoxiously camera loving and cannot wait to be in the bathroom to take selfies, then it fits you. Likewise, you might think this is a perfect woman who will capture every moment you are having a good time in the bathroom. Either way, she is the elusive woman every man is looking for. Look at the posture. Nothing can be more appetizing than this!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-841 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/My-Perfect-Woman.jpg\" alt=\"my-perfect-woman\" width=\"535\" height=\"443\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What An Ugly Beast</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We akk have our pet preferences. My dog love could be way below par or someone may be loving the animal excessively. Either way, this selfie just nailed it. For those who love dogs, it is the perfect way to have your pet ose for a one shot of life. On the flip isde those who fairy like them, this is just a constant reminder of a horrific shot. The selfie is just incredibly taken!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-842 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-An-Ugly-Beast.png\" alt=\"what-an-ugly-beast\" width=\"556\" height=\"557\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What Can You Even Say Here?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Your partner just sent you this and you want my opinion? Well, I have none. How would you think when you got such a selfie from someone taking a bath? This is simply a duo for me: it is either a show of perfect partnership or you are in for the worst nightmare of your life – your call!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-843 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-Can-You-Even.jpg\" alt=\"what-can-you-even\" width=\"615\" height=\"461\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Don’t Have Kids</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Did something go wrong and now dealing with the consequences is killing you? I bet you would ask this selfie fanatic the same question. She appears to have slipped into having a kid and now her old memories cannot let her be a parent.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-844 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Don’t-Have-Kids.jpg\" alt=\"dont-have-kids\" width=\"537\" height=\"717\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Say Hello</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie is an attestation that flexibility is fun. This lady want to bring that to our attention – nothing much. Just tap and say HELLO!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-845 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Say-Hello.png\" alt=\"say-hello\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>BROAD CITY 4 LYF</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is Lena Dunham, but I didn’t know until someone jogged my memory. The incessant love between her and the ‘Girls’ is just incredible. Broad City is probably the best comedy of all times!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-846 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/BROAD-CITY-4-LYF.jpg\" alt=\"broad-city-4-lyf\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What A Genius</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie might appear or mean very stupid. However, the idea behind it is just out of this world. This lad must be thanking his camera to capture such incredible shots. I hope in future this lad creates something that will change the way of life.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-847 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-A-Genius.jpg\" alt=\"what-a-genius\" width=\"512\" height=\"768\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>No Shame</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Mirrors used to be the obsession for many until that space was closed by the selfie cameras. This lad cannot help but keep checking on how he is fairing. It is a weird habit but this selfie will leave you shaking your head with dismay.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-848 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/No-Shame-366x1024.jpg\" alt=\"no-shame\" width=\"327\" height=\"915\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Shout, Shout, Let It All Out!</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You do not know the beauty of pets until you spend hours waiting for that perfect shot. The human/animal hybrid selfie is one of the best things to ever happen in front of camera. This is an amazing art and the shouting face selfie is a true explanation for wonderful shots.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-849 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Shout-Shout-Let-It.jpg\" alt=\"shout-shout-let-it\" width=\"540\" height=\"934\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Ever Heard Of Priorities?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is this love for camera or just priorities upside down? I might not have been kept in a hospital bed for long or anything serious but if anyone was to come and pull such camera tricks in front of me, I bet nothing healthy would happen. This is not only weird but also ‘inhuman’. I cannot imagine what the selfie has to do with this setting.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-850 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Ever-Heard-Of-Priorities.png\" alt=\"ever-heard-of-priorities\" width=\"606\" height=\"455\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>You Shouldn’t Have Bought Him It!</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When technology meets age, this is what to expect. No one in this selfie should blame the old man. The birthday present just got into use right away and now everyone seems embarrassed, but how was he to use it?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-851 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/You-Shouldn’t-Have.jpg\" alt=\"you-shouldnt-have\" width=\"592\" height=\"429\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Perfect Positioning</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is it the lighting or the positioning that is making this selfie incredibly hot? Well, any professional photographer knows that this hottie got the blend just right and you do need to be told the results.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-852 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Perfect-Positioning.jpg\" alt=\"perfect-positioning\" width=\"604\" height=\"453\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The One Selfie That Was Worth It</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You look at most selfies and wonder why some people bought selfie sticks. But this is one selfie that will answer you all that. You feel the urge to be involved, the indulge is just uncontrollable and this selfie just won it all. It is brilliant and all you feel is to be in it!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-853 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/The-One-Selfie-That-Was.jpg\" alt=\"the-one-selfie-that-was\" width=\"527\" height=\"395\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Another Example Of Parents Who Aren’t Ready</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>What is happening to mum and dad! Probably the next generation will be a traumatized one.  These are some of the things you promised never to leave behind and settle down as parents? Well, this could be a recipe for disaster in future!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-854 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Another-Example.jpg\" alt=\"another-example\" width=\"582\" height=\"387\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Going For A Swim</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Jump in hottie! And that moment had to be captured, right? Question is, does the camera know the landing point? I bet not. This lady is on a thrill and swimming is never an issue for her to stay off the camera.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-855 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Going-For-A-Swim.jpg\" alt=\"going-for-a-swim\" width=\"604\" height=\"457\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>View From Above</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Selfies have gone a notch higher and this girl is probably on the wheels. She knows what to do and how to hold her phone so as to leave the world on cringe. I bet the bikini is about to burst open and let the oozing beauty off!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-856 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/View-From-Above-1024x1018.jpg\" alt=\"view-from-above\" width=\"603\" height=\"600\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Public Displays</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It does not matter the setting, this hottie had to capture the moment. A snick-pick on her curvy body will tell you why nothing would have stopped her from taking the selfie. Is she working or on some break? Anyway, it does not bother anyone, it matters that she got the selfie just right!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-857 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Public-Displays.jpg\" alt=\"public-displays\" width=\"533\" height=\"529\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What To Expect When You’re Expecting</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>I do not know the recipient of this selfie but the idea was truly genius. You can always lift a leg onto a sink and stay off the bending. Your phone can do the rest and what to expect is just magical. Take a look!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-858 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-To-Expect.jpg\" alt=\"what-to-expect\" width=\"591\" height=\"438\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Teacher’s Pet</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Teachers too got style, and this hottie took it to snapchat to express her class. We only hope that her students are not seeing how she has been rocking the internet. The modern teacher has affinity for selfies and this is what she gave us.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-859 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Teacher.jpg\" alt=\"teacher\" width=\"482\" height=\"856\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>As Much As I Don’t Like Dogs…</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is your boss driving you nuts? Well, this dog knows the tough side of a selfie-holic. Not only is the little pet uneasy but also scared of whatever the owner is doing on camera. Anyone should be worried about this trend and for that reason; I do not blame the dog.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-860 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/As-Much-As.jpg\" alt=\"as-much-as\" width=\"484\" height=\"657\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Girls’ Night Out</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Well, the camera has its taste too – and this selfie tells it all. First, the setting went under but the gorgeous pair came through for it. It was truly their time to take a breath. It does not matter what you do, they will always come in handy!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-861 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Girls’-Night-Out.jpg\" alt=\"girls-night-out\" width=\"556\" height=\"662\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Annoyed Or Impressed?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Someone needs to nature this acrobat. It could be low on the content of the selfie but the talent here is undoubted. This will leave you with a mixed feeling: pleasure and displeasure at the same time.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-863 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Annoyed-Or-Impressed.jpg\" alt=\"annoyed-or-impressed\" width=\"413\" height=\"550\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Who Picks Chicken?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>If you love the horse masks then this will kill you. The chicken selfie is just hilarious. It is a simple way to explain how camera can be interesting to everyone and everything. If you think this is not super creative, then let us know what it is!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-862 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Who-Picks-Chicken.jpg\" alt=\"who-picks-chicken\" width=\"594\" height=\"446\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>JUST SIT STILL</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The animal-human hybrid selfie is just right. My question is whether that is a dog or a cat? That’s least of the worries for the owner. It must have taken enough time to get this selfie right and surely, they deserve a crown for this.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-864 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/JUST-SIT-STILL.png\" alt=\"just-sit-still\" width=\"517\" height=\"695\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Should We Be Laughing?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>And what is exactly going on here! I am not sure whether or not I should be laughing but this selfie got everyone cracking. This lad just got his phone into an overdrive!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-865 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Should-We-Be-Laughing.jpg\" alt=\"should-we-be-laughing\" width=\"473\" height=\"632\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>It’s Always The Background Characters</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You cannot afford to miss this – even the awkward looking lad behind this cutie cannot understand this. The dude cannot concentrate on the wheels anymore. The whole situation is just an amusement for him.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-867 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/It’s-Always-The-Background.png\" alt=\"its-always-the-background\" width=\"592\" height=\"441\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>So Cute It Hurts</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>One of those moments you never wanted to remember but you have your selfie camera to thank for it. The selfie is just an explanation for ‘sweet gone sour’. Take a moment and think about it!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-866 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/So-Cute-It-Hurts.jpg\" alt=\"so-cute-it-hurts\" width=\"563\" height=\"422\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Rich People Are Horrible</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Wait, what just happened? Of the two groups, which one became a victim of rich mindlessness? Well, I can imagine what it takes to set up such an emphatic scene just for a selfie under the water – but that’s rich people’s problem!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-868 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Rich-People-Are.png\" alt=\"rich-people-are\" width=\"471\" height=\"468\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>I Can’t Blame Him</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You got your selfie camera and as you walk in the open, this is what you land into: dogs at it! You do not just apologetically look at them and walk away – the perfect shot for you should be here. This is just mind-blowing!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-869\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-Can’t-Blame-Him.png\" alt=\"i-cant-blame-him\" width=\"560\" height=\"417\" />','The Most Cringeworthy Selfies!','','publish','open','open','','the-most-cringeworthy-selfies','','','2016-10-27 21:09:23','2016-10-27 21:09:23','',0,'http://feelsyoung.com/?p=836',0,'post','',0),(837,1,'2016-10-27 20:40:57','2016-10-27 20:40:57','','red-eyed-raven','','inherit','open','closed','','red-eyed-raven','','','2016-10-27 20:40:57','2016-10-27 20:40:57','',836,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Red-Eyed-Raven.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(838,1,'2016-10-27 20:41:36','2016-10-27 20:41:36','','dogs-are-cra','','inherit','open','closed','','dogs-are-cra','','','2016-10-27 20:41:36','2016-10-27 20:41:36','',836,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Dogs-Are-Cra.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(839,1,'2016-10-27 20:42:15','2016-10-27 20:42:15','','i-wish-i-could-photoshop','','inherit','open','closed','','i-wish-i-could-photoshop','','','2016-10-27 20:42:15','2016-10-27 20:42:15','',836,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-Wish-I-Could-Photoshop.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(840,1,