rich-people-are','','inherit','open','closed','','rich-people-are','','','2016-10-27 21:01:49','2016-10-27 21:01:49','',836,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Rich-People-Are.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(869,1,'2016-10-27 21:02:30','2016-10-27 21:02:30','','i-cant-blame-him','','inherit','open','closed','','i-cant-blame-him','','','2016-10-27 21:02:30','2016-10-27 21:02:30','',836,'http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-Can’t-Blame-Him.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(870,1,'2016-10-27 21:03:32','2016-10-27 21:03:32','<h2><strong>Red Eyed Raven</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>And who wouldn’t love the show that is put by this camera hottie? She is not only red and ready but shoe also got beauty oozing out of her. Look at the twins below the chin, I am left speechless!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-837 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Red-Eyed-Raven.png\" alt=\"red-eyed-raven\" width=\"551\" height=\"408\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Dogs Are Crap</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie speaks volumes about the choice of pets you have. Not only do I hate, or love less, dogs but also I admire the independence of cats. They are too creepy and this photograph is my testimony. I doubt how this fits to be a selfie: how was it even taken?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-838 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Dogs-Are-Cra.jpg\" alt=\"dogs-are-cra\" width=\"600\" height=\"376\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>I Wish I Could Photoshop</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>The world of today is utterly run by cameras – at least for most selfie fans. If you need a perfect selfie, I think you need to explore other picture editing techniques. I have never done it before but I wouldn’t mind trying Photoshop. Some people struggle so hard to get it right in front of a camera. I wish they knew that beauty can be achieved in other ways.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-839 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-Wish-I-Could-Photoshop.jpg\" alt=\"i-wish-i-could-photoshop\" width=\"580\" height=\"513\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>I DON’T LIKE SHARKS</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is it just me or everyone freaks about sharks? I have always had an issue with sharks. I find it horrible and I hardly have fun with their images in front of me. However, this selfie is worth looking at; time and again. How on earth do you take such an incredible shot?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-840 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/I-DON’T-LIKE-SHAR.jpg\" alt=\"i-dont-like-shar\" width=\"598\" height=\"336\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>My Perfect Woman</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We all have our take on a perfect woman. This selfie is a mix of the likes and dislikes. It matters the page you are reading from. If you want to see this photo as an obnoxiously camera loving and cannot wait to be in the bathroom to take selfies, then it fits you. Likewise, you might think this is a perfect woman who will capture every moment you are having a good time in the bathroom. Either way, she is the elusive woman every man is looking for. Look at the posture. Nothing can be more appetizing than this!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-841 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/My-Perfect-Woman.jpg\" alt=\"my-perfect-woman\" width=\"535\" height=\"443\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What An Ugly Beast</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>We akk have our pet preferences. My dog love could be way below par or someone may be loving the animal excessively. Either way, this selfie just nailed it. For those who love dogs, it is the perfect way to have your pet ose for a one shot of life. On the flip isde those who fairy like them, this is just a constant reminder of a horrific shot. The selfie is just incredibly taken!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-842 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-An-Ugly-Beast.png\" alt=\"what-an-ugly-beast\" width=\"556\" height=\"557\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What Can You Even Say Here?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Your partner just sent you this and you want my opinion? Well, I have none. How would you think when you got such a selfie from someone taking a bath? This is simply a duo for me: it is either a show of perfect partnership or you are in for the worst nightmare of your life – your call!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-843 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-Can-You-Even.jpg\" alt=\"what-can-you-even\" width=\"615\" height=\"461\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Don’t Have Kids</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Did something go wrong and now dealing with the consequences is killing you? I bet you would ask this selfie fanatic the same question. She appears to have slipped into having a kid and now her old memories cannot let her be a parent.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-844 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Don’t-Have-Kids.jpg\" alt=\"dont-have-kids\" width=\"537\" height=\"717\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Say Hello</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie is an attestation that flexibility is fun. This lady want to bring that to our attention – nothing much. Just tap and say HELLO!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-845 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Say-Hello.png\" alt=\"say-hello\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>BROAD CITY 4 LYF</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This is Lena Dunham, but I didn’t know until someone jogged my memory. The incessant love between her and the ‘Girls’ is just incredible. Broad City is probably the best comedy of all times!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-846 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/BROAD-CITY-4-LYF.jpg\" alt=\"broad-city-4-lyf\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What A Genius</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>This selfie might appear or mean very stupid. However, the idea behind it is just out of this world. This lad must be thanking his camera to capture such incredible shots. I hope in future this lad creates something that will change the way of life.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-847 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-A-Genius.jpg\" alt=\"what-a-genius\" width=\"512\" height=\"768\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>No Shame</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Mirrors used to be the obsession for many until that space was closed by the selfie cameras. This lad cannot help but keep checking on how he is fairing. It is a weird habit but this selfie will leave you shaking your head with dismay.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-848 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/No-Shame-366x1024.jpg\" alt=\"no-shame\" width=\"327\" height=\"915\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Shout, Shout, Let It All Out!</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You do not know the beauty of pets until you spend hours waiting for that perfect shot. The human/animal hybrid selfie is one of the best things to ever happen in front of camera. This is an amazing art and the shouting face selfie is a true explanation for wonderful shots.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-849 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Shout-Shout-Let-It.jpg\" alt=\"shout-shout-let-it\" width=\"540\" height=\"934\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Ever Heard Of Priorities?</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is this love for camera or just priorities upside down? I might not have been kept in a hospital bed for long or anything serious but if anyone was to come and pull such camera tricks in front of me, I bet nothing healthy would happen. This is not only weird but also ‘inhuman’. I cannot imagine what the selfie has to do with this setting.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-850 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Ever-Heard-Of-Priorities.png\" alt=\"ever-heard-of-priorities\" width=\"606\" height=\"455\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>You Shouldn’t Have Bought Him It!</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>When technology meets age, this is what to expect. No one in this selfie should blame the old man. The birthday present just got into use right away and now everyone seems embarrassed, but how was he to use it?</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-851 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/You-Shouldn’t-Have.jpg\" alt=\"you-shouldnt-have\" width=\"592\" height=\"429\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Perfect Positioning</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Is it the lighting or the positioning that is making this selfie incredibly hot? Well, any professional photographer knows that this hottie got the blend just right and you do need to be told the results.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-852 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Perfect-Positioning.jpg\" alt=\"perfect-positioning\" width=\"604\" height=\"453\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>The One Selfie That Was Worth It</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>You look at most selfies and wonder why some people bought selfie sticks. But this is one selfie that will answer you all that. You feel the urge to be involved, the indulge is just uncontrollable and this selfie just won it all. It is brilliant and all you feel is to be in it!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-853 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/The-One-Selfie-That-Was.jpg\" alt=\"the-one-selfie-that-was\" width=\"527\" height=\"395\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Another Example Of Parents Who Aren’t Ready</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>What is happening to mum and dad! Probably the next generation will be a traumatized one.  These are some of the things you promised never to leave behind and settle down as parents? Well, this could be a recipe for disaster in future!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-854 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Another-Example.jpg\" alt=\"another-example\" width=\"582\" height=\"387\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Going For A Swim</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Jump in hottie! And that moment had to be captured, right? Question is, does the camera know the landing point? I bet not. This lady is on a thrill and swimming is never an issue for her to stay off the camera.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-855 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Going-For-A-Swim.jpg\" alt=\"going-for-a-swim\" width=\"604\" height=\"457\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>View From Above</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Selfies have gone a notch higher and this girl is probably on the wheels. She knows what to do and how to hold her phone so as to leave the world on cringe. I bet the bikini is about to burst open and let the oozing beauty off!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-856 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/View-From-Above-1024x1018.jpg\" alt=\"view-from-above\" width=\"603\" height=\"600\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>Public Displays</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>It does not matter the setting, this hottie had to capture the moment. A snick-pick on her curvy body will tell you why nothing would have stopped her from taking the selfie. Is she working or on some break? Anyway, it does not bother anyone, it matters that she got the selfie just right!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-857 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Public-Displays.jpg\" alt=\"public-displays\" width=\"533\" height=\"529\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h2><strong>What To Expect When You’re Expecting</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>I do not know the recipient of this selfie but the idea was truly genius. You can always lift a leg onto a sink and stay off the bending. Your phone can do the rest and what to expect is just magical. Take a look!</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-858 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/What-To-Expect.jpg\" alt=\"what-to-expect\" width=\"591\" height=\"438\" /><!