.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-918 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Charles-E.-Blake.jpg\" alt=\"charles-e-blake\" width=\"588\" height=\"433\" />\r\n<h2><strong><!--nextpage-->Robert Tilton $500,000</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>At some point, the renowned televangelist earned $80 million yearly through his Success-N-Life infomercial. Tilton was accused of taking advantage of the vulnerable people.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-919 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Robert-Tilton.jpg\" alt=\"robert-tilton\" width=\"552\" height=\"436\" />\r\n<h2><strong><!--nextpage-->Paul Cain $1Million</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>At 18 years, Cain became a minister in Europe for the Voice of Healing Revival back in the 40s. He has made a fortune while struggling with homosexuality and alcoholism problems.</h3>\r\n<a id=\"amznPsBmLink_967733\" class=\"amzn_ps_bm_il\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Paul-Cain-Omnibus-Originally-Published-ebook/dp/B00GXSG6WE/ref=as_li_bk_ia/?tag=lpvg90-20&amp;linkId=138b9ddac36033728335766a1fcb471b&amp;linkCode=kia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-amzn-ps-bm-keyword=\"paul-cain\" data-amzn-link-id=\"138b9ddac36033728335766a1fcb471b\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-920 alignleft\" src=\"http://feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Paul-Cain.jpg\" alt=\"paul-cain\" width=\"536\" height=\"382\" /><!--nextpage--></a><img id=\"amznPsBmPixel_967733\" style=\"border: none !important; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; width: 0px !important;\" src=\"https://ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?source=bk&amp;t=lpvg90-20&amp;bm-id=default&amp;l=kia&amp;linkId=138b9ddac36033728335766a1fcb471b&amp;_cb=1477642974082\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Charles Stanley $1.5 Million</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Stanley became a minister at the age of 14 years. He owns a worldwide radio network and TV program. He has a Master of Theology, Do