selves. But sometimes, the choice of their hearts can be quite surprising. Here are 30 celebrity couples that you might be surprised as to how they ended up together.</h2>\r\n<h1>30. Chris Evans and Jenny Slate</h1>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1148\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-evans.jpg\" alt=\"Mandatory Credit: Photo by Dave Allocca/Starpix/REX/Shutterstock (5736897aa) Jenny Slate, Chris Evans Universal Pictures and Illumination Entertainment Present The Premiere of \'The Secret Life of Pets\', New York, USA - 25 Jun 2016\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h3>The \"Captain America\" star, who has enjoyed incredible success in recent years, began dating the former Saturday Night Live actress in early 2016.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>29. Emma Watson and William Knight</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1155\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emma-watson.jpg\" alt=\"emma-watson\" width=\"549\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<h3>With the Harry Potter saga behind her, Emma Watson has moved on to new and different projects. Meanwhile, she has been dating tech entrepreneur and businessman William \"Mack\" Knight.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>28. Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley</h1>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1174\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/tom-hardy.jpg\" alt=\"LONDON, ENGLAND - SEPTEMBER 03:  Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley attend the UK Premiere of &quot;Legend&quot; at Odeon Leicester Square on September 3, 2015 in London, England.  (Photo by John Phillips/Getty Images)\" width=\"328\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>Rising star and British heartthrob Tom Hardy and actress Charlotte Riley have been together since meeting on the set of the 2009 TV film \"Wuthering Heights\". They have been married since 2014.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>27. Scarlett Johansson and Romain Dauriac</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1170\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac.jpg\" alt=\"scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac\" width=\"388\" height=\"483\" />\r\n<h3>Previously married to Ryan Reynolds, the gorgeous actress has been married to French journalist Romain Dauriac since 2014.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>26. Jennifer Lawrence and Darren Aronofsky</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1156\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"362\" height=\"496\" />\r\n<h3>One of Hollywood\'s hottest names, Jennifer Lawrence is enjoying incredible success on the big screen – and off it. She is currently dating \"Requiem for a Dream\" director Darren Aronofsky.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>25. Sophie Turner and Joe Jonas</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1172\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sophie.jpg\" alt=\"sophie\" width=\"298\" height=\"481\" />\r\n<h3>The British star, known to audiences for her ongoing role on \"Game of Thrones\", has been dating \"DNCE\" lead man and former \"Jonas Brothers\" singer Joe Jonas.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>24. Ed Sheeran and Cherry Seaborn</h1>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1154\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ed.jpeg\" alt=\"Singer Ed Sheeran again out with his mystery lady this time at the Philadelphia Phillies Vs New York Mets at Citi Field on September 2, 2015 in the Flushing neighborhood of the Queens borough of New York City. Pictured: Ed Sheeran Ref: SPL1115780  030915   Picture by: Splash News Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles:	310-821-2666 New York:	212-619-2666 London:	870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"551\" height=\"342\" />\r\n<h3>English folk singer Ed Sheeran gained respectable fame over the past few years, releasing a number of critically acclaimed records. He first met his girlfriend Cherry Seaborn in high school, and the two started dating in 2016.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>23. David Cross and Amber Tamblyn</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1153\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/david-cross.jpg\" alt=\"david-cross\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<h3>Actor, stand-up comedian and director David Cross, of \"Arrested Development\" fame, has been married to actress Amber Tamblyn – who most recently appeared on \"Two and a Half Men\" – since 2012.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>22. Jason Sudeikis and Olivia Wilde</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1168\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/olivia.jpg\" alt=\"olivia\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<h3>A true Hollywood power couple, versatile comedy actor Jason Sudeikis and the former \"House M.D.\" Star Olivia Wilde have been engaged since 2013. The have two children together – a son and a daughter.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>21. Marcus Mumford and Carey Mulligan</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1166\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mumford.jpg\" alt=\"mumford\" width=\"480\" height=\"430\" />\r\n<h3>The \"Mumford and Sons\" lead singer broke into the limelight in 2012 with his band\'s Grammy Award winning album \"Babel\". He and his BAFTA award-winning wife Carey Mulligan have actually been childhood pen pals.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>20. Jeffrey Dean Morgan and Hilarie Burton</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1167\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/negan.jpg\" alt=\"negan\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<h3>The versatile actor, currently appearing on TV screens all over the world on \"The Walking Dead\" as the menacing Negan, has been together with former \"One Tree Hill\" star Hilarie Burton since 2009.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>19. Jesse Eisenberg and Anna Strout</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1158\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jesse.jpg\" alt=\"jesse\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h3>The \"Social Network\" and \"Now You See Me\" star has been dating Anna Strout since 2002, with the couple experiencing a short breakup between 2013 and 2015. They are currently expecting their first child together.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>18. Maya Rudolph and Paul Thomas Anderson</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1164\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/maya-rudolph.jpg\" alt=\"maya-rudolph\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<h3>Comedian and former SNL cast member Maya Rudolph has been in a relationship with respected film director and screenwriter Paul Thomas Anderson since 2001. They have three children together.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>17. Chris Pratt and Anna Faris</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1149\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-pratt.jpg\" alt=\"chris-pratt\" width=\"550\" height=\"483\" />\r\n<h3>Chris Pratt is currently at the height of his career. His films are extremely successful and he seems to be loved by all. Pratt has been married to Anna Farris, of \"Scary Movie\" fame, since 2009.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>16. Daniel Radcliff and Erin Darke</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1151\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dan.jpg\" alt=\"dan\" width=\"549\" height=\"409\" />\r\n<h3>The child star, recognized by most people all over the world as Harry Potter, has been dating American actress Erin Darke since meeting her on the set of \"Kill Your Darlings\".<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>15. Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1157\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jennifer-aniston1-a.jpg\" alt=\"jennifer-aniston1-a\" width=\"352\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<h3>It took her some time to get over the over-publicized breakup from Brad Pitt, but Jennifer Aniston has finally found her soulmate in \"Mulholland Drive\" and \"Inland Empire\" actor Justin Theroux. The couple has been married since 2015.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>14. Anna Kendrick and Ben Richardson</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1145\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/anna-kendrick.jpg\" alt=\"anna-kendrick\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>Previously attached to some big names as Jake Gyllenhaal and Edgar Wright, the \"Pitch Perfect\" and \"Up in the Air\" actress has been seeing cinematographer Ben Richardson since 2014.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>13. Margot Robbie and Tom Ackerley</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1163\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/margot.jpg\" alt=\"margot\" width=\"550\" height=\"329\" />\r\n<h3>Young Australian actress Margot Robbie has found notable success in recent years, appearing in blockbusters such as \"The Wolf of Wall Street\" and \"Suicide Squad\". The gorgeous Robbie and British assistant director Tom Ackerley tied the knot in December 2016.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>12. Michael Fassbender and Alicia Vikander</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1165\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/michael-fassbender.jpg\" alt=\"michael-fassbender\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<h3>The Irish-German esteemed actor Michael Fassbender first met Swedish actress Alicia Vikander on the set of the film \"The Light Between Oceans\" in 2014, and the two have been together ever since.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>11. Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal</h1>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1162\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/leo.jpg\" alt=\"*PREMIUM EXCLUSIVE* New York, NY - Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal are spotted after dinner with a friend. The couple looks smitten and in love as they cuddle up while walking in the Big Apple. Leo and Nina keep it casual as they grab a smoke outside the restaurant. The actor is seen holding hands with the supermodel while talking to a friend. **Shot on August 18, 2016* AKM-GSI       August 21, 2016 To License These Photos, Please Contact : Maria Buda (917) 242-1505 mbuda@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com or  Mark Satter (317) 691-9592 msatter@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com www.akmgsi.com\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h3>Finally winning the Academy Award for best actor he worked so hard for, Leonardo DiCaprio has been with a fair share of girlfriends over his career. His latest girlfriend is Danish model Nina Agdal, with whom he has been dating since May 2016.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>10. Kate Mara and Jamie Bell</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1159\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kate-mara.jpg\" alt=\"kate-mara\" width=\"550\" height=\"429\" />\r\n<h3>After making her breakthrough on \"House of Cards\", Kate Mara went on to appear on the critically panned \"Fantastic Four\", where she met actor Jamie Bell. The two started dating in 2015 and got married in January 2017.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>9. Sofia Vergara and Joe Manganiello</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1171\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sofia.jpg\" alt=\"sofia\" width=\"309\" height=\"499\" />\r\n\r\nNamed as the highest paid actress in television in 2016 by Forbes, Sofia Vergara has been married to \"True Blood\" star Joe Manganiello since November 2015.<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>8. Sacha Baron Cohen and Isla Fischer</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1169\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sacha.jpg\" alt=\"sacha\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" />\r\n<h3>Comical mastermind Sacha Baron Cohen and his wife, Australian actress Isla Fischer, have been married since 2010. They have three children together: two daughters and a son.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>7. Chris Hemsworth and Elsa Pataky</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1173\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/thor.jpg\" alt=\"thor\" width=\"407\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>The \"Thor\" actor has been married to Spanish model and actress Elsa Pataky since 2010. The coupl