9:06:53','2017-01-22 09:06:53','',1178,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor-Swift-Cat.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1211,1,'2017-01-22 09:07:18','2017-01-22 09:07:18','<h2>We all love pets, and celebrities are no different. Whether they show them to the world or not, these celebs have the cutest pets you can find.</h2>\r\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth and Dora</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1192\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/liam-hem.jpg\" alt=\"liam-hem\" width=\"388\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<h3>Known for his role in \"The Hunger Games\" trilogy, Liam Hemsworth is a known dog lover, and has adopted a pet dog called Dora.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Lady Gaga and Miss Asia Kinney</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1190\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lady-gaga1.jpg\" alt=\"lady-gaga\" width=\"519\" height=\"518\" />\r\n<h3>Famous and successful singer and performer Lady Gaga has a black French Bulldog named Miss Asia Kinney. Miss Kinney is a pet model and has also appeared on television.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Cara Delevigne and Cecil The Bunny</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cara.png\" alt=\"cara\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>Cara Delevigne is a very successful young actor and model, but her bunny Cecil is successful in his own right. Cecil has a Twitter account as well as an Instagram account with thousands of followers on each one.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Taylor Swift and Her Cats</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1199\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor.png\" alt=\"taylor\" width=\"480\" height=\"475\" />\r\n<h3>Taylor Swift, besides being a pop sensation, is a known cat enthusiast. Her cats are named Dr. Meredith Grey and Detective Olivia Benson. Both cats have flourishing Instagram accounts.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Miley Cyrus\' Cats and Dogs</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1193\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/miley.png\" alt=\"miley\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h3>Miley Cyrus is a wonderful pet owner. She is known to adopt many pets – dogs, cats, rabbits and even a pig, once. Her current pet resume includes 6 dogs and 3 cats (that we know of).<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Paris Hilton and Peter Pan</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1197\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/paris.jpg\" alt=\"paris\" width=\"353\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>Paris Hilton\'s pets were always famous, and she is known to keep them by her side at all times. Her most famous current pooch, the Chihuahua Peter Pan Hilton, has over 39 thousand followers on Instagram.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ariel Winter and Chloe</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1203\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ariel.jpg\" alt=\"ariel\" width=\"539\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<h3>Ariel Winter of \"Modern Family\" fame has recently adopted a beautiful German Shepard and named her Chloe. Besides Chloe, Winter has 2 other dogs.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Justin Bieber and Esther</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1204\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bieber.jpg\" alt=\"bieber\" width=\"520\" height=\"515\" />\r\n<h3>Justin Bieber, the teen pop sensation and heartthrob, has a cute puppy named Esther Bieber. He also owns another pup named Phil.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Sirius Black</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1183\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-black.jpg\" alt=\"grande-black\" width=\"538\" height=\"538\" />\r\n<h3>Ariana Grande is apparently a Harry Potter fan, as she named her newest puppy Sirius Black, after a character in the Harry Potter series.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Toulouse</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1184\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-toulouse.jpg\" alt=\"grande-toulouse\" width=\"540\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<h3>Before adopting Sirius Black, Grande has adopted Toulouse from an animal shelter. Toulouse has since modeled for Coach.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Demi Lovato\'s Buddy</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1180\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/demi.jpg\" alt=\"demi\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3>Demi Lovato\'s pup named Buddy has his own Twitter following, with over 61 thousand followers on his account.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Kitty Purry</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1189\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Katy_perry_and_kitty_purry.jpg\" alt=\"katy_perry_and_kitty_purry\" width=\"472\" height=\"461\" />\r\n<h3>Katy Perry is an avid cat lover and has gone on record announcing it on various occasions. Her most famous cat is Kitty Purry, who made a cameo in Perry\'s \"I Kissed a Girl\" video.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Emmy Rossum and Cinnamon</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1182\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emmy-rossum.jpg\" alt=\"emmy-rossum\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<h3>Emmy Rossum of the TV series \"Shameless\" has a cute puppy named Cinnamon. She shares pictures of Cinnamon and her frequently on Instagram.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nikki Reed and Ian Somerhalder\'s dogs</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1209\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nikki-reed1.jpg\" alt=\"nikki-reed\" width=\"548\" height=\"517\" />\r\n<h3>The successful couple owns two dogs, and they make sure to post as many pictures of them on Instagram as they can. The dogs are named Enzo Reed and Nietzsche Somerhalder.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Anna Sophia Robb and Sir Ferguson</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1202\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/annasophia.png\" alt=\"annasophia\" width=\"549\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<h3>Anna Sophia Robb is a teen actor. She has appeared in numerous successful Hollywood films and is a proud owner of a pet dog named Sir Ferguson.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Iggy Azalea</h1>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1185\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/iggy.jpg\" alt=\"iggy\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Iggy Azalea has been in the spotlight for the past few years, releasing some hit singles. She owns a French bulldog who goes by the very long name of Shrinkabull Jam Don\'t Shake Like That Jelli Azalea.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kaley Cuoco and Ruby</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1205\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/caley.jpg\" alt=\"caley\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<h3>Kaley Cuoco is known for playing the character of Penny in \"The Big Bang Theory\". She also owns a cute little pup she has adopted from an animal shelter, named Ruby.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Diana Agron and Freddie</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1200\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/agron.jpg\" alt=\"agron\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" />\r\n<h3>The former \"Glee\" star also owns a cute French bulldog, who she named Freddie. She regularly posts pictures of Freddie on Instagram.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Chelsea Handler</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1207\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chelsea.jpeg\" alt=\"chelsea\" width=\"377\" height=\"502\" />\r\n<h3>American actress, television host and producer Chelsea Handler has a cute pup named Tammy.<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Miranda Kerr and Frankie</h1>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1194\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Miranda-Kerrr.jpg\" alt=\"Australian model Miranda Kerr looking beautiful in blue as she poses with her pet dog while 