www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/61.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1275,1,'2017-01-23 10:01:53','2017-01-23 10:01:53','','62','','inherit','open','closed','','62','','','2017-01-23 10:01:53','2017-01-23 10:01:53','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/62.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1276,1,'2017-01-23 10:02:00','2017-01-23 10:02:00','','63','','inherit','open','closed','','63','','','2017-01-23 10:02:00','2017-01-23 10:02:00','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/63.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1277,1,'2017-01-23 10:02:07','2017-01-23 10:02:07','','64','','inherit','open','closed','','64','','','2017-01-23 10:02:07','2017-01-23 10:02:07','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/64.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1278,1,'2017-01-23 10:02:12','2017-01-23 10:02:12','','65','','inherit','open','closed','','65','','','2017-01-23 10:02:12','2017-01-23 10:02:12','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/65.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1279,1,'2017-01-23 10:02:20','2017-01-23 10:02:20','','66','','inherit','open','closed','','66','','','2017-01-23 10:02:20','2017-01-23 10:02:20','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/66.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1280,1,'2017-01-23 10:02:28','2017-01-23 10:02:28','','featured','','inherit','open','closed','','featured','','','2017-01-23 10:02:28','2017-01-23 10:02:28','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/featured.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1281,1,'2017-01-23 10:52:51','2017-01-23 10:52:51','<h2>The 90\'s were hectic yet fantastic years. Audiences all over the world enjoyed countless wonderful series, sitcoms, and films. The women who appeared in these films and TV shows found a place in our hearts forever. We lived with them, we grew up with them, and we fell in love with them. But as time passes, each one of them went on a different way, and we have lost tracks of many of our favorite women of the 90\'s. Where did they end up?</h2>\r\n<h1>Sarah Michelle Gellar</h1>\r\n<h3>Sarah Michelle Gellar was a name on everyone\'s lips in the 90\'s. The talented actress rose to fame with her role in \"Buffy The Vampire Slayer\" and appeared in classics such as \"I Know What You Did Last Summer\" and \"Cruel Intentions\". Today, she is happily married to Freddie Prinze Jr. Gellar is set to appear on the TV sequel series to \"Cruel Intentions\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1214\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/1.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"549\" height=\"420\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Alicia Silverstone</h1>\r\n<h3>Alicia Silverstone had a very short yet very bright career. She won everyone\'s hearts as Cher Horowitz in \"Clueless\", but she pretty much disappeared afterward. Nowadays she is happily married and has one child with musician Christopher Jarecki.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1215\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"549\" height=\"481\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julia Louis-Dreyfus</h1>\r\n<h3>TV fans and viewers all over the world will always recognize Julia Louis-Dreyfus as Elaine from the legendary TV show \"Seinfeld\". Louis-Dreyfus appeared on shows such as \"SNL\" and \"Arrested Development\" since \"Seinfeld\" ended, but truly returned to the top recently with her hit TV show \"Veep\", for which she have won multiple Emmy Awards.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1216\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"549\" height=\"467\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tara Reid</h1>\r\n<h3>Tara Reid one truly one of the biggest names of the 90\'s. She starred in films like \"American Pie\", \"The Big Lebowski\" and \"Urban Legend\". Reid went through a series of plastic surgeries that destroyed her public image and took much of her beauty in the 2000\'s. Her last major big-screen appearance was on the \"American Reunion\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1217\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennie Garth</h1>\r\n<h3>We all know her as Kelly Taylor from \"Beverly Hills: 90210\". Jennie Garth continued to appear during the 2000\'s in shows like \"What I Like About You\" and \"Dancing With The Stars\". In 2014 she had her own TV reality show called \"The Jennie Garth Project\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1218\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"550\" height=\"355\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>The Spice Girls</h1>\r\n<h3>The Spice Girls were the hottest female music group of the 90\'s and made their mark on history as the highest-selling female group ever. During their 6 year run, The Spice Girls released numerous hit albums and singles. Since the band\'s split, Victoria married David Beckham, Mel B became a talent judge, Geri Halliwell became a judge on \"Australia\'s Got Talent\", and both Emma Bunton and Melanie C are still going strong in the music industry after going on a solo career each.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1219\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"550\" height=\"544\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Larisa Oleynik</h1>\r\n<h3>Larisa Oleynik was, for 90\'s kids all over the world, Alex Mack from \"The Secret World of Alex Mack\". She also starred on the big screen in \"10 Things I Hate About You\". More recently, Oleynik appeared on the shows \"Pretty Little Liars\" and \"Mad Men\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1220\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/7.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Melissa Joan Hart</h1>\r\n<h3>\"Sabrina The Teenage Witch\" was the TV show that gave Melissa Joan Hart, aka Sabrina, worldwide recognition. After the show\'s cancellation in 2003, Hart went on a hiatus from acting. Nowadays she has 3 children with her husband Mark Wilkerson.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1221\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"550\" height=\"417\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Love Hewitt</h1>\r\n<h3>The beautiful Jennifer Love Hewitt helped define the term \"It Girl\" in the 90\'s. She appeared in some major Hollywood films such as \"Can\'t Hardly Wait\" and \"I Know What You Did Last Summer\". She went off the radar for most of the following decade. Today, Love-Hewitt is married to Brian Hallisay with whom she has 2 children.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1222\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"548\" height=\"548\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Drew Barrymore</h1>\r\n<h3>Drew Barrymore is undoubtedly one of the biggest names of the 90\'s. She already made a name for herself during the 80\'s and kept her momentum in film going with roles in films such as \"Batman Forever\", \"Scream\", \"The Wedding Singer\" and more. Nowadays Barrymore sticks more to producing with her own production company, and has also opened a winery, self-entitled \"Barrymore Wines\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1223\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/10.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mary Louise Parker</h1>\r\n<h3>Mary Louise Parker rose to fame during the 90\'s with roles in \"The Client\", \"Mr. Wonderful\" and \"The Five Senses\". She continued to star in supporting roles during the 2000\'s and was the lead character of the critically acclaimed TV series \"Weeds\", a role for which she had won a Golden Globe Award.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1224\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/11.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tiffani Amber Thiessen</h1>\r\n<h3>Tiffani Amber Thiessen is known mostly for her role as Kelly Kapaowski on TV\'s \"Saved By The Bell\". She also appeared on \"Beverly Hills 90210\". Nowadays, Tiffani mostly appears on low-budget films; she also has a cooking TV show called \"Dinner at Tiffani\'s\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1225\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/12.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"550\" height=\"458\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mary-Kate &amp; Ashley Olsen</h1>\r\n<h3>The lovable sisters broke in Hollywood for playing in \"Full House\". They went on to become successful businesswomen on their own, appeared in several TV shows and films, and opened their own production company. Mary-Kate is married to Olivier Sarkozy, the half-brother of former French president Nicolas Sarkozy, while Ashley is currently dating Richard Sachs, an art dealer.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1226\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/13.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"549\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Candace Cameron</h1>\r\n<h3>Another alumni of the \"Full House\" cast, the teenage sensation of the 90\'s made all boys fall in love with her and all the girls look up to her as a role model. Since 2015, she is reprising her role as DJ Tanner on the Netflix revival of \"Full House\", \"Fuller House\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1227\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Heather Locklear</h1>\r\n<h3>Heather Locklear starred on the 90\'s hit show \"Melrose Place\", where she played the role of Amanda Woodward. She was nominated for a Golden Globe award a whopping 6 times. Locklear was engaged to her \"Melrose Place\" former co-star Jack Wagner, but the two separated in 2011.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1228\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"550\" height=\"406\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julia Stiles</h1>\r\n<h3>Julia Stiles rose to fame following the success of the film \"10 Things I Hate About You\", in which she starred alongside Larisa Oleynik and Heath Ledger. During the 2000\'s she starred in the \"Bourne\" trilogy, and had a supporting role in the critically acclaimed \"Silver Linings Playbook\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1229\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"548\" height=\"398\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gillian Anderson</h1>\r\n<h3>Scully from \"The X-Files\" is what comes to mind when we see Gillian Anderson\'s face, and with good reason – the show was an incredible hit and so was Anderson\'s portrayal of Agent Scully. After \"The X-Files\" ended Gillian appeared in some stage productions in London before coming back to the small screen for roles in TV shows such as \"Hannibal\". She recently reprised her role as Agent Scully on the TV revival of \"The X-Files\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1230\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"550\" height=\"458\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kerri Russell</h1>\r\n<h3>Kerri Russell starred in TV\'s \"Felicity\" from 1998 to 2002. During that time she became one of the most beloved girls of the 90\'s. Nowadays she mainly stars in supporting roles in films, as well as starring on the TV series \"The Americans\". She and her boyfriend Matthew Rhys have one child together.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1231\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Liv Tyler</h1>\r\n<h3>Liv Tyler made her real breakthrough in the critically acclaimed \"Armageddon\", and has since gone on to play some iconic roles in films such as \"The Lord of the Rings\" trilogy. Since 2014 Tyler has been starring in HBO\'s \"The Leftovers\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1232\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/19.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kate Moss</h1>\r\n<h3>Kate Moss was one of the top supermodels of the 90\'s; Every respectable fashion magazine had her on its cover. Although she was criticized for the most of her career for being overly thin, Moss continues to model all over the world to this very day.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1233\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/20.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"550\" height=\"429\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mayim Bialik</h1>\r\n<h3>Mayim Bialik was one of the most famous child stars of the 90\'s, playing the lead role in the hit TV show \"Blossom\" until the show\'s cancellation in \'95. She also starred in \"Don\'t Drink The Water\" under Woody Allen\'s direction and did voice work for a number of TV cartoons. Bialik took a break from acting to pursue a career in science, and earned a Ph.D. degree in neuroscience, before coming back with a bang (pun intended) to the small screen as Amy Farrah Fowler in the hit TV show \"The Big Bang Theory\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1234\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/21.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Neve Campbell</h1>\r\n<h3>Neve Campbell was one of the most prominent and recognizable actresses in Hollywood during the 90\'s. She starred on hit shows like \"Party of Five\", as well as on the big screen in films such as \"The Craft\", \"Wild Things\", and, of course, \"Scream\". Nowadays Campbell mostly keeps herself out of the public eye, appearing from time to time in small parts on TV.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1235\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/22.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Christina Aguilera</h1>\r\n<h3>The 90\'s were full of hits from Christina Aguilera, as she launched a music career which spans over 20 years to this day. She continues to release hits almost at the same rate she did all those years ago when she was a teen sensation.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1236\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Aaliyah</h1>\r\n<h3>Aaliyah was one of the most promising talents of the 90\'s. The singer-actress was on her way to what seemed to be a prosperous career, with album sales surpassing the 30 million mark and numerous film appearances. Her career was cut short tragically when she died in a plane crash in 2001.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1237\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.jpg\" alt=\"24\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Claire Danes</h1>\r\n<h3>Claire Danes made her debut in Hollywood in the 1994 film \"Little Women\". Later she starred as Juliet in \"Romeo + Juliet\" with Leonardo DiCaprio playing the role of Romeo in the film. She currently stars on the hit show \"Homeland\" as the main character, Carrie Mathison.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1238\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"546\" height=\"546\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Courtney Cox</h1>\r\n<h3>Monica from \"Friends\", the legendary 90\'s classic, Courtney Cox has enjoyed tremendous success thanks to the show. She also played the role of \"Gale Weathers\" in the highly successful \"Scream\" trilogy. Courtney enjoyed a somewhat quiet time during the 2000\'s before she was cast as the lead character in the loveable series \"Cougar Town\" which aired from 2009 to 2015.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1239\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/26.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"549\" height=\"369\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston</h1>\r\n<h3>Another star of the timeless classic TV show \"Friends\", Jennifer Aniston can arguably be considered as the most successful of the bunch in the post-\"Friends\" era. She still appears in big-budgeted romantic comedies today and is happily married to Justin Theroux.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1240\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpeg\" alt=\"27\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Christina Applegate</h1>\r\n<h3>Christina Applegate made her name recognizable worldwide with her role as Kelly Bundy in \"Married… With Children\". After the show\'s ending Applegate sought a film career, which she successfully developed and maintained to this day. She most recently appeared in the film \"Anchorman 2\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1241\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/28.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Denise Richards</h1>\r\n<h3>Denise Richards reached stardom during the 90\'s for her beautiful looks as well as for her roles in \"Starship Troops\", \"Melrose Place\", \"Seinfeld\" and \"Wild Things\". She was married to Charlie Sheen until 2006, and had some supporting roles on shows such as \"30 Rock\" and \"Two and a Half Men\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1242\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/29.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"550\" height=\"385\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gwen Stefani</h1>\r\n<h3>The former lead singer of \"No Doubt\", Gwen Stefani\'s unique voice and style made sure she would remain on the top of the music charts to this day. She has her name written on numerous number-one hit singles and albums and has released her third solo studio album in 2016 to favorable reviews.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1243\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/30.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Winona Ryder</h1>\r\n<h3>Wynona Ryder starred in some iconic roles in films such as \"Dracula\", \"The Age of Innocence\" and \"Little Women\", to name a few. She had struggled for years with anxiety and depression which caused her career to fade during the 2000\'s. She recently made a very successful comeback, though, starring in the hit TV show \"Stranger Things\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1244\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/31.jpg\" alt=\"31\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Rachael Leigh Cook</h1>\r\n<h3>Rachael Leigh Cook was the star of the classic film \"She\'s All That\", which was one of the most watched teen movies in the 90\'s. She also starred in \"Josie and the Pussycats\". Nowadays she focuses mainly on her marriage and on her family life with her husband Daniel Gillies.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1245\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/32.jpg\" alt=\"32\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Lacey Chabert</h1>\r\n<h3>Lacey Chabert played Claudia in \"Party of Five\", a role for which she became one of the most appreciated child actresses in the 90\'s. Nowadays most people recognize Lacey as her character from the 2004 hit film \"Mean Girls\", Gretchen Wieners.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1246\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/33.jpg\" alt=\"33\" width=\"550\" height=\"360\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Calista Flockhart</h1>\r\n<h3>Calista Flockhart was Ally McBeal from 1997 to 2002. The role made Flockhart a feminist icon and earned her a Golden Globe award in 1998. She has been married to \"Star Wars\" and \"Indiana Jones\" star Harrison Ford since 2010 and currently stars on the TV series \"Supergirl\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1247\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/34.jpg\" alt=\"34\" width=\"548\" height=\"548\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Michelle Williams</h1>\r\n<h3>The adorable Michelle Williams captured everyone\'s hearts when she played Jen Lindley on TV\'s \"Dawson\'s Creek\". She went on to have a respectable career in film, acting in critically acclaimed films such as \"Brokeback Mountain\" and \"Blue Valentine\". She has one child, Matilda Rose Ledger, with her former late husband Heath Ledger, who died in 2008.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1248\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/35.jpg\" alt=\"DAWSON\'S CREEK Pictured: Michelle Williams as Jennifer Lindley Photo Credit: © The WB/Andrew Eccles\" width=\"550\" height=\"397\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Brittany Murphy</h1>\r\n<h3>Brittany Murphy\'s acting talents cannot be overstated. She had her breakthrough in \"Clueless\", and went on to have a respectable and prosperous career, appearing in many films and receiving recognition for her parts. The beautiful actress tragically died in 2009 at the young age of 32, leaving fans all over the world to wonder \"what if\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1249\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/36.jpg\" alt=\"36\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jenny McCarthy</h1>\r\n<h3>The 90\'s Playboy Girl Jenny McCarthy also got a few acting gigs during the 90\'s. Since then she appeared in several more movies, most notably in \"Scary Movie 3\". She is currently married to actor Donnie Wahlberg.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1250\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/37.jpg\" alt=\"&quot;Die Sportskanonen&quot;. Im Bild: Jenny McCarthy. SENDUNG: ORF1, MO, 20.02.2006, 01:45 UHR. - Veroeffentlichung fuer Pressezwecke honorarfrei ausschliesslich im Zusammenhang mit oben genannter Sendung des ORF bei Urhebernennung. Foto:ORF/-. Andere Verwendung honorarpflichtig und nur nach schriftlicher Genehmigung der Abteilung ORF/GOEK-Photographie. Copyright:ORF-PHOTOGRAPHIE, Wuerzburggasse 30, A-1136 Wien, Tel. +43-(0)1-87878-14383.\" width=\"550\" height=\"382\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Janet Jackson</h1>\r\n<h3>Janet followed in the footsteps of her legendary brother Michael into music and released her first album, \"Janet\", in 1993. She also appeared in several films in the 90\'s including \"Poetic Justice\". Since then Janet has been keeping a lower profile, although she continues to make music.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1251\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/38.jpg\" alt=\"38\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Shannen Doherty</h1>\r\n<h3>Shannen Doherty starred in the 90\'s classic \"Beverly Hills: 90210\" for four seasons before she was dismissed from the show due to her feud with Tori Spelling. She also starred in the hit TV show \"Charmed\", but was let go after three seasons because of a personal feud yet again. She was diagnosed with breast cancer in 2005 and is currently still going through treatments for the disease.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1252\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/39.jpg\" alt=\"39\" width=\"550\" height=\"370\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Danica McKellar</h1>\r\n<h3>Audiences will recognize Danica McKellar as Winnie Cooper from \"The Wonder Years\", the TV series which went on from 1988 to 1993. She quit acting in the early 2000\'s and is now a mathematician.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1253\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/40.jpg\" alt=\"40\" width=\"548\" height=\"411\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Yasmine Bleeth</h1>\r\n<h3>Yasmine Bleeth starred in the classic TV show \"Baywatch\", which she joined in its 4<sup>th</sup> season. She was later let go and quit acting due to personal problems related to drug abuse.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1254\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/41.jpg\" alt=\"41\" width=\"531\" height=\"411\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Robin Tunney</h1>\r\n<h3>A 90\'s teen sensation, the talented actress Robin Tunney appeared in numerous films during her early years, with roles in \"Encino Man\", \"The Craft\", and \"Empire Records\". Nowadays she can be seen mostly on the TV screen, where she appeared in \"Prison Break\" and more recently on \"The Mentalist\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1255\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/42.jpg\" alt=\"42\" width=\"550\" height=\"427\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Shirley Manson</h1>\r\n<h3>Scottish singer-songwriter Shirley Manson gained fame as the lead singer of the alternative rock band \"Garbage\". Today she is married to a record producer named Bill Bush and sings for the re-united \"Garbage\" since 2012.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1256\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/43.jpg\" alt=\"43\" width=\"549\" height=\"318\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Brandy Norwood</h1>\r\n<h3>Brandy Norwood appeared on the TV show \"Moesha\" for 6 seasons during the 90\'s, and released some hit singles as part of her musical career. She was involved in a horrible car accident in 2006, after which her career took some time to recover. She released her 6<sup>th</sup> album in 2012.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1257\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/44.jpg\" alt=\"44\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tia &amp; Tamera Mowry</h1>\r\n<h3>The parental sisters were stars of the 90\'s sitcom \"Sister, Sister\", which went on to become the longest-running sitcom in the history of Warner Brothers. They also appeared in the films \"Twitches\" and its sequel \"Twitches 2\". Nowadays Tamera is married to Adam Housley, a Fox News correspondent, and Tia is married to Cory Hardrict.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1258\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/45.jpg\" alt=\"45\" width=\"550\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Danielle Fishel</h1>\r\n<h3>Danielle Fishel played Topanga on the series \"Boy Meets World\" and quickly became every 90\'s male teenager\'s crush. She recently reprised her role as Topanga on Disney\'s \"Girl Meets World\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1259\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/46.jpg\" alt=\"46\" width=\"551\" height=\"391\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Fairuza Balk</h1>\r\n<h3>Fairuza Balk had appeared in a fair share of films in the 1990\'s. Her resume includes roles in films such as \"The Worst Witch\", \"Return to Oz\", \"The Craft\" and \"American History X\". Nowadays Balk is mostly involved doing voice work for TV shows such as \"Justice League\" and \"Family Guy\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1260\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/47.jpg\" alt=\"47\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Amber Valletta</h1>\r\n<h3>The 90\'s Supermodel has enjoyed incredible success at the height of her career, modeling for some of the top brands in the world. She is now maintaining a strong career in acting and has appeared in several movies like \"Hitch\", \"Days of Wrath\" and \"Premonition\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1261\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpeg\" alt=\"48\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Stacy Dash</h1>\r\n<h3>Stacy Dash\'s first role was Dionne Davenport in \"Clueless\". She has continued acting, albeit in smaller roles and on smaller productions, and has been co-hosting the show \"Outnumbered\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1262\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/49.jpg\" alt=\"49\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Brittany &amp; Cynthia Daniel</h1>\r\n<h3>Sisters Brittany and Cynthia Daniel portrayed the Wakefield sisters on the TV show \"Sweet Valley High\". Since the show ended Brittany has continued to work as an actress, most prominently as a recurring character on \"It\'s Always Sunny In Philadelphia\". Cynthia is laying low, living with her husband and two children in California.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1263\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/50.jpg\" alt=\"50\" width=\"550\" height=\"237\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Elizabeth Berkley</h1>\r\n<h3>Elizabeth Berkley is mostly recognized as Jessie Spano from the hit 90\'s show \"Saved By The Bell\". Today she is married to Greg Lauren, an actor with whom she has one child.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1264\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/51.jpg\" alt=\"51\" width=\"550\" height=\"320\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Fiona Apple</h1>\r\n<h3>Gaining instant fame with the release of her single \"Criminal\" in 1996, Fiona Apple was considered one of the bad girls of the 90\'s. These days Apple still records music while going on tours and performing live.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1265\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/52.jpg\" alt=\"52\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jessica Biel</h1>\r\n<h3>Jessica Biel was first revealed to the world as Mary Camden in \"7<sup>th</sup> Heaven\". Her career blossomed since then, and she became one of Hollywood\'s top young actresses, starring in big-budgeted films such as \"The Illusionist\", \"Total Recall\" and \"Hitchcock\". She is happily married to Justin Timberlake, with whom she has a son.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1266\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/53.jpg\" alt=\"53\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Thora Birch</h1>\r\n<h3>Thora got her breakthrough in the film \"Hocus Pocus\" and went on to have a stellar and well-received performance in \"American Beauty\". Since then Thora has mainly appeared in some smaller films, mainly films made for television and numerous TV series.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1267\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/54.jpg\" alt=\"54\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Alanis Morissette</h1>\r\n<h3>Alanis Morissette released her debut album \"Jagged Little Pill\", in 1995, and gained famed immediately afterward. The Canadian musician-turned-actress has appeared on a number of TV series, including \"Weeds\" and \"Nip/Tuck\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1268\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/55.jpg\" alt=\"55\" width=\"549\" height=\"478\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Bridget Fonda</h1>\r\n<h3>Jane Fonda\'s niece Bridget Fonda has films such as \"The Point of No Return\", \"Jackie Brown\", \"It Could Happen To You\" and \"The Godfather Part III\" in her resume. She also starred in the film \"No Ordinary Baby\", for which she was nominated for a Golden Globe award. Nowadays Fonda is married to famous film composer Danny Elfman; the two have a son together, named Oliver.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1269\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/56.jpg\" alt=\"56\" width=\"548\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Courtney Love</h1>\r\n<h3>The former wife of Kurt Cobain and lead singer of the band \"Hole\", Courtney Love also starred in several films in the 90\'s, such as \"200 Cigarettes\" and \"Man on the Moon\". She is currently in recovery yet again from her ongoing drug addiction.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1270\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/57.jpg\" alt=\"57\" width=\"549\" height=\"318\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Leelee Sobieski</h1>\r\n<h3>Leelee Sobieski appeared in critically acclaimed roles in the films \"Deep Impact\" and \"Eyes Wide Shut\", as well as in the TV miniseries \"Joan of Arc\" where she played the titular character. Nowadays Sobieski is married to Adam Kimmel with whom she has two children, and acts mostly in independent films.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1271\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/58.jpg\" alt=\"58\" width=\"548\" height=\"377\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Téa Leoni</h1>\r\n<h3>The 90\'s were good to Tea Leoni, as she appeared in a number of TV sitcoms such as \"Flying Blind\" and \"The Naked Truth\". She also starred in the 1995 hit \"Bad Boys\" alongside Will Smith. Tea mostly appears on Television these days and was famously married to actor David Duchovny until 2014.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1272\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/59.jpg\" alt=\"59\" width=\"549\" height=\"369\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lopez</h1>\r\n<h3>Still considered one of the strongest names in the music industry, Jennifer Lopez started as a dancer on \"In Living Color\" and never looked back since then. She starred in several films during the 90\'s and the 2000\'s, but nowadays mostly sticks to releasing one hit after another.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1273\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/60.jpg\" alt=\"60\" width=\"550\" height=\"439\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Vivica Fox</h1>\r\n<h3>Vivica Fox had her fair share of acting gigs in the 90\'s. She appeared in \"Independence Day\", \"Batman &amp; Robin\", \"Soul Food\" and \"Teaching Mrs. Tingle\", to name a few. Today she can be seen on the TV series \"Empire\", in which she has a supporting role.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1274\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/61.jpg\" alt=\"61\" width=\"525\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Juliette Lewis</h1>\r\n<h3>Starring in Martin Scorcese\'s \"Cape Fear\" earned Juliette Lewis an Academy Award nomination, and propelled her career forward. She later starred in \"Natural Born Killers\", \"From Dusk Till Dawn\" and \"Strange Days\", amongst other films. She currently stars on ABC\'s \"Secrets and Lies\" and had a supporting role on the TV series \"Wayward Pines\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1275\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/62.jpg\" alt=\"62\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Christina Ricci</h1>\r\n<h3>After starring as Wednesday Addams in the film \"The Addams Family\", Cristina Ricci went on to star in many 90\'s films, such as \"Casper\", \"Now and Then\" and \"Sleepy Hollow\", to name a few. Today, Ricci is married to dolly grip operator James Heerdegen with whom she has a son.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1276\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/63.jpg\" alt=\"63\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Alyssa Milano</h1>\r\n<h3>Although she appeared in several roles as a child in the 80\'s, Alyssa Milano became known to audiences all over the globe for her roles on \"Melrose Place\" and \"Charmed\". She had a quieter time during the late 2000\'s after \"Charmed\" went off the air, but has recently been cast to partake in Netflix\'s \"Wet Hot American Summer\" which will air in 2017.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1277\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/64.jpg\" alt=\"64\" width=\"549\" height=\"308\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Sandra Bullock</h1>\r\n<h3>One of Hollywood\'s most prominent and respected actresses to this day, Sandra Bullock started her career back in the 90\'s, with roles in films like \"Speed\" and \"While You Were Sleeping\". Nowadays Bullock continues to act in big budgeted Hollywood films, and won the Academy Award for Best Actress for her role in the 2009 film \"The Blind Side\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1278\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/65.jpg\" alt=\"65\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mariah Carey</h1>\r\n<h3>The queen of the 90\'s and one of the best-selling female artists of all time, Mariah Carey reigned supreme over the charts in the 90\'s. She is still performing live and releasing new music, as well as appearing on her own reality show on E!, \"Mariah\'s World\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1279\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/66.jpg\" alt=\"66\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" />','Women Of The 90\'s: Then & Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','1213-revision-v1','','','2017-01-23 10:52:51','2017-01-23 10:52:51','',1213,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1282,2,'2017-01-24 11:18:07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2017-01-24 11:18:07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/?p=1282',0,'post','',0),(1283,2,'2017-01-27 09:16:47','2017-01-27 09:16:47','<h2>\"Neighbours\" is amongst Australian television\'s longest-running and most successful soaps. The show has been running from 1985 and has aired over 7,000 episodes to this day. With such a long time in the running, it\'s intriguing to stop and look where some of the show\'s cast are today.</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Guy Pearce – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Guy Pearce was one of the original members of the cast, and the show jumpstarted his acting career. He remained on the show for four years and portrayed the character of Mike Young.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1284\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/110.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"290\" height=\"440\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Guy Pearce – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>After leaving \"Neighbours\", Pearce moved to Hollywood, where he managed to get into the movie business and landed roles in some big-budgeted motion pictures. He appeared in some memorable roles in films such as \"Memento\", \"L.A. Confidential\", and \"The Hurt Locker\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1285\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"302\" height=\"434\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Liam Hemsworth also got his career started as a member of the \"Neighbours\" cast. He was on the show for one season, during which he portrayed Bridget Parker\'s love interest, Josh Taylor.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1286\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/310.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"306\" height=\"352\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Liam has also moved to bigger and brighter pastures in Hollywood soon after leaving the show. He has found success in Hollywood as well, playing in the blockbuster saga of \"The Hunger Games\" films as well as in \"The Last Song\" and \"The Elephant Princess\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1287\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"372\" height=\"411\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Madeleine West - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Madeleine\'s story regarding \"Neighbours\" is a truly spectacular one: The actress got was cast as Dee Bliss on the show just three days after getting an agent for the first time.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1288\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/510.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Madeleine West - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Madeleine has been away from \"Neighbours\" for a few years as she wanted to raise a family – in which she found great success, giving birth to 6 children. She recently got back to the show.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1289\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/67.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"549\" height=\"330\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jesse Spencer - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Famous actor Jesse Spencer also got his career started starring in \"Neighbours\". He spent six years on the show, portraying the character of Billy Kennedy, Libby, and Malcolm Kennedy\'s younger brother.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1290\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/71.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"550\" height=\"343\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jesse Spencer - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Jesse moved to Hollywood like many of his fellow \"Neighbours\" alumni. He enjoyed tremendous success on the critically acclaimed series \"House M.D.\" where he portrayed the character of Robert Chase, and can currently be seen acting in the series \"Chicago Fire\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1322\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/82.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Natalie Imbruglia - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>A young Natalie Imbruglia starred on the show as café/construction worker Beth, who had a complicated love life and went through some difficult relationships on the show.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1292\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/91.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"304\" height=\"371\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Natalie Imbruglia - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Natalie continued with her acting career after leaving the show but found the most success in music. She developed a career as a singer and has released five albums to date.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1293\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/101.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Delta Goodrem – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Delta Goodrem portrayed the shy Nina Tucker on the show. As the show went on, her character evolved and became more and more confident in herself.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1294\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/111.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"302\" height=\"401\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Delta Goodrem - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Delta followed the example of her character Nina Tucker and became a singer. She has released several well-received songs while continuing to act in between. She was also appointed as a judge on \"The Voice Australia\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1295\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/121.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"302\" height=\"399\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Alan Dale - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Alan Dale was one of the show\'s most devoted actors, as he appeared in over 800 episodes. He starred as Jim Robinson, who eventually died of a heart attack.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1296\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/131.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"301\" height=\"408\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Alan Dale - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Alan Dale found great success after being written off of the show, and has appeared in several TV series including \"Once Upon a Time\" and \"NCIS\" - and films, such as \"Captain America: The Winter Soldier\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1297\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/141.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"550\" height=\"396\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Dichen Lachman - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>The talented actress Dichen Lachman portrayed Rachel and Zeke Kinski\'s older sister, the rebellious Katya, for a whopping 103 episodes.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1298\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/151.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"399\" height=\"327\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Dichen Lachman - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Dichen\'s career has only gone upwards as time went by, as she has appeared in several successful TV series, such as \"Dollhouse\", \"The 100\", \"Shameless\" and \"Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1299\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/161.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Stefan Dennis – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>One of \"Neighbours\" original cast members and longest-serving cast members, Stefan Dennis portrays the much-loved character of Paul Robinson to this day.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1326\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/171.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Stefan Dennis – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Stefan has appeared in over 3,100 episodes of the show to this day, and has been its devoted cast member for over 30 years. He makes appearances on other shows from time to time, but his main commitment is and always has been to \"Neighbours\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1325\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/181.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"472\" height=\"323\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Craig McLachlan - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Craig McLachlan is a Gold Logie award-winning actor, musician, singer and composer. He portrayed the curly haired Henry Ramsay on the show.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1300\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/191.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"303\" height=\"374\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Craig McLachlan – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Nowadays Craig McLachlan is acting again after taking a hiatus to try his luck in music. He has continued to star in soap shows, and can be seen today on the show \"The Doctor Blake Mysteries\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1301\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/201.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Leah de Niese - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Leah de Niese joined the show\'s cast when she was only eleven years old. She appeared on the show as Miranda Starvaggi from 1994 all the way to 2001.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1302\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/211.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"319\" height=\"479\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Leah de Niese - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Nowadays Leah has already passed the age of 30. She mostly keeps to herself, and tries to stay away from the limelight. She was last seen in a supporting role on the show \"Twentysomething\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1303\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/221.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tom Oliver – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Tom Oliver is one of \"Neighbours\" longest-serving cast members, joining in 1985 and appearing in over 2,800 episodes to this day.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1304\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/231.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"396\" height=\"471\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Tom Oliver – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Tom Oliver quit the show at the age of 78, after almost 20 years of playing the role of lovable rogue Lou Carpenter. His final appearance on \"Neighbours\" came in December 2016.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1305\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/241.jpg\" alt=\"24\" width=\"345\" height=\"481\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Dean Geyer – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Dean Geyer was a contestant of \"Australian Idol\" before joining the show. He portrayed the character of Ty Harper while in \"Neighbours\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1306\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/251.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"472\" height=\"324\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dean Geyer – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>After his story arc on the show was completed, Geyer left for the US and joined the highly successful TV show \"Glee\", where he portrayed the character of Brody Weston.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1307\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/26.jpeg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"303\" height=\"407\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>David Hoflin – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Swedish-born David Hoflin joined the cast of \"Neighbours\" for one year in 2007. He played the character of Oliver Barns on the show.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1308\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.png\" alt=\"27\" width=\"331\" height=\"416\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>David Hoflin – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>David went on to appear in some very successful TV series, such as \"Supernatural\", \"Hawaii Five-O\", \"Crossbones\" and \"American Crime\". He can now be spotted portraying the main character of F. Scott Fitzgerald on Amazon\'s period drama series \"Z: The Beginning of Everything\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1327\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/281.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"316\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ben Mendelson – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Ben Mendelson appeared on the show for one year between 1986 and 1987. He portrayed the character of Warren Murphy, but left the show after just 19 episodes to star in the film that turned out to give him his big breakthrough – \"The Year My Voice Broke\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1309\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/291.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"295\" height=\"437\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ben Mendelson – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Mendelson went on to have a very successful career both in Australia and in Hollywood. He has appeared in some major blockbusters these past few years in particular – he portrayed antagonists on both \"The Dark Knight Rises\" and the \"Star Wars\" anthology film \"Rogue One\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1310\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/301.jpg\" alt=\"Premiere of the new Netflix original series \'Bloodline\' at the SVA Theatre - Red Carpet Arrivals Featuring: Ben Mendelsohn Where: New York City, New York, United States When: 03 Mar 2015 Credit: Ivan Nikolov/WENN.com\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>James Sorensen – Then</h1>\r\n<h3>A more recent member of the show\'s cast, James Sorensen has appeared on the show as the teenage single father Declan Napier.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1311\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/311.jpg\" alt=\"31\" width=\"334\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>James Sorensen – Now</h1>\r\n<h3>James has pretty much moved on from acting, choosing to become a doctor instead. He currently attends university in order to obtain his medical degree.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1312\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/321.jpg\" alt=\"32\" width=\"421\" height=\"470\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Natalie Bassingthwaighte - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Natalie\'s character on the show was the crazy Isabelle \"Izzy\" Hoyland. Her character provided some controversial and crazy storylines to the show.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1313\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/331.jpg\" alt=\"Editorial Use Only / No Merchandising Mandatory Credit: Photo by FremantleMedia Ltd/REX (853826kg) \'Neighbours\' Stefan Dennis and Natalie Bassingthwaighte Grundy TV Archives\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Natalie Bassingthwaighte - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>After leaving the show, Natalie decided to branch out into music alongside her acting career. She enjoyed some success in music, and was chosen to be one of the judges on the Australian version of \"The X-Factor\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1314\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/341.jpg\" alt=\"34\" width=\"314\" height=\"471\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Radha Mitchell - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Radha Mitchell started her (now long and prosperous) career on \"Neighbours\" in 1994 at the mere age of 21. She stayed on the show for 3 years, during which she portrayed the character of Catherine O\'Brien.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1315\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/35.png\" alt=\"35\" width=\"549\" height=\"472\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Radha Mitchell - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Radha went on to have a very successful career which is still in full swing even today. She has appeared in \"Man on Fire\", \"Finding Neverland\", \"Pitch Black\", \"Silent Hill\" and \"Surrogates\", and has won several awards.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1316\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/361.jpg\" alt=\"36\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Margot Robbie - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Hollywood hotshot Margot Robbie has also started her career with a role on \"Neighbours\". She portrayed Donna Freedman, a groupie who was overly-obsessed with Ty Harper, on the show.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1317\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/371.jpg\" alt=\"37\" width=\"331\" height=\"472\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Margot Robbie - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Margot has really made it in Hollywood these past few years and is considered one of the hottest names around in the industry. She had roles in major films including \"The Wolf of Wall Street\", \"The Legend of Tarzan\" and \"Suicide Squad\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1318\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/381.jpg\" alt=\"Mandatory Credit: Photo by Jim Smeal/BEI/BEI/Shutterstock (3511922jh) Margot Robbie 19th Annual Critics\' Choice Movie Awards, Arrivals, Los Angeles, America - 16 Jan 2014\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kylie Minogue - Then</h1>\r\n<h3>Kylie Minogue appeared on the show in the early stages of her career. She portrayed the character of Charlene \"Lenny\" Robinson.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1319\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/391.jpg\" alt=\"39\" width=\"328\" height=\"410\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kylie Minogue - Now</h1>\r\n<h3>Kylie Minogue enjoyed tremendous success in her career and became a pop icon. She has continued to act from time to time, but her main focus was her musical career, during which she had released 13 albums and countless hit songs.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1320\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/401.jpg\" alt=\"40\" width=\"379\" height=\"474\" />','The \"Neighbours\" Cast – Then & Now','','publish','open','open','','the-neighbours-cast-then-now','','','2017-01-27 09:16:47','2017-01-27 09:16:47','',0,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/?p=1283',0,'post','',0),(1284,2,'2017-01-26 11:10:44','2017-01-26 11:10:44','','1','','inherit','open','closed','','1-6','','','2017-01-26 11:10:44','2017-01-26 11:10:44','',1283,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/110.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1285,2,'2017-01-26 11:10:50','2017-01-26 11:10:50','','2','','inherit','open','closed','','2-6','','','2017-01-26 11:10:50','2017-01-26 11:10:50','',1283,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1286,2,'2017-01-26 11:10:55','2017-01-26 11:10:55','','3','','inherit','open','closed','','3-6','','','2017-01-26 11:10:55','2017-01-26 11:10:55','',1283,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/310.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1287,2,'2017-01-26 11:10:58','2017-01-26 11:10:58','','4','','inherit','open','closed','','4-5','','','2017-01-26 11:10:58','2017-01-26 11:10:58','',1283,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1288,2,'2