','','20','','inherit','open','closed','','20-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:01','2017-01-30 13:10:01','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/204.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1441,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:07','2017-01-30 13:10:07','','21','','inherit','open','closed','','21-4','','','2017-01-30 13:10:07','2017-01-30 13:10:07','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/216.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1442,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:12','2017-01-30 13:10:12','','22','','inherit','open','closed','','22-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:12','2017-01-30 13:10:12','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/224.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1443,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:18','2017-01-30 13:10:18','','23','','inherit','open','closed','','23-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:18','2017-01-30 13:10:18','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1444,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:25','2017-01-30 13:10:25','','24','','inherit','open','closed','','24-4','','','2017-01-30 13:10:25','2017-01-30 13:10:25','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1445,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:33','2017-01-30 13:10:33','','25','','inherit','open','closed','','25-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:33','2017-01-30 13:10:33','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1446,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:39','2017-01-30 13:10:39','','26','','inherit','open','closed','','26-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:39','2017-01-30 13:10:39','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/263.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1447,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:46','2017-01-30 13:10:46','','27','','inherit','open','closed','','27-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:46','2017-01-30 13:10:46','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/271.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1448,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:53','2017-01-30 13:10:53','','28','','inherit','open','closed','','28-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:53','2017-01-30 13:10:53','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/284.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1449,2,'2017-01-30 13:10:58','2017-01-30 13:10:58','','29','','inherit','open','closed','','29-5','','','2017-01-30 13:10:58','2017-01-30 13:10:58','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/294.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1450,2,'2017-01-30 13:11:05','2017-01-30 13:11:05','','30','','inherit','open','closed','','30-5','','','2017-01-30 13:11:05','2017-01-30 13:11:05','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/304.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1451,2,'2017-01-30 13:11:11','2017-01-30 13:11:11','','featured','','inherit','open','closed','','featured-3','','','2017-01-30 13:11:11','2017-01-30 13:11:11','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/featured3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1452,2,'2017-01-30 13:19:23','2017-01-30 13:19:23','<h2>Most people look better when they\'re young, that\'s no secret. The skin is smoother, the eyes sharper, and the hair fuller. Celebrities are just the same – their looks degrade as they get older. But not these stars. These stars get better looking with age: the older they become, the better they look. Check out the list and see if you agree!</h2>\r\n<h1>Robert Downey Jr.</h1>\r\n<h3>Robert Downey Jr. spent his early Hollywood days in a battle with various drug addictions, which clearly didn\'t help his boyish looks back in the day. Now he is considered one of Hollywood\'s hottest men while being the top-earning actor in the business for the past few years.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1421\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/116.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Joseph Gordon-Levitt</h1>\r\n<h3>Moviegoers got their first look of the then-teenager Joseph Gordon-Levitt when he appeared on \"10 Things I Hate About You\" in 1999. Back then he looked like the skinnier, less successful version of his co-star Heath Ledger. Today Joseph has gained some muscle weight, and has grown overall, and looks finer than he did in his early days.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1422\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/215.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Dwayne Johnson</h1>\r\n<h3>Dwayne \"The Rock\" Johnson started his career in wrestling, and wrestlers don\'t necessarily need to be beautiful and presentable. The Rock certainly wasn\'t, as this picture here from his early 20\'s shows. The move to Hollywood did well for old Dwayne, as he is one of the finest looking actors around, with an impeccable style and handsome looks that just keep getting better with time.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1423\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/316.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lopez</h1>\r\n<h3>Jennifer Lopez has been around for a long, long time. She was always adored by men and women alike all around the world for her beauty, as well as for her singing and dancing skills. It\'s unbelievable to think that J-Lo is nearing her 50\'s – as she looks better than ever, and keeps showing that at every opportunity.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1424\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/412.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston</h1>\r\n<h3>OK, Jennifer Aniston was always stunning. From her early days on \"Friends\", Jennifer has always been considered as one of Hollywood\'s prettiest actresses. But recent appearances in films such as \"Horrible Bosses\" (1&amp;2) and \"We\'re The Millers\" prove that her looks just keep getting better with age, even at 47. If you have any doubts, consider this: She was named the \"Most Beautiful Woman\" of 2016 by People Magazine.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1425\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/513.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Johnny Depp</h1>\r\n<h3>Johnny Depp is a case very similar to Robert Downey Jr. He\'s one of Hollywood\'s most appreciated and sought-after actors today, and while he was certainly a good looking young man back in his early boyish days, there\'s no denying today\'s Johnny is one of the hottest and sexiest men in the world. He\'s also approaching his mid-50s, mind you. Not that it shows.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1426\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.png\" alt=\"6\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>George Clooney</h1>\r\n<h3>To be honest, Clooney has always been good looking. But today he is the prime example of what every man wishes he would look like, no matter his age. There\'s no arguing that Clooney is one of the best looking men in the world. For him, age is not only not an issue, but a blessing.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1427\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/74.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicole Kidman</h1>\r\n<h3>The amazingly talented Australian actress Nicole Kidman has been considered a rare and true beauty since her early days. But today, even though she is nearing the age of 50, the beautiful blonde looks even more stunning, her looks stand in complete contrast with her age.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1428\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.png\" alt=\"8\" width=\"550\" height=\"353\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tom Cruise</h1>\r\n<h3>Tom Cruise is easily one of the most recognizable faces in Hollywood. With a prosperous career spanning over 20 years behind him, it\'s truly a wonder how that man has managed to maintain his good looks and to look even better than he did when he was younger. He\'s been named by People magazine as one of the 50 most beautiful men in the world for three times, and you can obviously understand why.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1429\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.png\" alt=\"9\" width=\"549\" height=\"349\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Charlize Theron</h1>\r\n<h3>It truly speaks volumes when you\'re having trouble identifying which picture is from the past and which picture is from the present. Charlize Theron\'s unique, stunning beauty is undeniable, but she manages to look better with each passing year. It\'s mind-boggling to think that these pictures were taken years apart.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1430\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/104.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Sean Connery</h1>\r\n<h3>Connery was a gorgeous young man when he played Bond, there\'s absolutely no doubt about that. But even at old age, the Scottish actor looks terrific, showing that for him looks don\'t fade – they improve.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1431\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/117.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"551\" height=\"551\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ryan Phillippe</h1>\r\n<h3>Ryan Phillippe has been around Hollywood since the 90\'s and has been consistently considered one of the industry\'s biggest heartthrobs. Age doesn\'t seem to affect dear old Ryan as well – on the contrary, he looks just as good today as he did back then. Maybe even better…</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1432\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/121.png\" alt=\"12\" width=\"551\" height=\"375\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Halle Berry</h1>\r\n<h3>Halle Berry was always a beauty, and while it certainly is true that it doesn\'t seem like she aged that much since the beginning of her career way back in the 90\'s, you could argue that the Academy Award-winning actress looks even better today. Her style and elegance just keep getting better and better. She is in top shape indeed – could you guess she is already 50 years old?</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1433\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/134.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julia Louis-Dreyfus</h1>\r\n<h3>There\'s something about Julia Louis-Dreyfus that just looks much better today than she did back in her \"Seinfeld\" days. Not that she didn\'t look great back then – but the \"Veep\" star has managed to keep her charm while becoming even better looking than before.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1434\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.png\" alt=\"14\" width=\"550\" height=\"289\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gwyneth Paltrow</h1>\r\n<h3>The veteran actress has been around for many years and was always considered a true beauty. What\'s truly astonishing about her is that she is in her mid-40s, but doesn’t look a day over 30. Gwyneth is as beautiful as ever no matter her age.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1435\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.png\" alt=\"15\" width=\"550\" height=\"350\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julianna Margulies</h1>\r\n<h3>Julianna Margulies undoubtedly looks more beautiful today than she did in her early years, but what\'s so amazing about that is that she does it without looking any older. She is as classy, elegant and sophisticated as they come, but never looks a day over 30 at worst.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1436\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.png\" alt=\"16\" width=\"550\" height=\"473\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Victoria Beckham</h1>\r\n<h3>Yes, Victoria Beckham was always famous for her good looks. But she is well in her forties now, and still looks just as gorgeous – if not more – as she was in her twenties. And this alone speaks volumes, doesn\'t it?</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1437\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.png\" alt=\"17\" width=\"550\" height=\"440\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Demi Moore</h1>\r\n<h3>Demi Moore has blossomed with every passing year. Time has turned this once beautiful young lady into a matured, stunningly gorgeous woman, and she still turns heads around wherever she goes.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1438\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.png\" alt=\"18\" width=\"550\" height=\"418\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kate Winslet</h1>\r\n<h3>Kate Winslet is another beautiful star that has shown us that it is possible to blossom even as we get older. She probably has some truly magical genes as she shines bright and beautiful even today, some 20 years after she got her start in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1439\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/19.png\" alt=\"19\" width=\"550\" height=\"418\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicole Richie</h1>\r\n<h3>Tuning down her troubled lifestyle has certainly helped Nicole Richie with her looks. Her early years were surrounded by controversy and some very brave fashion choices. Nowadays Nicole is just breathtaking, her beauty more balanced, her style more defined than ever before.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1440\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/204.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Blair Underwood</h1>\r\n<h3>Blair Underwood had a very boyish, round look back in his 20\'s. This look always gave away the impression that Blair is actually younger than he really was. Today he is 47 years old and looks simply fantastic – He could certainly pass for a 30-something-year-old.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1441\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/216.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Malcolm-Jamal Warner</h1>\r\n<h3>Back in the 90\'s, Malcolm was a cute, good boy looking kind of guy. Today he\'s looking much manlier and is a handsome young man by all accounts.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1442\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/224.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Uma Thurman</h1>\r\n<h3>While her eyes will never change and will stay as stunning as they are forever, Uma Thurman is still one of Hollywood\'s sexiest and most beautiful actresses at the age of 46. Wrinkles and other signs of old age just seem to stay away from her.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1443\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.png\" alt=\"23\" width=\"550\" height=\"363\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gabrielle Union</h1>\r\n<h3>Gabrielle Union joins this lists\' list of people that were already beautiful, to begin with. She has been gorgeous from the start, but it\'s truly amazing to witness how she just keeps looking better and better as time goes by; by all accounts, she looks even better today than she ever did.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1444\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.png\" alt=\"24\" width=\"549\" height=\"439\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kevin Bacon</h1>\r\n<h3>Being one of the most respected and loved actors in Hollywood must be doing wonders for your look, as Kevin Bacon proves once again that he just keeps getting better and better looking as the years go by. He looks nowhere near his true age of 58 years old and has managed to maintain his wonderful youthful look.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1445\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.png\" alt=\"25\" width=\"550\" height=\"377\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Beckinsale</h1>\r\n<h3>Kate Beckinsale started acting at a very young age. She was a pretty teenager-turned-gorgeous young woman, but as the years go by it seems like she\'s just getting more and more beautiful. Her face has lost its roundness and has a more refined chiseled look nowadays, which aids Kate\'s undeniable elegance.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1446\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/263.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"497\" height=\"497\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Justin Timberlake</h1>\r\n<h3>Something about Justin Timberlake\'s looks early in his career just feels off. Maybe it\'s the way he used to style his hair. Today, though, it\'s a completely different story, as Justin has turned into a stunning young man, whose good looks assured that his transition from music to the big screen would go as smoothly as can be.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1447\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/271.png\" alt=\"27\" width=\"549\" height=\"449\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Beyonce</h1>\r\n<h3>Beyonce was beautiful when she was younger too, sure, but today the pop star is absolutely gorgeous and serves as an example and as a role model for millions of women worldwide. Although she is fast approaching her 40\'s, Beyonce is looking better and prettier than ever.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1448\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/284.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper</h1>\r\n<h3>Bradley Cooper is consistently featured in every respectful magazine\'s list of the best looking men in Hollywood, and with good reason. Now in his early 40\'s, he looks undoubtedly better than he did even a decade before. He has perfected his rough yet stylish look and developed a sense of fashion like no other actor in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1449\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/294.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ryan Gosling</h1>\r\n<h3>Ryan Gosling got his major breakthrough in Hollywood when he starred in the 2004 film the notebook. The film\'s director Nick Cassavetes actually chose Gosling for the role because he thought he wasn\'t good looking. Gosling, of course, has gotten better and better looking as time went by and is widely considered to be one of the hottest men in Hollywood today.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1450\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/304.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />','30 Stars Who Look Better With Age','','inherit','closed','closed','','1420-revision-v1','','','2017-01-30 13:19:23','2017-01-30 13:19:23','',1420,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1420-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1454,1,'2017-01-31 17:10:04','2017-01-31 17:10:04','<h2>Most people look better when they\'re young, that\'s no secret. The skin is smoother, the eyes sharper, and the hair fuller. Celebrities are just the same – their looks degrade as they get older. But not these stars. These stars get better looking with age: the older they become, the better they look. Check out the list and see if you agree!</h2>\r\n<h1>Joseph Gordon-Levitt</h1>\r\n<h3>Moviegoers got their first look of the then-teenager Joseph Gordon-Levitt when he appeared on \"10 Things I Hate About You\" in 1999. Back then he looked like the skinnier, less successful version of his co-star Heath Ledger. Today Joseph has gained some muscle weight, and has grown overall, and looks finer than he did in his early days.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1422\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/215.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n