=\"madonna\" width=\"550\" height=\"397\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>5. Dr. Dre - $700 Million</h1>\r\n<h3>Emerging into the public eye as a member of the controversial Hip Hop group NWA, Dr. Dre is now one of the most respected names in the Rap scene as well as in the music industry. His record label Aftermath Entertainment is responsible for launching the careers of mega-stars Eminem and 50 Cent. Dr. Dre is also the founder of headphone company Beats Audio, which was sold to Apple for an estimated $3 billion.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1077\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Dr-Dre.jpg\" alt=\"1/7/2009 Las Vegas Nevada, CES -- Dr. Dre, record producer/rapper shows off his new headphones. Note- Mike Snider is writing something on this. Photo by Tim Loehrke, USAToday (Via MerlinFTP Drop)\" width=\"550\" height=\"359\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>4. Sean Combs (P. Diddy) - $750 Million</h1>\r\n<h3>Record producer, singer and businessman Sean Combs has reinvented himself countless times over the course of his career, and so he has managed to stay at the top of the music industry as a household name. Founder of successful record company \"Bad Boy Records\" and owner of his own clothing line \"Sean John\", Sean Combs\' fortune just keeps on rising.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1099\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Sean-Combs.jpg\" alt=\"CANNES, FRANCE - MAY 22: Sean Combs attends the \'Killing Them Softly\' Premiere during 65th Annual Cannes Film Festival at Palais des Festivals on May 22, 2012 in Cannes, France. (Photo by Gareth Cattermole/Getty Images)\" width=\"385\" height=\"501\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>3. Herb Alpert - $850 Million</h1>\r\n<h3>Herb Alpert started in the 1960\'s as a part of the \"Herb Alpert and the Tijuana Grass\" jazz group, and went on to become one of the industry\'s most powerful executives.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1083\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Herb-Alpert.jpg\" alt=\"herb-alpert\" width=\"509\" height=\"505\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>2. Andrew Lloyd Webber – $1.2 Billion</h1>\r\n<h3>Sir Andrew Lloyd Webber made his fortune composing musicals. Throughout his 50-year career Webber has composed some incredibly iconic music for operas such as \"The Phantom of the Opera\". His company, the Really Useful Group, is one of the largest and most successful theater operators in the United Kingdom.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1073\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Andrew-Lloyd-Webber.jpg\" alt=\"andrew-lloyd-webber\" width=\"502\" height=\"333\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>1. Paul McCartney – $1.24 Billion</h1>\r\n<h3>One of the most popular and respected musicians of the 20<sup>th</sup> century, Paul McCartney started out with The Beatles, where he helped propel them to worldwide and historical success. After the band\'s breakup, McCartney started an almost equally successful solo career, during which the Guinness World Records crowned him \"The most successful composer and recording artist of all time\".  To this day, there is no concert hall in the world that McCartney won\'t be able to fill up completely.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1102\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Paul-McCartney-2.png\" alt=\"paul-mccartney-2\" width=\"551\" height=\"379\" />','Top Richest Musicians And Their Net Worth','','inherit','closed','closed','','1071-revision-v1','','','2017-01-31 17:34:16','2017-01-31 17:34:16','',1071,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1071-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1458,1,'2017-01-31 17:34:57','2017-01-31 17:34:57','<h2>We think we know everything there is to know about our favorite stars. We know where they live, who they\'re dating, and sometimes even what their children look like. But we don\'t always know everything there is to know about their family and life before stardom. Most stars have siblings, sure. But the siblings of stars on our list are not just their siblings – they are their twins. Check out our list of famous celebrities who actually have twin siblings!</h2>\r\n<h1>Eva &amp; Joy Green</h1>\r\n<h3>That one\'s surprising. The stunning, talented actress Eva Green, who appeared in numerous high-profile films such as \"The Dreamers\", \"Sin City: A Dame To Kill For\", \"300: Rise of an Empire\" and was, of course, a bond girl on \"Casino Royale\", has a twin sister named Joy. Eva has gone on record stating that her sister and she are very different from each other. Unlike Eva, Joy has studied business and is married to an Italian count; the two live in Normandy, France.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1413\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/115.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ashton &amp; Michael Kutcher</h1>\r\n<h3>Ashton Kutcher\'s twin Michael is more known and famous to the world because of Ashton\'s great commitment for him. Michael is two minutes younger than Ashton, and was diagnosed with Cerebral Palsy as a child and went through a heart transplant when he was only 13. Ashton has been fighting to raise awareness for the condition ever since; He considers Michael to be his best friend, and the two are as close as can be.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1414\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/214.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"550\" height=\"438\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Charlotte &amp; Samantha Ronson</h1>\r\n<h3>Did you know these two were related? Did you know they were twins? Charlotte is a highly successful fashion designer, while her twin sister Samantha is one of the world\'s most famous and most appreciated DJ\'s. The family\'s creative genes didn\'t end with them, as the twins\' older brother Mark is one of the best music producers in the world.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1415\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/315.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"401\" height=\"470\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Scarlett &amp; Hunter Johansson</h1>\r\n<h3>Scarlett\'s twin brother Hunter Johansson is a foot taller than her and has a different hair color. So they may not be that identical, but they sure are twins. Hunter doesn\'t shy away from the limelight and Scarlett takes him to accompany her to many high-profile events, showing the whole world how proud she is of her younger-by-three-minutes brother.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1416\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/411.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"549\" height=\"546\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Vin Diesel &amp; Paul Vincent</h1>\r\n<h3>Yes, that\'s correct, the \"Fast and Furious\" star has a twin brother. Vin is a highly respected and loved actor in Hollywood, appearing in films consistently over the past 15 years. His twin brother Paul also works in the film industry, albeit behind the scenes – as a film editor.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1417\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/512.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"495\" height=\"380\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gisele and Patricia Bundchen</h1>\r\n<h3>Gisele was raised in Brazil along with five sisters (you read that right), Gabi, Graziela, Raquel, Rafaela, and Patricia. What\'s so special about Patricia, though, is that she\'s actually Gisele\'s fraternal twin. They took a modeling course together way back in 1993, with Patricia opting to go for a different career (unfortunately). Gisele went on to become one of the world\'s top supermodels. Gisele\'s beauty simply cannot be denied, but Patricia definitely could have made it big in modeling too.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1384\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/69.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"550\" height=\"473\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Barbara Pierce Bush &amp; Jenna Bush Hager</h1>\r\n<h3>These two are known mostly because of their father, George W. Bush, who was the President of the United States from 2001 to 2009. Both high achievers, Barbara is a Yale grad and the co-founder of Global Health Corps, a non-profit organization, while Jenna is a known contributor to NBC\'s \"Nightly News\" and is a correspondent for \"The Today Show\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1385\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/73.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"550\" height=\"485\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Linda &amp; Leslie Hamilton</h1>\r\n<h3>Linda Hamilton is famous all over the world for her role on the \"Terminator\" series. Her twin sister Leslie initially followed her into Hollywood, and acted as Linda\'s body double on the set of \"Terminator 2: Judgement Day\". She has chosen a different path since then, though, and is now working as a nurse.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1386\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/84.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Joseph &amp; Jacob Fiennes</h1>\r\n<h3>Joseph Fiennes is gaining momentum in Hollywood thanks to his role on the TV anthology series \"American Horror Story\". His twin brother Jacob works as a conservationist. The twins also have an older brother to look up to – Ralph Fiennes, who is one of England\'s most respected actors, and has appeared in films such as \"Schindler\'s List\", \"The English Patient\" and \"The Grand Budapest Hotel\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1387\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/93.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"548\" height=\"336\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Brittany &amp; Cynthia Daniel</h1>\r\n<h3>Brittany and her twin sister Cynthia have both famously appeared on the 90\'s TV show \"Sweet Valley High\", where they played – you guessed it, sisters. Brittany went on to appear on several TV shows, most notably on CW\"s \"The Game\". Cynthia quit acting after \"Sweet Valley High\" was canceled and became a photographer.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1388\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/103.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"431\" height=\"431\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mary-Kate &amp; Ashley Olsen</h1>\r\n<h3>You can\'t have a celebrity twins list without mentioning the most famous twins of the 90\'s. The power-twins rose to fame with their portrayal of the lovable Michelle Tanner in the 90\'s classic \"Full House\", and went on to appear in multiple films and shows together. They also founded some business together, and overall, seem to really enjoy each other\'s company.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1389\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/114.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"550\" height=\"518\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Olly &amp; Ben Murs</h1>\r\n<h3>Oliver \"Olly\" Murs is an English singer, songwriter, television presenter and actor, who rose to fame thanks to his participation in the sixth season of \"The X-Factor\", where he finished as the runner-up. He has a twin brother named Ben with whom he\'s usually on good terms, though Ben was angry with Olly for missing out on his wedding due to his participation in \"The X-Factor\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1390\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/12.png\" alt=\"12\" width=\"418\" height=\"350\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jon &amp; Dan Heder</h1>\r\n<h3>Jon Heder is an actor known for Napoleon Dynamite. He has an identical twin, Dan, with whom he used to prank people as a child, with each of the two pretending to be the other. They own a production company together, while Dan\'s main work is behind the scenes on visual effects.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1391\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/133.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Aaron &amp; Shawn Ashmore</h1>\r\n<h3>Talk about identical twins! The Ashmore Twins, Aaron and Shawn, simply couldn\'t look any similar. They are both actors and have enjoyed great success in their respective careers. Shawn has famously starred as Iceman in the \"X-Men\" film series, while Aaron famously starred on the TV series \"Smallville\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1392\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/143.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"549\" height=\"397\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Siva &amp; Kumar Kaneswaran</h1>\r\n<h3>Siva Kumar is a member of the British successful boy band \"The Wanted\". He was also a model before turning his focus to music and rising to fame with his band. He has an identical twin brother, Kumar. They really are identical!</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1393\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/153.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"548\" height=\"336\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tiki &amp; Ronde Barber</h1>\r\n<h3>Tiki and Ronde Barber have both started their careers playing football in the NFL. Tiki has moved on from football to become an on-air personality, while Ronde has remained in the NFL and is now playing for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1394\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/163.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"549\" height=\"337\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Aimee Ann &amp; Katy Ann Duffy</h1>\r\n<h3>Aimee Ann Duffy is a singer who is best known for her hit records \"Mercy\" and \"Warwick Avenue\". She has a twin sister named Katy Ann and an older sister named Kelly and is known to write songs about both of them.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1395\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/173.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"548\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Alanis &amp; Wade Morissette</h1>\r\n<h3>Born 12 minutes apart, Alanis\' twin brother Wade is a multi talented person: He\'s an indie pop-rock musician, an author, a therapist and a yoga instructor. Alanis and Wade are reportedly on great terms with one another, with Alanis stating that she\'s a great admirer of her twin brother\'s music.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1396\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/183.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"551\" height=\"432\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jason &amp; Jeremy London</h1>\r\n<h3>The London twins are similar in their career choices as well as in their looks, having both chosen to become actors. Jason has appeared on \"Dazed and Confused\", while Jeremy appeared on \"7<sup>th</sup> Heaven\" and \"Party of Five\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1397\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/193.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"448\" height=\"470\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Benji &amp; Joel Madden</h1>\r\n<h3>The Madden twins sure look alike! They are known to the world as members of the band \"Good Charlotte\". Their talents ensured them success in music while their good looks ensured them success with the ladies, as Benji is known to have dated Paris Hilton and Holly Madison while Joel has once dated Hilary Duff and is now married to Nicole Richie.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1398\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/203.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"332\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dylan &amp; Cole Sprouse</h1>\r\n<h3>Dylan and Cole Sprouse are another pair of twins that made it big together, taking full advantage of their status. They rose to fame after appearing in Adam Sandler\'s 1999 film \"Big Daddy\", and went on to star on a show of their own – \"Suite Life of Zach &amp; Cody\" on the Disney channel, and its spin-off series \"Suite Life On Deck\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1399\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/213.jpg\" alt=\"LONDON, ENGLAND - JANUARY 29: (l-r) Actors Cole Sprouse and Dylan Sprouse arrive to teach a Master Workshop on acting, hosted by Celebrity Talent Academy and Starlight Children\'s Foundation at the Cochrane Theatre on January 29, 2011 in London, England. (Photo by Tim Whitby/Getty Images)\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tia &amp; Tamera Mowry</h1>\r\n<h3>Another pair of twins who rose to fame during the 90\'s, Tia and Tamera Mowry starred on the ABC show \"Sister, Sister\" which lasted a long six seasons. They later appeared on the Disney Channel\'s original films \"Twitches\" and \"Twitches Too\", and starred on their own reality TV series \"Tia &amp; Tamera\", which followed and chronicled their lives. They sure make the most out of being twins!</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1400\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/223.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"549\" height=\"503\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Aaron &amp; Angel Carter</h1>\r\n<h3>Aaron and Angel are Nick Carter\'s (of the Backstreet Boys) younger siblings. Aaron went on to become a successful musician in his own right, while the stunning Angel chose to pursue a career in modeling, in which she has found success too.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1401\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/233.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"331\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kiefer &amp; Rachel Sutherland</h1>\r\n<h3>Kiefer Sutherland has followed in his famous father Donald\'s shoes, making a name for himself in Hollywood as the star of the highly successful TV series \"24\". His twin sister Rachel, who is seven minutes younger than him, chose a different path and became a television post-production supervisor.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1402\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/243.jpg\" alt=\"TORONTO - MARCH 24: Actress Shirley Douglas and her daughter Rachel Sutherland arrive at the gala premiere \'Lord of the Rings\' play on March 24, 2006 in Toronto, Canada. (Photo by Jim Ross/Getty Images)\" width=\"457\" height=\"469\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Parker &amp; Christopher Posey</h1>\r\n<h3>Unlike his famous sister Parker, who starred in classic films such as \"Dazed and Confused\" and \"Best in Show\", Christopher Posey has chosen to stay out of the limelight, and little is known about him, other than the fact that he is a lawyer.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1403\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/253.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"424\" height=\"471\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Elvis &amp; Jessie Presley</h1>\r\n<h3>Elvis\' twin brother, who was famously born 35 minutes before him, was sadly stillborn. Many mysteries and conspiracy theories revolve around Elvis\' lost twin brother: some claim that he was the force behind both Elvis\' creativity and his self-destructive tendencies, as Elvis would hear his brother speak to him in his head. Some go as far as to claim that Jessie never died – his death certificate was faked and he is alive and well today.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1404\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/262.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"548\" height=\"411\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Judy &amp; Joselin Reyes</h1>\r\n<h3>Judy Reyes\' most famous and high-profile role was that of nurse Carla Espinoza on the beloved TV series \"Scrubs\". Her twin sister, Joselin, actually played her sister on one of the episodes of the show. She is an actress herself, and has also appeared on several episodes of \"Law &amp; Order\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1405\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/272.jpg\" alt=\"27\" width=\"420\" height=\"410\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicholas Brendon &amp; Kelly Donovan</h1>\r\n<h3>Nicholas Brendon is recognizable to TV audiences from his role as Xander Harris on the beloved TV show \"Buffy The Vampire Slayer\". His brother, Kelly Donovan, has actually worked with Nicholas on the show and was his stand-in for many of his scenes on it.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1406\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/283.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Rami &amp; Sami Malek</h1>\r\n<h3>Rami Malek has risen to fame thanks to his critically-acclaimed role on the successful TV series \"Mr. Robot\", in which he plays the main character, Elliot Alderson. He has a twin brother named Sami who is four minutes younger than him, works as a middle school teacher, and considered by many fans to be even better looking than his famous brother.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1407\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/293.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"304\" height=\"479\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>James &amp; Oliver Phelps</h1>\r\n<h3>The ginger Phelps brothers rose to fame when they landed the roles of Fred and George Weasley in the film series adaptation of the \"Harry Potter\" book series. They have appeared in all of the series\' films – 8, to be exact, and have gained a following thanks to what many fans considered their faithful representation of the characters.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1408\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/303.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jill &amp; Jacqueline Hennessey</h1>\r\n<h3>The Canadian beauties have established themselves as strong TV personalities. Jacqueline hosted a Canadian show called \"Medical Intelligence\", while Jill appeared on some popular American shows such as \"Law and Order\" and \"Crossing Jordan\".</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1409\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/314.jpg\" alt=\"31\" width=\"413\" height=\"390\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Giovanni and Marissa Ribisi</h1>\r\n<h3>Giovanni Ribisi is a highly respected actor and has shown his talents on some of Hollywood\'s most memorable films of the last two decades, playing a variety of well-received characters. His twin sister, while not as known or as accomplished as he is, appeared in several films too, such as in \"Dazed and Confused\" and \"Pleasantville\". Marissa is also married to famous musician Beck.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1410\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/323.jpg\" alt=\"32\" width=\"328\" height=\"470\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Willow &amp; Autumn Shields</h1>\r\n<h3>Willow Shields in best known for her work on \"The Hunger Games\" film series, where she played Primrose Everdeen alongside Jennifer Lawrence. Her twin sister, Autumn, with whom she has a very close and warm relationship, is also an actress.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1411\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/333.jpg\" alt=\"33\" width=\"433\" height=\"480\" /> <!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Mo &amp; Hassan Farah</h1>\r\n<h3>Recently-knighted Olympic and World Champion runner Sir Mo Farah has a twin brother named Hassan. Hassan actually stayed behind in Somalia when Mo left to England with his father. The two waited for 12 years before meeting again, and are now as close as can be.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1412\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/343.jpg\" alt=\"34\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" />','Celebrities You Didn\'t Know Had Twin Siblings','','inherit','closed','closed','','1383-revision-v1','','','2017-01-31 17:34:57','2017-01-31 17:34:57','',1383,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1383-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1459,1,'2017-01-31 17:35:06','2017-01-31 17:35:06','<h2>Celebs tend to date amongst themselves. But sometimes, the choice of their hearts can be quite surprising. Here are 30 celebrity couples that you might be surprised as to how they ended up together.</h2>\r\n<h1>Chris Evans and Jenny Slate</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Captain America\" star, who has enjoyed incredible success in recent years, began dating the former Saturday Night Live actress in early 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1148\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-evans.jpg\" alt=\"Mandatory Credit: Photo by Dave Allocca/Starpix/REX/Shutterstock (5736897aa) Jenny Slate, Chris Evans Universal Pictures and Illumination Entertainment Present The Premiere of \'The Secret Life of Pets\', New York, USA - 25 Jun 2016\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Emma Watson and William Knight</h1>\r\n<h3>With the Harry Potter saga behind her, Emma Watson has moved on to new and different projects. Meanwhile, she has been dating tech entrepreneur and businessman William \"Mack\" Knight.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1155\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emma-watson.jpg\" alt=\"emma-watson\" width=\"549\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley</h1>\r\n<h3>Rising star and British heartthrob Tom Hardy and actress Charlotte Riley have been together since meeting on the set of the 2009 TV film \"Wuthering Heights\". They have been married since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1174\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/tom-hardy.jpg\" alt=\"LONDON, ENGLAND - SEPTEMBER 03: Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley attend the UK Premiere of &quot;Legend&quot; at Odeon Leicester Square on September 3, 2015 in London, England. (Photo by John Phillips/Getty Images)\" width=\"328\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Scarlett Johansson and Romain Dauriac</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously married to Ryan Reynolds, the gorgeous actress has been married to French journalist Romain Dauriac since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1170\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac.jpg\" alt=\"scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac\" width=\"388\" height=\"483\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Darren Aronofsky</h1>\r\n<h3>One of Hollywood\'s hottest names, Jennifer Lawrence is enjoying incredible success on the big screen – and off it. She is currently dating \"Requiem for a Dream\" director Darren Aronofsky.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1156\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"362\" height=\"496\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sophie Turner and Joe Jonas</h1>\r\n<h3>The British star, known to audiences for her ongoing role on \"Game of Thrones\", has been dating \"DNCE\" lead man and former \"Jonas Brothers\" singer Joe Jonas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1172\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sophie.jpg\" alt=\"sophie\" width=\"298\" height=\"481\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Cherry Seaborn</h1>\r\n<h3>English folk singer Ed Sheeran gained respectable fame over the past few years, releasing a number of critically acclaimed records. He first met his girlfriend Cherry Seaborn in high school, and the two started dating in 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1154\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ed.jpeg\" alt=\"Singer Ed Sheeran again out with his mystery lady this time at the Philadelphia Phillies Vs New York Mets at Citi Field on September 2, 2015 in the Flushing neighborhood of the Queens borough of New York City. Pictured: Ed Sheeran Ref: SPL1115780 030915 Picture by: Splash News Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"551\" height=\"342\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>David Cross and Amber Tamblyn</h1>\r\n<h3>Actor, stand-up comedian and director David Cross, of \"Arrested Development\" fame, has been married to actress Amber Tamblyn – who most recently appeared on \"Two and a Half Men\" – since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1153\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/david-cross.jpg\" alt=\"david-cross\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jason Sudeikis and Olivia Wilde</h1>\r\n<h3>A true Hollywood power couple, versatile comedy actor Jason Sudeikis and the former \"House M.D.\" Star Olivia Wilde have been engaged since 2013. The have two children together – a son and a daughter.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1168\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/olivia.jpg\" alt=\"olivia\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Marcus Mumford and Carey Mulligan</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Mumford and Sons\" lead singer broke into the limelight in 2012 with his band\'s Grammy Award winning album \"Babel\". He and his BAFTA award-winning wife Carey Mulligan have actually been childhood pen pals.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1166\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mumford.jpg\" alt=\"mumford\" width=\"480\" height=\"430\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jeffrey Dean Morgan and Hilarie Burton</h1>\r\n<h3>The versatile actor, currently appearing on TV screens all over the world on \"The Walking Dead\" as the menacing Negan, has been together with former \"One Tree Hill\" star Hilarie Burton since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1167\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/negan.jpg\" alt=\"negan\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jesse Eisenberg and Anna Strout</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Social Network\" and \"Now You See Me\" star has been dating Anna Strout since 2002, with the couple experiencing a short breakup between 2013 and 2015. They are currently expecting their first child together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1158\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jesse.jpg\" alt=\"jesse\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Maya Rudolph and Paul Thomas Anderson</h1>\r\n<h3>Comedian and former SNL cast member Maya Rudolph has been in a relationship with respected film director and screenwriter Paul Thomas Anderson since 2001. They have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1164\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/maya-rudolph.jpg\" alt=\"maya-rudolph\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Pratt and Anna Faris</h1>\r\n<h3>Chris Pratt is currently at the height of his career. His films are extremely successful and he seems to be loved by all. Pratt has been married to Anna Farris, of \"Scary Movie\" fame, since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1149\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-pratt.jpg\" alt=\"chris-pratt\" width=\"550\" height=\"483\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Daniel Radcliff and Erin Darke</h1>\r\n<h3>The child star, recognized by most people all over the world as Harry Potter, has been dating American actress Erin Darke since meeting her on the set of \"Kill Your Darlings\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1151\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dan.jpg\" alt=\"dan\" width=\"549\" height=\"409\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux</h1>\r\n<h3>It took her some time to get over the over-publicized breakup from Brad Pitt, but Jennifer Aniston has finally found her soulmate in \"Mulholland Drive\" and \"Inland Empire\" actor Justin Theroux. The couple has been married since 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1157\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jennifer-aniston1-a.jpg\" alt=\"jennifer-aniston1-a\" width=\"352\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Anna Kendrick and Ben Richardson</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously attached to some big names as Jake Gyllenhaal and Edgar Wright, the \"Pitch Perfect\" and \"Up in the Air\" actress has been seeing cinematographer Ben Richardson since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1145\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/anna-kendrick.jpg\" alt=\"anna-kendrick\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Margot Robbie and Tom Ackerley</h1>\r\n<h3>Young Australian actress Margot Robbie has found notable success in recent years, appearing in blockbusters such as \"The Wolf of Wall Street\" and \"Suicide Squad\". The gorgeous Robbie and British assistant director Tom Ackerley tied the knot in December 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1163\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/margot.jpg\" alt=\"margot\" width=\"550\" height=\"329\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Michael Fassbender and Alicia Vikander</h1>\r\n<h3>The Irish-German esteemed actor Michael Fassbender first met Swedish actress Alicia Vikander on the set of the film \"The Light Between Oceans\" in 2014, and the two have been together ever since.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1165\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/michael-fassbender.jpg\" alt=\"michael-fassbender\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal</h1>\r\n<h3>Finally winning the Academy Award for best actor he worked so hard for, Leonardo DiCaprio has been with a fair share of girlfriends over his career. His latest girlfriend is Danish model Nina Agdal, with whom he has been dating since May 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1162\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/leo.jpg\" alt=\"*PREMIUM EXCLUSIVE* New York, NY - Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal are spotted after dinner with a friend. The couple looks smitten and in love as they cuddle up while walking in the Big Apple. Leo and Nina keep it casual as they grab a smoke outside the restaurant. The actor is seen holding hands with the supermodel while talking to a friend. **Shot on August 18, 2016* AKM-GSI August 21, 2016 To License These Photos, Please Contact : Maria Buda (917) 242-1505 mbuda@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com or Mark Satter (317) 691-9592 msatter@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com www.akmgsi.com\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Mara and Jamie Bell</h1>\r\n<h3>After making her breakthrough on \"House of Cards\", Kate Mara went on to appear on the critically panned \"Fantastic Four\", where she met actor Jamie Bell. The two started dating in 2015 and got married in January 2017.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1159\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kate-mara.jpg\" alt=\"kate-mara\" width=\"550\" height=\"429\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sofia Vergara and Joe Manganiello</h1>\r\n<h3>Named as the highest paid actress in television in 2016 by Forbes, Sofia Vergara has been married to \"True Blood\" star Joe Manganiello since November 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1171\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sofia.jpg\" alt=\"sofia\" width=\"309\" height=\"499\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sacha Baron Cohen and Isla Fischer</h1>\r\n<h3>Comical mastermind Sacha Baron Cohen and his wife, Australian actress Isla Fischer, have been married since 2010. They have three children together: two daughters and a son.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1169\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sacha.jpg\" alt=\"sacha\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Hemsworth and Elsa Pataky</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Thor\" actor has been married to Spanish model and actress Elsa Pataky since 2010. The couple are still going strong, and they have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1173\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/thor.jpg\" alt=\"thor\" width=\"407\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dave Franco and Alison Brie</h1>\r\n<h3>Often considered to be even prettier than his older brother James, Dave Franco has been dating beautiful actress Alison Brie since 2012, with the two becoming engaged in 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1152\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dave-franco.jpg\" alt=\"dave-franco\" width=\"360\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cobie Smulders and Taran Killam</h1>\r\n<h3>Canadian actress Cobie Smulders, of \"How I Met Your Mother\" fame, has been married to comedian and SNL cast member Taran Killam since 2012. Smulders and Killam have two daughters together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1150\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cobie.jpg\" alt=\"13 Mar 2014 --- Hollywood, CA - March 13: Cobie Smulders, Taran Killam Attending &quot;Captain America: The Winter Soldier&quot; - Los Angeles Premiere Held at El Capitan Theatre California on March 13, 2014. Photo Credit: Faye Sadou / UPA . --- Image by © Faye Sadou / UPA ./Retna Ltd./Corbis\" width=\"329\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kit Harington and Rose Leslie</h1>\r\n<h3>Known to all as Jon Snow from the hit TV series \"Game of Thrones\", British actor Kit Harrington is actually dating his former co-star Rose Leslie, who played Ygritte on the show. They have been together since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1161\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kit.jpg\" alt=\"kit\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Billie Lourd and Taylor Lautner</h1>\r\n<h3>Billie Lourd is a prime example of true Hollywood royalty: The daughter of the late Carrie Fisher and the granddaughter of the late Debbie Reynolds is currently dating former \"Twilight\" star, Taylor Lautner.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1146\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/billie.jpg\" alt=\"billie\" width=\"551\" height=\"297\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Orlando Bloom</h1>\r\n<h3>Katy Perry was previously famously married to controversial comedian and actor Russell Brand. She is currently dating English versatile actor Orlando Bloom, of \"The Lord of the Rings\" and \"The Pirates of the Caribbean\" fame.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1160\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/katy.jpg\" alt=\"katy\" width=\"549\" height=\"288\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper and Irina Shayk</h1>\r\n<h3>Widely and consistently considered to be one of Hollywood\'s hottest men, Bradley Cooper is currently dating Russian supermodel Irina Shayk. They have been together since early 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1147\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/bradley.jpg\" alt=\"bradley\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" />','Surprising Celebrity Couples','','inherit','closed','closed','','1113-revision-v1','','','2017-01-31 17:35:06','2017-01-31 17:35:06','',1113,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1113-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1460,1,'2017-01-31 17:35:13','2017-01-31 17:35:13','<h2>We all love pets, and celebrities are no different. Whether they show them to the world or not, these celebs have the cutest pets you can find.</h2>\r\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth and Dora</h1>\r\n<h3>Known for his role in \"The Hunger Games\" trilogy, Liam Hemsworth is a known dog lover, and has adopted a pet dog called Dora.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1192\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/liam-hem.jpg\" alt=\"liam-hem\" width=\"388\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Lady Gaga and Miss Asia Kinney</h1>\r\n<h3>Famous and successful singer and performer Lady Gaga has a black French Bulldog named Miss Asia Kinney. Miss Kinney is a pet model and has also appeared on television.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1190\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lady-gaga1.jpg\" alt=\"lady-gaga\" width=\"519\" height=\"518\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cara Delevigne and Cecil The Bunny</h1>\r\n<h3>Cara Delevigne is a very successful young actor and model, but her bunny Cecil is successful in his own right. Cecil has a Twitter account as well as an Instagram account with thousands of followers on each one.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cara.png\" alt=\"cara\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Taylor Swift and Her Cats</h1>\r\n<h3>Taylor Swift, besides being a pop sensation, is a known cat enthusiast. Her cats are named Dr. Meredith Grey and Detective Olivia Benson. Both cats have flourishing Instagram accounts.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1199\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor.png\" alt=\"taylor\" width=\"480\" height=\"475\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Miley Cyrus\' Cats and Dogs</h1>\r\n<h3>Miley Cyrus is a wonderful pet owner. She has been known to adopt many pets – dogs, cats, rabbits and even a pig, once. Her current pet resume includes 6 dogs and 3 cats (that we know of).</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1193\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/miley.png\" alt=\"miley\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Paris Hilton and Peter Pan</h1>\r\n<h3>Paris Hilton\'s pets were always famous, and she is known to keep them by her side at all times. Her most famous current pooch, the Chihuahua Peter Pan Hilton, has over 39 thousand followers on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1197\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/paris.jpg\" alt=\"paris\" width=\"353\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariel Winter and Chloe</h1>\r\n<h3>Ariel Winter of \"Modern Family\" fame has recently adopted a beautiful German Shepard and named her Chloe. Besides Chloe, Winter has 2 other dogs.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1203\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ariel.jpg\" alt=\"ariel\" width=\"539\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Justin Bieber and Esther</h1>\r\n<h3>Justin Bieber, the teen pop sensation and heartthrob, has a cute puppy named Esther Bieber. He also owns another pup named Phil.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1204\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bieber.jpg\" alt=\"bieber\" width=\"520\" height=\"515\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Sirius Black</h1>\r\n<h3>Ariana Grande is apparently a Harry Potter fan, as she named her newest puppy Sirius Black, after a character in the Harry Potter series.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1183\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-black.jpg\" alt=\"grande-black\" width=\"538\" height=\"538\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Toulouse</h1>\r\n<h3>Before adopting Sirius Black, Grande has adopted Toulouse from an animal shelter. Toulouse has since modeled for Coach.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1184\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-toulouse.jpg\" alt=\"grande-toulouse\" width=\"540\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Demi Lovato\'s Buddy</h1>\r\n<h3>Demi Lovato\'s pup named Buddy has his own Twitter following, with over 61 thousand followers on his account.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1180\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/demi.jpg\" alt=\"demi\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Kitty Purry</h1>\r\n<h3>Katy Perry is an avid cat lover and has gone on record announcing it on various occasions. Her most famous cat is Kitty Purry, who made a cameo in Perry\'s \"I Kissed a Girl\" video.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1189\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Katy_perry_and_kitty_purry.jpg\" alt=\"katy_perry_and_kitty_purry\" width=\"472\" height=\"461\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Emmy Rossum and Cinnamon</h1>\r\n<h3>Emmy Rossum of the TV series \"Shameless\" has a cute puppy named Cinnamon. She shares pictures of Cinnamon and her frequently on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1182\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emmy-rossum.jpg\" alt=\"emmy-rossum\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Nikki Reed and Ian Somerhalder\'s dogs</h1>\r\n<h3>The successful couple owns two dogs, and they make sure to post as many pictures of them on Instagram as they can. The dogs are named Enzo Reed and Nietzsche Somerhalder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1209\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nikki-reed1.jpg\" alt=\"nikki-reed\" width=\"548\" height=\"517\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Anna Sophia Robb and Sir Ferguson</h1>\r\nAnna Sophia Robb is a teen actor. She has appeared in numerous successful Hollywood films and is a proud owner of a pet dog named Sir Ferguson.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1202\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/annasophia.png\" alt=\"annasophia\" width=\"549\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Iggy Azalea</h1>\r\n<h3>Iggy Azalea has been in the spotlight for the past few years, releasing some hit singles. She owns a French bulldog who goes by the very long name of Shrinkabull Jam Don\'t Shake Like That Jelli Azalea.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1185\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/iggy.jpg\" alt=\"iggy\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kaley Cuoco and Ruby</h1>\r\n<h3>Kaley Cuoco is known for playing the character of Penny in \"The Big Bang Theory\". She also owns a cute little pup she has adopted from an animal shelter, named Ruby.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1205\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/caley.jpg\" alt=\"caley\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Diana Agron and Freddie</h1>\r\n<h3>The former \"Glee\" star also owns a cute French bulldog, who she named Freddie. She regularly posts pictures of Freddie on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1200\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/agron.jpg\" alt=\"agron\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chelsea Handler</h1>\r\n<h3>American actress, television host and producer Chelsea Handler has a cute pup named Tammy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1207\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chelsea.jpeg\" alt=\"chelsea\" width=\"377\" height=\"502\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Miranda Kerr and Frankie</h1>\r\n<h3>Miranda Kerr is an international supermodel. When she has some time off from modeling, though, she enjoys cuddling with her cute puppy Frankie.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1194\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Miranda-Kerrr.jpg\" alt=\"Australian model Miranda Kerr looking beautiful in blue as she poses with her pet dog while on the set of a commercial in Santa Monica, Ca Pictured: Miranda Kerr Ref: SPL943776 050215 Picture by: London Entertainment /Splash Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"404\" height=\"499\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Lena Dunham and Lamby</h1>\r\n<h3>Lena Dunham gained fame for writing and starring in the hit TV show \"Girls\". She has a dog named Lamby whom she takes with her everywhere.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1191\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lena.jpg\" alt=\"lena\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chrissy Teigen and Pippa</h1>\r\n<h3>Chrissy Teigen and her husband, singer-songwriter John Legend, own a handful of dogs. One of which is the cute Pippa, who is a French bulldog.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1179\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chrissy.jpg\" alt=\"chrissy\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Amanda Seyfried and Finn</h1>\r\n<h3>Amanda Seyfried is an American actress known for roles in films such as \"Mean Girls\" and \"Mamma Mia\". Her best friend is an Australian Shepard named Finn.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1201\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/amanda.jpg\" alt=\"amanda\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Graham</h1>\r\n<h3>Ed Sheeran is known for writing and singing heartfelt songs. The English singer has a big heart himself, and he has adopted a cute little kitten who goes by the name of Graham.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1181\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ed-sheeran.jpg\" alt=\"ed-sheeran\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chloe Grace Moretz and Missy</h1>\r\n<h3>Chloe Grace Moretz is a dog enthusiast, and currently owns two dogs, one of which she named Missy. She even took Missy with her to the set of her film \"Carrie\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1208\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chloe.jpg\" alt=\"chloe\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sarah Hyland and Barkley</h1>\r\n<h3>Another \"Modern Family\" star who is a famous pet owner is Sarah Hyland who plays the role of Haley on the show. She owns a cute puppy called Barkley whom she trained all on her own.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1198\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Sarah-Hyland-1.jpg\" alt=\"sarah-hyland-1\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jessica Chastain and Chaplin</h1>\r\n<h3>Jessica Chaplain sure has a kind heart. She has adopted a three-legged pooch named Chaplin. The two appeared together on the TV show \"The View\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1188\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jessica.jpg\" alt=\"jessica\" width=\"550\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Orlando Bloom and Sidi</h1>\r\n<h3>The other half of the Perry-Bloom couple, Orlando Bloom is known for his affection for dogs. He has a rescue Saluki mix named Sidi, of whom he takes great care.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1196\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/orlando-bloom.jpg\" alt=\"orlando-bloom\" width=\"550\" height=\"447\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jake Gyllenhaal and Atticus</h1>\r\n<h3>Jake Gyllenhaal is a respected and versatile American actor, known for his Academy Award-nominated performance in \"Brokeback Mountain\". He has a beloved dog named Atticus.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1186\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Jake.jpg\" alt=\"jake\" width=\"368\" height=\"502\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Pippi</h1>\r\n<h3>Jennifer Lawrence can\'t seem to do anything wrong, as the young talented actress enjoys incredible success over the past few years. She has a cute puppy called Pippi Lawrence who is very close to her heart.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1187\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen1.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" />','Celebrities And Their Cute Pets','','inherit','closed','closed','','1178-revision-v1','','','2017-01-31 17:35:13','2017-01-31 17:35:13','',1178,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1178-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1461,1,'2017-01-31 19:28:02','2017-01-31 19:28:02','<h2>Some celebs have a little more than just a high school diploma under their belts. They chose to pursue a career in acting or in music eventually, but what were their other career options?</h2>\r\n<h1>Shaquille O\'Neal</h1>\r\n<h3>The former NBA superstar promised his mother that he will complete his Bachelor\'s degree after he left LSU for the NBA. He fulfilled that promise in 2000, earning a B.A. in general studies. O\'Neal continued to follow his passion for education in the following years, earning an MBA from the University of Phoenix through online courses, and finally received his Doctorate in Education in 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1133\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shaq.jpg\" alt=\"shaq\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ken Jeong</h1>\r\n<h3>Ken Jeong is known to most people from his iconic roles in films (such as The Hangover trilogy) and in TV series, such as Community. Although stand-up comedy and comedy work in general were his life-long passions, Jeong obtained an M.D. from the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill in 1995. He is a licensed physician for internal medicine in California.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1126\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ken-Jeong.jpg\" alt=\"ken-jeong\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Sigourney Weaver</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Alien\", \"Ghostbusters\", \"Avatar\" and \"The Ice Storm\" successful actress has a wealth of awards at her disposal, winning seven Golden Globe Awards. Nicknamed \"The Sci-Fi Queen\", Weaver has obtained a Bachelor\'s Degree from Stanford University as well as a Master of Fine Arts degree from Yale University.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1134\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Sigourney.jpg\" alt=\"NEW YORK, NY - MAY 13: Actress Sigourney Weaver attends the American Ballet Theatre opening night Spring Gala at Lincoln Center on May 13, 2013 in New York City. (Photo by Stephen Lovekin/Getty Images)\" width=\"328\" height=\"493\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>David Duchovny</h1>\r\n<h3>Before making his breakout role in The X-Files, David Duchovny attended Yale University, where he earned an M.A. in English Literature. He was aiming to obtain a doctorate but gave it up to pursue his acting career.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1117\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/David.jpg\" alt=\"david\" width=\"550\" height=\"330\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dolph Lundgren</h1>\r\n<h3>The Swedish bodybuilder, recognizable to audiences all over the world from films such as Rocky VI and The Expendables, earned his Master\'s in Engineering at the University of Sydney.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1118\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Dolph.jpg\" alt=\"dolph\" width=\"376\" height=\"501\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jodie Foster</h1>\r\n<h3>One of the most prominent actresses of our time, Jodie Foster has appeared in countless memorable films and roles. And despite beginning her acting career in her teens, she made sure to obtain a higher education degree, receiving a B.A. in English Literature from Yale University. She later received an honorary Ph.D. from her alma mater.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1124\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Jodie.jpg\" alt=\"jodie\" width=\"550\" height=\"336\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Lisa Kudrow</h1>\r\n<h3>Lisa Kudrow can be considered to be the complete opposite of her dim-witted representation of Phoebe Buffay on TV\'s Friends. Kudrow has a B.Sc. degree in Biology from Vassar College.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1127\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lisa.jpg\" alt=\"TORONTO, ON - SEPTEMBER 16: Actress Lisa Kudrow from the film \'Love and Other Impossible Pursuits\' poses for a portrait during the 2009 Toronto International Film Festival at The Sutton Place Hotel on September 16, 2009 in Toronto, Canada.\" width=\"344\" height=\"496\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Conan O\'Brien</h1>\r\n<h3>Popular talk-show host Conan O\'Brien is not only funny, but he is also very smart and sharp. O\'Brian graduated valedictorian from his high school and went on to study at Harvard, where he obtained a B.A. in History and Literature.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1115\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/conan.jpg\" alt=\"conan\" width=\"548\" height=\"365\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Art Garfunkel</h1>\r\n<h3>Before he rose to fame as the second half of the legendary musical duo Simon and Garfunkel, Art Garfunkel was serious about his studies. So serious, that he obtained his B.A. in art history in 1962 and his M.A. in mathematics in 1967. He was on his way to earning a doctorate in mathematics education when his musical partnership with Paul Simon reached its height.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1109\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/art-gar.jpg\" alt=\"art-gar\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Spike Lee</h1>\r\n<h3>Widely considered to be one of the most successful African-American directors in Hollywood, Spike Lee has a B.A. in mass communications. After receiving his B.A., Lee attended New York\'s Tisch School of the Arts, where he has earned an M.A. in film and television.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1135\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/spike-lee.jpg\" alt=\"spike-lee\" width=\"549\" height=\"343\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jerry Springer</h1>\r\n<h3>The controversial host of \"The Jerry Springer Show\" has earned a B.A. in Political Science from Tulane University. He has also earned a Juris Doctor degree from Northwestern University.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1123\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jerry-springer.jpg\" alt=\"jerry-springer\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ashley Judd</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Ruby in Paradise\", \"Norma Jean &amp; Marilyn\" and \"Divergent\" actress has earned a Master\'s Degree in public administration from Harvard. She is also currently working on obtaining a Ph.D. from the University of Berkeley.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1140\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ashley-judd1.jpg\" alt=\"ashley-judd\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Bill Cosby</h1>\r\n<h3>Comedian, actor and author Bill Cosby has had his fair share of controversy in the past few years. He holds many honorary degrees from various universities, some of which have rescinded those degrees due to the controversy he was involved in. But Cosby can reassure himself that his own, hard earned Ed.D. Degree from the University of Massachusetts will remain at his disposal.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1116\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cosby-bu.jpg\" alt=\"cosby-bu\" width=\"549\" height=\"386\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Peter Weller</h1>\r\n<h3>Known mainly for his role as the original RoboCop, Peter Weller not only has an M.A. in Renaissance Art, but he also has a Ph.D. in Italian Renaissance Art History.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1131\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/peter-weller.jpeg\" alt=\"peter-weller\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>\"Weird\" Al Yankovic</h1>\r\n<h3>Actor, singer, songwriter, parodist, comedian, satirist, author, and, apparently, also an architect, \"Weird\" Al Yankovic has obtained a B.A. in architecture from the California Polytechnic State University.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1137\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/weird-al.jpg\" alt=\"weird-al\" width=\"549\" height=\"385\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Graham Chapman</h1>\r\n<h3>The late Graham Chapman, known for his parts as a member of the legendary comical group Monty Python, was initially torn between pursuing an acting career or continuing on his path for a medical career. He has had an M.D. from St. Bartholomew\'s Hospital Medical School.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1121\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/graham-chapman.jpg\" alt=\"graham-chapman\" width=\"519\" height=\"518\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Brian May</h1>\r\n<h3>Brian May is best known as the lead guitarist of the rock band Queen. While still touring with the remaining living members of the group, May has obtained a Ph.D. in astrophysics and is an active astrophysicist, publishing scientific research papers.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1111\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/brian-may.jpg\" alt=\"SONY DSC\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Adam Driver</h1>\r\n<h3>Adam Driver broke through in Hollywood with his role as Adam Sackler in the TV show Girls. He was later cast as Kylo Ren, the main antagonist of the new Star Wars trilogy. Before his breakthrough, though, Adam Driver was in the Marines; After he was released from service, he went on to obtain a B.A. in drama from Julliard.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1139\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/adam.jpg\" alt=\"adam\" width=\"389\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ludacris</h1>\r\n<h3>Mostly known for his successful music career during the 2000\'s and for his various roles in films – mainly in the Fast and Furious franchise – Ludacris has a Bachelor\'s degree in Music Management from Georgia State University.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1128\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/luda.jpg\" alt=\"luda\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Martin</h1>\r\n<h3>Leading singer of the popular British band Coldplay, Chris Martin has attended the University College London, where he\'s earned his Bachelor\'s degree in Greek and Latin.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1141\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Chris-Martin-singing.jpg\" alt=\"chris-martin-singing\" width=\"549\" height=\"424\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>John Legend</h1>\r\n<h3>John Legend is an American musician, singer, and songwriter. He is the winner of ten Grammy Awards, as well as a Golden Globe Award and an Academy Award. He attended the University of Pennsylvania, where he has earned a Bachelor\'s degree in English with an emphasis on African-American literature in 1999.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1125\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/John-Legend.jpg\" alt=\"john-legend\" width=\"357\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Brooke Shields</h1>\r\n<h3>The American actress and model started acting at the very young age of 12. Shields put her modeling career on hold so she could attend Princeton University, where she obtained a B.A. in Romance Languages.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1112\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Brooke-Shields-ppcorn.jpg\" alt=\"brooke-shields-ppcorn\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Edward Norton</h1>\r\n<h3>Edward Norton has gained fame for acting in some critically approved roles in films such as \"Primal Fears\", \"American History X\", \"Fight Club\" and \"Red Dragon\". He is one of Hollywood\'s most recognizable faces. Norton began acting while attending Yale University, where he studied towards – and eventually gained – a B.A. in History.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1119\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ed.jpg\" alt=\"ed\" width=\"406\" height=\"499\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Hugh Hefner</h1>\r\n<h3>It\'s hard to imagine anyone in the world who is not familiar with the name Hugh Hefner. The founder of Playboy Enterprises, Hefner made a fortune for himself over the years and became one of the most recognizable celebrities in the world. In 1949, Hefner graduated from the University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign with a B.A. in psychology.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1122\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/heff.jpg\" alt=\"heff\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Steve Carell</h1>\r\n<h3>Widely regarded as one of the funniest actors in Hollywood, Steve Carell has appeared in dozens of films. He was also the leading actor on the critically acclaimed TV Series \"The Office\". Prior to his career in acting, Carell attended Denison University, where he earned his Bachelor\'s degree in History.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1136\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/steve-carell.jpg\" alt=\"steve-carell\" width=\"549\" height=\"331\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Will Ferrell</h1>\r\n<h3>Another one of Hollywood\'s funniest, Will Ferrell\'s career didn’t always seem to head towards comedy: in 1990 he graduated from the University of Southern California with a B.A. in Sports Information.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1138\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/will.jpg\" alt=\"will\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>James Franco</h1>\r\n<h3>Often playing laid back, careless stoner characters, James Franco does not display the same attitude when it comes to his education. Franco has an M.F.A. degree in writing from Columbia University and is working towards obtaining a Ph.D. in English from Yale University.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1120\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/franco.jpg\" alt=\"NEW YORK, NY - AUGUST 22: Actor James Franco attends the &quot;Kink&quot; New York Premiere at IFC Center on August 22, 2014 in New York City. (Photo by Andrew H. Walker/Getty Images)\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Mayim Bialik</h1>\r\n<h3>Although she appears on Television week-in, week-out as part of the cast of the highly popular series \"The Big Bang Theory\", Bialik\'s main focus prior to joining the show was actual science, and she has a Ph.D. in neuroscience to prove it.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1129\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mayim.jpg\" alt=\"BEVERLY HILLS, CA - AUGUST 24: Actress Mayim Bialik attends the Television Academy\'s Performers Peer Group Hold Cocktail Reception to Celebrate the 67th Emmy Awards at the Montage Beverly Hills Hotel on August 24, 2015 in Beverly Hills, California. (Photo by Frederick M. Brown/Getty Images)\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Natalie Portman</h1>\r\n<h3>The Academy Award winning talented actress has made her mark on Hollywood over the past two decades. Before that, though, she has attended Harvard University, where she obtained a B.A. degree in psychology.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1130\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/natalie.jpg\" alt=\"natalie\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Rowan Atkinson</h1>\r\n<h3>The character of Mr. Bean is far from a truthful representation of the multitalented and brilliant Rowan Atkinson. The British actor actually has a Master\'s degree in Electrical Engineering from The Queen\'s College in Oxford. It appears he is as smart as he is funny.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1132\" src=\"http://www.feelsyoung.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/rowan.jpg\" alt=\"rowan\" width=\"549\" height=\"288\" />','Celebs With Higher Education Degrees That You Didn\'t Know About','','inherit','closed','closed','','1108-autosave-v1','','','2017-01-31 19:28:02','2017-01-31 19:28:02','',1108,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1108-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1462,1,'2017-03-05 15:51:49','2017-03-05 15:51:49','test<!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\ntest','Test','','trash','open','open','','__trashed-2','','','2017-03-05 15:53:15','2017-03-05 15:53:15','',0,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/?p=1462',0,'post','',0),(1463,1,'2017-03-05 15:51:44','2017-03-05 15:51:44','test<!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\ntest','Test','','inherit','closed','closed','','1462-revision-v1','','','2017-03-05 15:51:44','2017-03-05 15:51:44','',1462,'http://www.feelsyoung.com/1462-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1464,1,'2017-03-05 15:54:05','0000-00-00 